(893, 1, '2021-03-20 11:23:41', '2021-03-20 11:23:41', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/huynhma-16161338525991993633042.jpg\" id=\"img_f05f69d0-8878-11eb-accd-4b65fc5be44e\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1347\" alt=\"TP.HCM mun gim 30% thi gian x l phn nh ca doanh nghip - nh 1.\" title=\"TP.HCM mun gim 30% thi gian x l phn nh ca doanh nghip - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"f05f69d0-8878-11eb-accd-4b65fc5be44e\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/huynhma-16161338525991993633042.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">B L Th Hunh Mai, gim c S K hoch - u t TP.HCM, trao i bn l vi i din cc hip hi doanh nghip nc ngoi  - nh: T TRUNG</p></div></div><p><span style=\"\">T cng tc do ng Nguyn Thnh Phong, ch tch UBND TP, lm t trng cng cc thnh vin l cc ph ch tch UBND TP v th trng cc s ngnh ch cht.</span><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">B L Th Hunh Mai, gim c S K hoch - u t, thng trc t cng tc, cho bit s</span><span style=\"\">au 3 nm thnh lp, t chc ny tr thnh m hnh u tin ca c nc trong h tr cc nh u t, nhiu im nghn ca khng t d n  c tho g.</span><br/></p><p>Sau 32 bui lm vic, 110 d n, lnh vc lin quan n u t trn a bn thnh ph  c a vo chng trnh lm vic ca t cng tc.</p><p><span style=\"\">Trong 92 d n c t cng tc kt lun hng x l vng mc, hin c 35 d n, vi tng mc u t hn 320.000 t ng  c tho g cc kh khn, ang trin khai thc hin cc bc u t tip theo.Ngoi ra, 108  xut, kin ngh ca doanh nghip, nh u t cng c t cng tc tip nhn, phn loi, x l.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Trao i vi cc doanh nghip, nh u t quc t ti hi ngh, ng Nguyn Thnh Phong cho bitTP xc nh nm 2021 l nm ch  thc hin \"xy dng chnh quyn  th v ci thin mi trng u t\", do  TP c k hoch 10 nhm gii php ci thin mi trng u t, tng nng lc cnh tranh.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">\"Cc s ngnh TP</span><span style=\"\">nghin cu gim t nht 30% thi gian x l th tc phn nh ca doanh nghip so vi quy nh hin nay, thng xuyn tip xc vi cc doanh nghip theo hi ng kinh t ngnh, kp thi gii quyt vng mc cho doanh nghip, nh u t\", Ch tch UBND TP.HCM yu cu.</span><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">Cng ti hi ngh, UBND TP.HCM trao giy chng nhn u t cho 8 d n vi tng vn u t 23.145 t ng; trao ch trng u t cho 5 d n, tng vn u t gn 15.000 t ng.</span><br/></p><p>Trong s , ng ch ,<span style=\"\">UBND TP.HCM  trao ngh quyt ca Chnh ph cho Cng ty Lotte Properties HCMC i vi d n khu phc hp thng minh - Th Thim Eco Smart City trong khu  th mi Th Thim vi tng vn u t 20.100 t ng.</span></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p><b> xut ngi  tim vc xin c rt ngn thi gian cch ly</b></p><p>Ti bui ly  kin, b<span> Mary Tarnowka, gim c iu hnh AmCham Vit Nam, cho rng Vit Nam cng nh TP.HCM c th xem cung cp v to iu kin thun li mt quy trnh hp l, rt ngn thi gian cch ly cho nhng chuyn gia, doanh nhn quc t  tim vc xin vo Vit Nam.</span></p><p><span>\"Mt chng trnh th im cho php gim hoc min cch ly cho nhng c nhn  c tim chng ng cch s gip to iu kin thun li cho vic ti ha nhp, m ca du lch v phc hi kinh t ca Vit Nam\", b Mary  xut. </span></p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/tp-hcm-muon-giam-30-thoi-gian-xu-ly-phan-anh-cua-doanh-nghiep-20210319103800272.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'TP.HCM mun gim 30% thi gian x l phn nh ca doanh nghip', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tp-hcm-muon-giam-30-thoi-gian-xu-ly-phan-anh-cua-doanh-nghiep', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:23:41', '2021-03-20 11:23:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tp-hcm-muon-giam-30-thoi-gian-xu-ly-phan-anh-cua-doanh-nghiep/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
