(896, 1, '2021-03-20 11:25:58', '2021-03-20 11:25:58', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/20/20191127161223-1616224943009614733904.jpg\" id=\"img_07fc6280-894d-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1143\" alt=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: T cho huyt - nh 1.\" title=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: T cho huyt - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"07fc6280-894d-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/20/20191127161223-1616224943009614733904.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">T cho huyt Si Gn - nh: QUN NAM</p></div></div><p>Nghe my thng bn i chi Si Gn v k chuyn, lu lu li chm vo vi cu ging Si Gn nha nha: \" trng\", \"sao dzy\" l ti m tt.</p><p><b>Ri dp may cng n</b></p><p> l nhng nm cui i hc, ti r thm thng bn i tin c bn nh c nc ngoi, nhn tin gh chi Si Gn mt chuyn cho bit. Sinh vin thi bao cp ngoi mi my k go cng c thm cht hc bng nn hai thng cng  dnh t tin lm l ph chuyn i. </p><p>Tin tu xe lc  rt t v kh mua c v nn hai thng tnh bi liu nhy tu i chui. Xm nh ti  gn ga v c nhiu ngi lm bn ngnh ng st. Bn ti nh c hng xm lm kim sot vin trn tu dn vo ga v chui ln tu trt lt. </p><p>Hai a c pht hai ci vng  ti n th ra u toa mc ln ng. Ban ngy th i ti i lui, nu thy kim sot v th gi v i vo toilet. Ti sng  khu vc gn ga, bit nn mc ti, n cp vt trn tu thi  xy ra nh cm ba nn dn thng bn cn thn, ti ng nh b giy, bp di lng nm  ln cho chc n. </p><p>Dn k nh vy m khng bit ti sao n vn qun. Hu qu l vo ti Si Gn th n mt lun c bp ln giy. Hai thng lang thang gia Si Gn vi b dng khng th hi hc hn: thng mang giy ty, thng i chn t, tht tha tht thu gia  hi. </p><p><b>T cho huyt ca ngi khng quen</b></p><p>Vi s tin cn li khng  thu phng tr nn hai a bn nhau ra cng vin ng qua m cho  tin. Lang thang mt lc, hai thng quyt nh dng chn  cng vin Trn Hng o. Hai thng tm hai ci gh   ng lng ch tri sng. </p><p>Lc ny cng  khuya m hai a cha c ci g cho vo bng, i cn co. Gn ch gh  bn ti nm c chic xe y bn cho huyt. C b bn cho nhn c trc tui bn ti nhng  trng c v tng tri, mn m. </p><p>Xe cho huyt ny hnh nh bn xuyn m phc v khch bnh dn i chi v khuya. C b c v lanh l, d mn. Mc d mun gi hai thng hai t cho n cho  i nhng ngh n ci bp lp kp ca ti nn nh thi. </p><p>ang thiu thiu ng cht nghe ting gi: \"Anh i, n cho huyt khng?\". Bn ti nhn nhau na mun gt, na mun lc. C b cht hi: \"Hai anh l sinh vin phi hng?\". Ti ngc nhin: \"Sao em bit?\". C b ci nh mt tinh nghch: \"Nhn b dng hai anh l bit ri\". </p><p>Hai a nh khai tht chuyn mt  c trn tu. Tht ra khng phi  c b thng hi m mun c dp chuyn tr vi con gi Si Gn th xem sao. Lt sau c b bng ti hai t cho huyt nng hi: \"My anh n i cho nng. Chc i ri phi hng? My anh ng c lo, em mi\". </p><p>Bn ti mt  bng, khng ng ln u tin i Si Gn chi li gp cnh oi om th ny. D sao cng khng th lm mt mt sinh vin ngnh kinh t, ti rt bp tnh tr tin th em xua tay: \"Thi, my anh  dnh cn tiu xi v mua v v nh na\". \", my anh a bp vi  c y em ct gim cho ch ng  y bn ma c hay chn lt lm  nghen\". </p><p>Mt thong chn ch v kch bn tng t ny ti  nghe hay c  u : mi n ung, sau  b thuc m ri lt sch  c. By gi m a bp v hnh l cho c nu khng may gp k gian th ch c nc i n my. Khng hiu sao ci  ngh tiu cc  ch thong qua trong u ti nh xt in ri bin mt.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/20/20180817145615-1616224943007183238101.jpg\" id=\"img_d580a2c0-8948-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1714\" alt=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: T cho huyt - nh 2.\" title=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: T cho huyt - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"d580a2c0-8948-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/20/20180817145615-1616224943007183238101.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Cho huyt kh qun - nh: QUN NAM</p></div></div><p><b>Cm n em</b></p><p>Ti lt ng h, bp tin, bal o qun a ht cho c b nh b thi min. Thng bn ti sau mt thong chn ch v \"kinh cung chi iu\" ri cng rm rp lm theo. C l v mt c b tot ln v thnh thin, chn tht. Hai thng lm hai t cho nng hi, thm lng ri nh mt gic ti sng. </p><p>C b ang li hi dn hng. Khi thy bn ti thc dy lin mang ti hai ly c ph sa v hai ci bnh bao nng hi. Bui sng nhn r mt em cng m thm hn, v p mn m ca ngi con gi t phng Nam y nng gi. </p><p>Bn ti cm n v tnh ni li chia tay th em lc trong xe y a cho thng bn ti i dp Lo nhn hi c nhng vn cn tt: \"Anh mang tm ri tm mua i mi nhen. Hn gp li\". Bn ti sau  ri Si Gn v qu vi li ha s tm gp li em mt ngy gn nht.</p><p>Sau ny ra trng, c nhiu dp cng tc Si Gn ti vn thng gh qua cng vin Trn Hng o, tm c b bn cho huyt ngy xa nhng bng chim tm c. </p><p>Thnh ph by gi phn hoa, khng bit c ai cn nh mn cho huyt ngy xa? Ti vn tm n cho huyt mi khi c dp vo Si Gn v vn gi i dp Lo mang nhiu k nim v mt c b Si Gn mi quen bit v v cng tt bng. Cm n em.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/sai-gon-bao-dung-tphcm-nghia-tinh-to-chao-huyet-20210320133238638.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: T cho huyt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sai-gon-bao-dung-tp-hcm-nghia-tinh-to-chao-huyet', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:25:58', '2021-03-20 11:25:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/sai-gon-bao-dung-tp-hcm-nghia-tinh-to-chao-huyet/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
