(898, 1, '2021-03-20 11:26:58', '2021-03-20 11:26:58', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/20/20210320-anh-1-suoi-khoang-nong-truong-xuan-anh-doan-minh-long-16162308110811843008151.jpg\" id=\"img_6f1c4e00-895a-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" w=\"1024\" h=\"707\" alt=\"Khnh Ha cha thu hi c d n treo 1/4 th k c nhiu vi phm - nh 1.\" title=\"Khnh Ha cha thu hi c d n treo 1/4 th k c nhiu vi phm - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"6f1c4e00-895a-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/20/20210320-anh-1-suoi-khoang-nong-truong-xuan-anh-doan-minh-long-16162308110811843008151.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">D n khu du lch sui khong nng Trng Xun (th x Ninh Ha, Khnh Ha) ang b tnh x l thu hi d n do c nhiu vi phm, treo t nm 1996 n nay - nh: ON MINH LONG</p></div></div><p><span style=\"\">Lin quan n vic x l d n khu du lch sui khong nng Trng Xun, Ph th tng thng trc Trng Ha Bnh  c  kin ch o tnh cch y hn 3 nm phi \"m bo vic s dng t nng nghip, t rng ng mc ch, hn ch vic tc ng xu n mi trng rng t nhin\" (theo thng bo ca Vn phng Chnh ph ngy 5-2-2018).</span><br/></p><p>Sau khi tin hnh gim st, t nm 2018 HND tnh Khnh Ha cng   ngh UBND tnh x l vi phm ti d n trn. Thng 9-2020, UBND tnh c thng bo chm dt hot ng, thu hi giy chng nhn u t d n  nu nhng n nay vn cn c nhy, cha xong.</p><p>Mi y, Ch tch UBND tnh Khnh Ha Nguyn Tn Tun tip tc kt lun, giao S K hoch v u t thc hin th tc chm dt hot ng, thu hi giy chng nhn u t d n khu du lch sui khong nng Trng Xun ti x Ninh Ty, th x Ninh Ha (theo thng bo ca tnh ngy 17-3-2021).</p><p>D n trn  c UBND tnh Khnh Ha trc y giao t t nm 1996 v nm 1997 cho Cng ty TNHH nc khong Trng Xun thu hn 49ha  u t lm khu du lch sui khong nng. Trong  bao gm m sui khong nng, t nng nghip (19,12ha) v c rng phng h, rng g tnhin (33,6ha). Thi hn cho thu t lm d n l n thng 1-2030.</p><p>Th nhng sau khi c giao t, Cng ty TNHH nc khong Trng Xun khng thc hin u t nh  cam kt. Sau , d n  c sang tay cho nh u t mi. Nh u t mi l Cng ty TNHH thng mi, dch v sn xut ch bin thc phm Thnh Cng  c UBND tnh cp giy chng nhn u t vo thng 10-2009.</p><p>D n khu du lch sui khong nng Trng Xun ca nh u t mi c tng thi hn s dng t thm 19 nm (n thng 10-2049), gm ton b t, rng phng h v sui khong nng m tnh  cho nh u t c l Cng ty TNHH nc khong Trng Xun thu, nhng sau khi cng ty ny gii th  hn 8 nm vn khng b thu hi t (tnh n khi cp giy chng nhn u t cho nh u t mi vo thng 10-2009).</p><p>Theo kt lun thanh tra ca Tng cc a cht v khong sn Vit Nam th Cng ty TNHH nc khong Trng Xun b gii th trc thi hn cch y gn 20 nm, theo quyt nh ca B K hoch v u t ngy 28-5-2001. Cn giy php khai thc khong sn m nc khong nng ti d n khu du lch sui khong nng Trng Xun cng  b chm dt hiu lc theo quy nh ca Lut khong sn.</p><p>Cho n nay, theo thng bo ca UBND tnh Khnh Ha, \"d n khu du lch sui khong nng Trng Xun  ht tin , cha hon thnh cc th tc lin quan v t ai, rng, khong sn, cp php xy dng\".</p><p>V vy, ch tch UBND tnh Khnh Ha kt lun phi x l theo ng quy nh php lut, chm dt hot ng, thu hi giy chng nhn u t i vi d n treo 1/4 th k  nu trn.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://dulich.tuoitre.vn/khanh-hoa-chua-thu-hoi-duoc-du-an-treo-1-4-the-ky-co-nhieu-vi-pham-20210320162210893.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Cha thu hi c d n treo 1/4 th k c nhiu vi phm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chua-thu-hoi-duoc-du-an-treo-1-4-the-ky-co-nhieu-vi-pham', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:26:58', '2021-03-20 11:26:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/chua-thu-hoi-duoc-du-an-treo-1-4-the-ky-co-nhieu-vi-pham/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(899, 1, '2021-03-20 11:27:57', '2021-03-20 11:27:57', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/20/2021-03-15t124301z688123841rc2obm9cqvy5rtrmadp3tesla-musk-16162252854711041702101.jpg\" id=\"img_d30b91d0-894d-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"T ph Musk ni Tesla s ng ca nu dng xe lm gin ip - nh 1.\" title=\"T ph Musk ni Tesla s ng ca nu dng xe lm gin ip - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"d30b91d0-894d-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/20/2021-03-15t124301z688123841rc2obm9cqvy5rtrmadp3tesla-musk-16162252854711041702101.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">T ph Elon Musk ph nhn s dng xe lm gin ip - nh: REUTERS</p></div></div><p>\"Chng ti rt t tin trc bt c thng tin no. Nu Tesla dng xe  lm gin ip  Trung Quc hay bt c ni no, chng ti s b ng ca\", Hng tin Reuters dn li t ph M ni ngy 20-3 khi xut hin trc tuyn ti Din n pht trin Trung Quc. Theo ng Musk, nu mt cng ty thng mi nh Tesla dnh lu n bt c hot ng gin ip no cng s  li nhng hu qu nghim trng.</p><p>Ti din n ny, t ph M cng ku gi M v Trung Quc tin tng nhau hn trong bi cnh cc nh ngoi giao hai nc va c cuc gp cng thng  Alaska. y l cuc gp trc tip u tin gia hai bn k t khi Tng thng M Joe Biden ln nm quyn.</p><p>Tuyn b ca ng Musk a ra cha y 24 gi sau khi cc hng tin nh Bloomberg, Reuters  dn mt s ngun tin cho hay thng bo ca qun i Trung Quc cho rng cc my quay a hng v cm bin siu m trn nhng chic xe Tesla c th lm l a im, v vic cm xe ca hng ny nhm m bo an ton thng tin qun s. Theo , t tun ny, tt c ngi s dng xe Tesla b yu cu u xe bn ngoi cc khu phc hp qun i  Trung Quc.</p><p>Cng lc, <i>Wall Street Journal </i>cng a tin Chnh ph Trung Quc cm s dng xe Tesla ti cc khu nh cng, qun s ti nhng khu cng nghip nhy cm v cc c quan quan trng, vi lo ngi c th lm r r thng tin an ninh quc gia.</p><p>Pha Trung Quc cha xc nhn lnh cm. Theo cc quan chc Trung Quc, cm bin trn xe ca Tesla ghi li hnh nh cc a im ln cn. Tesla cng c th tip cn cc thng tin nh thi im v a im s dng xe, cng nh thng tin c nhn ca ti x, cc s in thoi c lu trn xe. Bc Kinh lo ngi nhng d liu ny c th c gi v M.</p><p>Cc dng xe ca Tesla s dng nhiu my quay gn quanh xe  h tr vic u xe v chc nng t li. Mt s dng c gn thm c my quay trn knh chiu hu  xc nh liu ngi dng c ang nhn ng hay khng.</p><p>Mt s ngun tin cho bit Trung Quc cng lo ngi vi chng trnh th nghim tnh nng t li hon ton ca Tesla. u thng 3-2021, t ph Elon Musk, ng ch ca Tesla, thng bo chng trnh  m rng ra trn 2.000 ch xe.<br/></p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://congnghe.tuoitre.vn/ti-phu-musk-noi-tesla-se-dong-cua-neu-dung-xe-lam-gian-diep-20210320143155818.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'T ph Musk ni Tesla s ng ca nu dng xe lm gin ip', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ti-phu-musk-noi-tesla-se-dong-cua-neu-dung-xe-lam-gian-diep', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:27:57', '2021-03-20 11:27:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/ti-phu-musk-noi-tesla-se-dong-cua-neu-dung-xe-lam-gian-diep/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
