(901, 1, '2021-03-20 11:30:44', '2021-03-20 11:30:44', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph Ch tch UBND TP.HCM V Vn Hoan va k vn bn khn gi cc s ngnh, UBND cc qun huyn v tng cng cng tc tuyn truyn, x l cc hnh vi vi phm ting n trn a bn.</p>\n<p class=\"item-photo\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/w800/Uploaded/2021/yfqfr/2021_03_20/tieng-on-karaoke-tu-phat-tphcm-2_fdjr.jpg\" alt=\"TP.HCM: Khoanh vng, kim tra t xut \'hung thn\' karaoke  - nh 1\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/yfqfr/2021_03_20/tieng-on-karaoke-tu-phat-tphcm-2_fdjr.jpg\" cms-photo-caption=\"Vn bn khn ca UBND TP.HCM. nh: T LM\"/><br/>&#13;\n<em class=\"image_caption\">Vn bn khn ca UBND TP.HCM. nh: T LM</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo , TP.HCM s chia t x l vi phm ting n lm hai giai on. Trong thi gian t 25-3 n 30-6, ton a bn TP s tp trung cng tc tuyn truyn, vn ng, nhc nh cc doanh nghip, h kinh doanh c th v ngi dn k cam kt thc hin nghim tc cc quy nh php lut c lin quan n ting n.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong giai on ny, chnh quyn TP s thng xuyn thng tin, nhc nh v hn ch ting n thng qua tin nhn n cc thu bao in thoi di ng; tuyn truyn vn ng ti cc a phng, c s, bng in t; c quan, trng hc</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia on hai bt u t ngy 30-6, TP s tp trung m t cao im kim tra, gim st, x l nghim cc hnh vi vi phm lin quan n ting n, trong  trng tm l chn chnh tnh trng gy ting n trong cc khu dn c.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong t cao im ny, chnh quyn cc cp cng s, ngnh lin quan s thnh lp cc t cng tc lin ngnh nhm xy dng k hoch kim tra nh k v t xut theo lnh vc ph trch; nhng khu vc thng xuyn b phn nh vi phm ting n s c khoanh vng, kim tra thng xuyn.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngi ng u mi a phng phi chu trch nhim nu  ti vi phm ti cc a im  kim tra, x l.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cng trong t cao im ny, UBND TP giao Cng an TP.HCM ch o cng an a bn pht hin, x l kp thi cc trng hp vi phm quy nh v ting n. Ngnh cng an cn nghin cu  xut b sung trang thit b k thut, phng tin cn thit phc v cng tc x l vi phm.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S TM&amp;MT c giao nghin cu, tng hp nhng kh khn trong qu trnh trin khai v  xut gii php cho UBND TP. S cng c trch nhim s kt, nh gi kt qu cao im x l vi phm v ting n.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S Vn ha Th thao ch tr xy dng, trin khai k hoch tng cng kim tra i vi cc c s vn ha, kinh doanh, dch v vn ha, th thao v vn  vi phm quy nh ting n.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngoi ra, UBND TP cng  ngh cc s, ngnh tip tc nghin cu,  xut hng x l cc hnh vi, vi phm trong lnh vc mnh ph trch.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trc , sau phn nh ca cc c quan bo ch v tnh trng karaoke t pht gy n trong khu dn c, hm 26-2, Ch tch UBND TP Nguyn Thnh Phong  c nhng ch o khn cho cc s ngnh, qun huyn. Trong  ng ch o Cng an TP Th c v cng an cc qun, huyn giao trch nhim cho trng cng an x, phng, th trn trc tip ch o cng tc phng nga, pht hin v ngn chn kp thi, x l hiu qu cc vi phm v ting n ti a bn qun l.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V lu di, ng yu cu cc s, ngnh cn phi hp  hon thin php l, r sot cc quy nh php lut  a ra nhng gii php x l dt im, hiu qu vn nn trn.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">n ngy 9-3, ti cuc hp v x l ting n, Ph Ch tch UBND TP V Vn Hoan, cho bit lnh o TP  thng nht ch trng m t cao im t nay n cui nm x l dt im cc hnh vi vi phm ting n.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ng Hoan, ting n nh hng n sc khe cng ng, c bit gim cht lng cuc sng ca ngi dn.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> Chng ta c gng  kinh t pht trin, i sng nng cao, vn ha c hng th  nhiu gc  khc nhau th dt khot phi tm cch  x l cho bng c nhng vn  tc ng lm gim cht lng cuc sng ca ngi dn, trong  c ting n - ng Hoan ni.</p>\n<p>					<article class=\"article-related clearfix cms-relate\">                            <figure class=\"thumb\">                              <img src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/170x123/uploaded/2021/yfqfr/2021_03_20/p4anhchinhlpjw_pgod.jpg\" alt=\"TP.HCM quyt lit x l vi phm ting n\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/yfqfr/2021_03_20/p4anhchinhlpjw_pgod.jpg\"/>                            </figure>&#13;\n<header>&#13;\nTP.HCM quyt lit x l vi phm ting n&#13;\n</header>&#13;\n<p>(PLO)- TP.HCM s m t cao im x l ting n, tp trung t nay n cui nm nhm x l trit  v m bo khng xy ra vic vi phm ting n trong khu dn c.</p>&#13;\n</article>				 				</p>\n\n</div><script>(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) return;\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v2.21&appId=178366485681696\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));</script><script>\n!function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)\n{if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?\nn.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};\nif(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version=\'2.0\';\nn.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;\nt.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];\ns.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, document,\'script\',\n\'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js\');\nfbq(\'init\', \'1739154382882652\');\nfbq(\'track\', \'PageView\');\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://plo.vn/thoi-su/tphcm-khoanh-vung-kiem-tra-dot-xuat-hung-than-karaoke-973650.html\">PLO.VN</a>', 'TP.HCM: Khoanh vng, kim tra t xut \'hung thn\' karaoke | Thi s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tp-hcm-khoanh-vung-kiem-tra-dot-xuat-hung-than-karaoke-thoi-su', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:30:44', '2021-03-20 11:30:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tp-hcm-khoanh-vung-kiem-tra-dot-xuat-hung-than-karaoke-thoi-su/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(902, 1, '2021-03-20 11:31:43', '2021-03-20 11:31:43', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<div>nh gi v t tp trung u tin ,HLV Troussier cho bit ng hi lng v tinh thn tp luyn v thi  chuyn cn, n lc vt kh ca ton b s cu th c gi. ng ni;  H n t nhiu CLB khng c mt ti vng chung kt U.19 nh Viettel, Nam nh,  Nng, Long An, Hu, TP.HCM. Thng th tm l ca nhng cu th khng gp mt  sn chi cao nht ca la tui s khng tt v ngh rng c n lc cng kh c BHL i tuyn  mt n. Nhng h  chng minh iu ngc li, cho thy mt  thc chuyn nghip rt cao. Tt c u th hin kht khao v lun c gng  vt qua chnh mnh. Chnh v vy ti rt phn khch khi nhn thy h  nut gio n ca ti mt cch chn chu, thm ch c khi bui tp ko di n 23 gi, cc cu th u say sa tp, chng c biu hin g l mt mi hay than vn c..</div>\n<p>ng Troussier cng by t v chuyn mn phn ln cu th cho thy kh nng x l tt,  thc chin thut kh trong cc bui tp cng nh trong trn u tp ha CLB hng nht Ph ng 0-0 vo chiu qua. Vic thi u trc mt CLB gii hng nht ng nhin l th thch khng h d dng. Do vy ti  t chc i vi s tp trung vo kh nng phng ng. Vic khng  thua bn no c th xem l kt qu tt. Quan trng l thng qua trn u ny ti mun xem cc cu th c phi hp vi nhau tt hay khng, c lin kt thng tin vi nhau tt hay khng. Cc cu th nhn chung  th hin c mt i hnh c s on kt, c s thng nht v mt t chc\", ng Troussier ni.</p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"HLV Troussier i ct tm vng ti vng chung kt gii v ch U.19 quc gia - nh 1\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/quangtuyen/2021_03_20/troussier4_ipzd.jpg\" caption=\"HLV Troussier i ct tm vng ti vng chung kt gii v ch U.19 quc gia - nh 1\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>HLV Troussier ch o trn sn </p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Ni v im cn hn ch ca la cu th U.19, ng Troussier nhn vai: D nhin cn phi un nn nhiu. Nhng thng qua c xt vi nhng i th gi r nh Ph ng, U.19 Vit Nam chc chn tch ly nhiu kinh nghim. T cch p t th trn, kh nng tranh chp, chuyn trng thi t phng ng sang phn cng, cch t chc bc lt, cch khai thc v x l c hi ghi bn u s c ch trng nhiu hn trong thi gian ti.</p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"HLV Troussier i ct tm vng ti vng chung kt gii v ch U.19 quc gia - nh 2\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/quangtuyen/2021_03_20/troussier3_uiru.jpg\" caption=\"HLV Troussier i ct tm vng ti vng chung kt gii v ch U.19 quc gia - nh 2\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>U.19 Vit Nam (o ) trong trn ha Ph ng</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>Sng nay ton i  c bui tp hi phc ti phng gym ca Lin on bng  Vit Nam, sau  c tr v CLB v kt thc giai on 1 ca t tp trung ln ny. t tp trung ln sau d kin s din ra t ngy 16/4 n 25/4 ti. HLV Troussier cho bit cui tun sau ng s i Bnh Dng  bt u chin dch d khn vng chung kt gii bng  v ch U.19 quc gia   i ct tm vng t 12 i bng vi nhiu cu th cht lng ca Sng Lam Ngh An Hong Anh Gia Lai, H Ni, PVF, Hc vin NutiiFood, ng Thp, Bnh Dng, Qung Nam, Si Gn FC, Khnh Ha, Bnh nh, An Giang. ng Troussier cho bit ng s gi khong 40 cu th t vng chung kt U.19 cho t tp trung th 2 v la ny s l nng ct  chun b cho gii v ch U.18 ng Nam  d kin vo thng 7 ti.</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center