(905, 1, '2021-03-20 11:32:46', '2021-03-20 11:32:46', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/2/quatai1-1614667409360483736969.jpg\" id=\"img_fc1cf190-7b1f-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" w=\"1920\" h=\"1280\" alt=\"Cng an k Lk cm n Tui Tr Online phn nh xe ma lng hnh trn quc l 26 - nh 1.\" title=\"Cng an k Lk cm n Tui Tr Online phn nh xe ma lng hnh trn quc l 26 - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"fc1cf190-7b1f-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/2/quatai1-1614667409360483736969.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Theo Cng an tnh k Lk, trong thi gian qua  x l hng chc phng tin ch ma vi phm do ch qu kh, qu ti - nh: TH TH</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Lin quan vCSGT  ra qun, xe ch ma cng knh vn tung honh trn quc l 26, ngy 20-3, Cng an tnh k Lk  c vn bn ghi nhn, cm n <i>Tui Tr Online</i> v  thng tin v tnh trng ny, gp phn tuyn truyn  m bo trt t an ton giao thng trn a bn tnh.<br/></p><p class=\"\">Theo Cng an tnh k Lk,<span style=\"\">tuyn quc l 26 l con ng huyt mch  vn chuyn ma nguyn liu v cc Nh my ma ng 333 (Ea Kar, k Lk) v mt s nh my ti Khnh Ha.</span></p><p class=\"\"> to iu kin thun li nht cho ngi dn khai thc, thu hoch v vn chuyn ma nguyn liu n cc nh my, Cng an tnh  ch ng trong cng tc tuyn truyn nhm m bo trt t an ton giao thng trn ton tuyn quc l 26.  </p><p class=\"\">Bn cnh , cng an tnh cng cht chn nhng tuyn ng huyt mch, quan trng  ngn chn tnh trng qu kh, qu ti.  </p><p class=\"\">V vy trong qu 1-2021, trn tuyn quc l 26 Cng an tnh k Lk  pht hin, lp bin bn 1.007 trng hp vi phm v trt t an ton giao thng, tm gi 287 phng tin cc loi.  </p><p class=\"\">Tnh t ngy 24-2-2021 n nay, lc lng cnh st giao thng  pht hin, lp bin bn 41 trng hp t ti ch ma qu kh, qu ti gy nguy him, mt an ton giao thng.  </p><p class=\"\">Tuy vy, Cng an tnh k Lk tha nhn vn cha th ngn chn trit  vi phm ca cc xe ch ma trong ma cao im va qua.</p><p class=\"\">Nguyn nhn l do mt s li xe c tnh trnh n lc lng tun tra, kim sot. Thm ch khi thy t tun tra th cho ngi theo st hot ng  thng bo cho cc phng tin ngng hot ng, ch thi im giao ca hoc i tun tra tuyn ng khc mi chy tip.  </p><p class=\"\">Mt s ch phng tin, li xe v li nhun chu p lc phi vn chuyn trong giai on cao im  trnh hao ht, tn tht sau thu hoch nn c  vi phm cc quy nh v ti trng  </p><p class=\"\">Cng an tnh k Lk cam kt thi gian ti, lc lng cnh st giao thng tnh s kin quyt x l nghim cc vi phm, bo m an ton giao thng trn tuyn quc l 26, ng thi tng cng lc lng, phng tin, thit b  tun tra, kim sot nhm pht hin v x l nghim cc hnh vi vi phm v hot ng kinh doanh vn ti.  </p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/cong-an-dak-lak-cam-on-tuoi-tre-online-phan-anh-xe-mia-long-hanh-tren-quoc-lo-26-20210320165907109.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Cng an k Lk cm n Tui Tr Online phn nh xe ma lng hnh trn quc l 26', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cong-an-dak-lak-cam-on-tuoi-tre-online-phan-anh-xe-mia-long-hanh-tren-quoc-lo-26', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:32:46', '2021-03-20 11:32:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/cong-an-dak-lak-cam-on-tuoi-tre-online-phan-anh-xe-mia-long-hanh-tren-quoc-lo-26/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(906, 1, '2021-03-20 11:33:44', '2021-03-20 11:33:44', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"content-id\">\n\n                                        \n                                        \n                                        <div class=\"content-news-detail old-news\" data-field=\"body\">\n                                            <p>Theo bo<i>The Health Times</i> (thuc Nhn dn Nht bo ca ng Cng sn Trung Quc), n y t k trn h Liu. C tnglm vic trong khu vc cch ly ca mt bnh vin  TP Ty An t hm 4-3, chu trch nhimthu thp mu ca nhng ngi b cch ly  xt nghim Covid-19.<br/></p><p>Trung Quc bo co trng hp ca c Liu cch y 2 ngykhin y tr thnh trng hp mc Covid-19 u tin ti a phngk t hm 14-2.The Health Times cho bit c Liu mc Covid-19 do \"v tnh tip xc khi  trong khu vc cch ly ca bnh vin\".</p><p>ng ni l n y t ny  c tim  2 liu vc-xin Covid-19 trong khong thi gian cui thng 1 ti u thng 2.<br/></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img id=\"img_f4a8df00-8957-11eb-a767-35c3c2bdff19\" w=\"670\" h=\"377\" alt=\"Trung Quc: Y t tim  2 liu vc-xin b mc Covid-19 - nh 1.\" title=\"Trung Quc: Y t tim  2 liu vc-xin b mc Covid-19 - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"f4a8df00-8957-11eb-a767-35c3c2bdff19\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" src=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/2021/3/20/1-16162296410191969041959.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Mt n y t tim vc-xin cho mt ngi n ng ti TP Nam Thng. nh: AP</p></div></div><p>Cu chuyn gia dch t hc ti Trung tm Kim sot v Phng nga Dch bnh Trung Quc (CDC)Zeng Guangni rng t l bo v ca vc-xin \"khng phi 100%\" v \"tng i an ton\" thay v \"an ton tuyt i\".<br/></p><p>\"T l hiu qu ca vc-xin ni a trong vic ngn nga cc ca bnh nng  Trung Quc l hn 90% v t l bo v tng th l hn 70%. Cc bnh vin iu tr Covid-19 l nhng khu vc c nguy c cao, trong  cc nhn vin y t  tim vc-xin khng loi tr kh nng b ly nhim\" - ngZeng tha nhn.</p><p>t nht 33 nhn vin lm vic trong khu vc cch ly vi c Liu cho kt qu xt nghim axit nucleic m tnh. H ang c cch ly v quan st y t tp trung.<i>The Health Times</i>khng ni r c Liu c tim loi vc-xin no.<br/></p><p>Trung Quc hin c 4 loi vc-xin Covid-19 ni a  s dng cho cng chng. Trong , vc-xin do CanSino Biologics Inc (CanSinoBIO) v Vin Sn phm Sinh hc V Hn - chi nhnh ca Tp on Dc phm Quc gia Trung Quc (Sinopharm) - sn xut  c ph duyt vo thng 2 nm nay.<br/></p><p>Ngoi ra, vc-xin caSinovac Biotechc ph duyt hi thng trc v vc-xin th t caSinopharmc ph duyt t nm ngoi.Mt loi vc-xin th nm do Vin Vi sinh vt thuc Hc vin Khoa hc Trung Quc (IMCAS) pht trin cng  c ph duyt  s dng khn cp  Trung Quc, theo thng bo ca IMCAS hm 15-3.</p>\n                                            <!-- B&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u Dable / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                            \n                                            <!-- K&#7871;t th&uacute;c / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                        </div>\n\n                                        <span class=\"author fr\" data-field=\"author\">&#13;\n                                            Phm Ngha</span>\n                                        \n                                        <div class=\"sharemxh bottomshare\">\n                                            \n                                            \n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"print\">\n                                                &#13;\n                                                    <img src=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/web_images/icon-print-3.png\" class=\"iconprintdetailbot\"/>&#13;\n                                                \n                                            </div>\n                                            \n                    