(908, 1, '2021-03-20 11:35:24', '2021-03-20 11:35:24', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><p>Khi ng cch y 20 nm nhng hin d n ci to rch Xuyn Tm, di 6,2 km, cha trin khai khin con knh ngy cng  nhim, hng nghn h dn b nh hng.</p><div id=\"\">\n<p class=\"Normal\">Nm 2001, khi ang b a con th hai, ng Nguyn Thanh c, 51 tui,  phng 2, qun Bnh Thnh, thy cn b phng cm s sch, thc o, i li dc hm rng gn 3 m trc ca nh. H ch tr, nh du hnh lang, ghi chp vo s ri ri i. Nhn cnh tng ny, ng c v c xm hn chc nc nh h hi v trc  nghe bo i ni rch s c ci to. Nhng t  n nay, d n ch nm trn giy, ngi dn hai bn rch phi sng trong  nhim.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-6781-1616130261.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=mz-A8WyJTEs5twLruP3gnQ\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"795\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.225165562914%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-6781-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Q371uqLfqagUsH5twNmTMw 1x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-6781-1616130261.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=KLWzQd04BVbD30XHyex1Yg 1.5x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-6781-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Ggu1HAojxBmOIB06cVxx8w 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"ng c ng nhn con knh  nhim, ngi dn sng hai bn x cht thi xung knh. nh: H An.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-6781-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Q371uqLfqagUsH5twNmTMw\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">ng Nguyn Thanh c ng nhn con knh  nhim. nh: <em>H An.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">ng c k nhng nm 1990, dng nc rch Xuyn Tm trong xanh, nhn thy tn y. Hi nh, ng cng l bn quanh xm bi men theo b knh tm mt. Chiu n, nhm tr cho ghe i hi da, by chim ti tn khu vc Cu Sn. Hai bn dng knh cy xanh r ro, gi thi lng lng mt ri.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Dng knh bt u  nhim khi ngi dn chuyn n sng ngy cng ng. Nhng cn nh \"chng nng\" c dng ln nm xiu vo, bn trn quy tn hoen r, mc nt. Nh v sinh, ni git gi, nu nng... c ngi dn tn dng mi khong khng ci ni,  mi cht thi xung knh. \"Cm gic con knh b thu hp dn bi nh ca, rc thi\", ng c ni.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Rc  xung knh ch yu chai l, o qun c, xc ng vt... Khi nc rng, mt knh tr y l nhiu vt dng nm ln trong lp bn en kt. Cht thi t nh v sinh cc gia nh x thng xung nc. Gia tri tra nng, mi x u bc ln nng nc. Cn nh ca ng c thm ch khng tr ca s  trnh mi hi nhng vn khng ngn c.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Cch nh ng c bng cy cu lin phng, b Nm Hng,  phng 15, qun Bnh Thnh, cm cy qut tay ngi trc hm gia ci nng 37  C gia bui tra. Khng chu ni oi bc trong cn nh rng 45 m2 lp mi tn, hn tun nay b Hng ly con hm nh trc nh lm ni trnh nng. Gn 20 nm t khi nghe thng tin con knh ci to, b v c xm vui mng nhng d n nm im, khng thy ng tnh.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-1-6102-1616130261.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=ejM8m85k_3mo5yJTTUWePQ\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"800\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-1-6102-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=cRtTAzln8o3t3CkcHKq_eg 1x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-1-6102-1616130261.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=e85TKwHujG-EcfLEbZ-RpQ 1.5x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-1-6102-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=qdKgqc5RGPrxmM1H0GqrhQ 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Ngi dn sng hai bn x rc thi xung dng knh. nh: H An.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-1-6102-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=cRtTAzln8o3t3CkcHKq_eg\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Ngi dn sng hai bn x rc thi xung dng knh. nh: <em>H An.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Ngi ph n gn 70 tui sng bn dng knh t trc nm 1975 k, con knh tng rt p v sch, c bn  n a hc sinh ti trng. Bui chiu b con thng ra b knh ngi hng mt, tr chuyn. Ri rc thi t ni khc  v, ngi dn thy  nhim nn c vt rc xung v ngh dng nc  bn sn, c gi gn cng kh thay i c.</p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Dn  y ch yu lm ngh lao ng t do, ngi bun bn t ni khc ti thu,  thc gn gi mi trng cha cao nn con knh ngy mt  nhim\", b k v mong mun c sm di di v khng chu ni mi hi bc ln khi nc rng. C thi im con rch c bo ch miu t l ni \" nhim nht thnh ph\", thng c i biu a ra cht vn ti k hp HND TP HCM.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Gia nh ng c, b Hng l hai trong s hn 1.600 h dn b nh hng trong d n ci to rch Xuyn Tm c UBND TP HCM ph duyt t thng 5/2002, giao Khu qun l ng sng (thuc S Giao thng Vn ti) thc hin vi kinh ph khong 123 t ng thi im . Tuy nhin d n sau  khng c thc hin.</p><p class=\"Normal\">n thng 8/2015, S K hoch v u t kin ngh UBND thnh ph ph duyt d n mi, kinh ph ln ti 5.100 t ng, thc hin trong 5 nm. Con rch thay v no vt, ci to, lm ng hai bn nh d n trc, s c u t thm khu  th thng minh thay th khu nh  chut... Nghe thuyt trnh nhiu ngi dn khp khi mng thm v mi trng sng s ci thin, nhng sau  d n c nh gi khng kh thi nn cha thc hin.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-4-5320-1616130261.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=pIefFagjDdPCn_dk2SxXkQ\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"760\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 63.291139240506%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-4-5320-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=ffI9ZzCDsn9p1E2ZZuGa2g 1x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-4-5320-1616130261.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=tDU36-dUv8NdNDIZaRTSqg 1.5x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-4-5320-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=qyEh6SrX9N3ipUizweJ56Q 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Rch Xuyn Tm nhn t trn cao. nh: Qunh Trn.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/rach-xuyen-tam-4-5320-1616130261.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=ffI9ZzCDsn9p1E2ZZuGa2g\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Rch Xuyn Tm chy qua qun Bnh Thnh nhn t trn cao. nh: <em>Qunh Trn.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Mi y, cng trnh ci to rch Xuyn Tm mt ln na c khi ng khi Ban qun l d n u t xy dng h tng  th TP HCM (ch u t) cho bit h s  xut u t d n  hon tt. Ban s trnh HND thnh ph thng qua ch trng u t trong k hp ti.</p><p class=\"Normal\">D n c kinh ph 9.300 t ng, no vt tuyn rch Xuyn Tm di 6,2 km t knh Nhiu Lc  Th Ngh n sng Vm Thut cng 3 tuyn nhnh di gn 2 km gm nhnh cu Sn, Bnh Triu v Bnh Li; lm ng 2 bn; h thng thu gom nc thi trn phm vi 700 ha... Kinh ph xy dng c tnh 4.500 t ng, cn li l tin gii phng mt bng.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Theo ng Nguyn Hong Anh Dng, Ph gim c Ban qun l d n u t xy dng h tng  th TP HCM, d n s khi cng v hon thnh trong giai on 2021-2025. Tin  d n nhanh hay chm ph thuc rt ln vo vic n b gii phng mt bng cc h dn b nh hng hai bn tuyn rch.</p><p class=\"Normal\">V pha a phng, ng H Phng, Ph ch tch UBND qun Bnh Thnh cho bit, trong khi ch i ngun vn trin khai d n,  gim bt  nhim, qun giao cc phng t chc vt rc, khi thng nhng v tr  nhim nng. Tuy nhin, lng rc qu ln, dng knh tri di nhiu km nn kh lm thng xuyn v ngun kinh ph hn ch.</p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Chng ti s gn camera gim st, vn ng ngi dn khng x rc ra knh\", ng Phng ni v cho bit a phng mun d n sm trin khai  tuyn knh c hi sinh, p ng mong mi ca ngi dn gn 20 nm ch i.</p><p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong>H An</strong></p>\n</div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/dan-sai-gon-20-nam-cho-cai-tao-rach-xuyen-tam-4247516.html\">VNEXPRESS.NET</a>', 'Dn Si Gn 20 nm ch ci to rch Xuyn Tm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dan-sai-gon-20-nam-cho-cai-tao-rach-xuyen-tam', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:35:24', '2021-03-20 11:35:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/dan-sai-gon-20-nam-cho-cai-tao-rach-xuyen-tam/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(909, 1, '2021-03-20 11:36:26', '2021-03-20 11:36:26', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/myvihk-1616119416884658185489.jpg\" id=\"img_59da40a0-8857-11eb-a726-f5ee3677901b\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1328\" alt=\"Nng sn M tung chin dch tip cn ngi dng Vit - nh 1.\" title=\"Nng sn M tung chin dch tip cn ngi dng Vit - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"59da40a0-8857-11eb-a726-f5ee3677901b\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/myvihk-1616119416884658185489.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">B Marie C. Damour, tng lnh s M ti TP.HCM, tr ti nu nng vi cc nguyn liu t M -  nh: QUANG NH</p></div></div><p><span style=\"\">Chng trnh \"United Tastes - M v Hoa K\" va c ra mt  TP.HCM, gii thiu thng tin cc sn phm, nguyn liu M v cung cp cc cng thc nu n y sng to m ngi tiu dng c th ch bin ngay ti nh. Cc sn phm nng sn M c tuyn chn t nhng thng hiu tiu biu ca vng min trn khp nc M nh tri cy, tht b, rau c, hi sn...</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Thng </span><span style=\"\">qua website, Facebook, Instagram v YouTube, cc nng sn, c sn M c th tip cn a dng ngi tiu dng Vit Nam bng nhng gi  v cch nu mn n mi m, hp dn.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Ngoi ra cn c nhng cu chuyn v thng tin v sn phm M c nui trng v ch bin  ngi tiu dng Vit c th hiu c cht lng v  an ton ca thc phm M.</span></p><p>Theo b Marie C. Damour - tng lnh s M ti TP.HCM, giao thng v nng nghip l mt phn quan trng trong quan h song phng gia M v Vit Nam vi mc tng trng ng k trong 25 nm qua.</p><p>Kt thc nm 2020, M  xut khu 3,7 t USD cc sn phm nng nghip sang Vit Nam, a Vit Nam tr thnh th trng xut khu th 7 ca M v sn phm nng nghip.<span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p>\"Khu v ca ngi Vit Nam rt tinh t, ngi tiu dng rt tinh  nhn bit nhng sn phm cht lng, bao gm cc sn phm n t M, vn c  an ton v gi tr dinh dng cao. Nhiu sn phm M  tr nn ph bin vi ngi tiu dng Vit Nam\", b Marie C. Damour by t.<br/></p><p><span style=\"\">T cc sn phm u, thc n chn nui, n nay nng sn M sang Vit Nam ngy cng a dng hn.ng Robert Hanson, trng phng nng nghip, i s qun M ti Vit Nam, cho bit nm ngoi, mt hng blueberry M chnh thc c php nhp khu trc tip vo Vit Nam v  c tng trng ng ghi nhn.</span><br/></p><p>Mi y, ht cao lng, mt loi ng cc ph bin  M, cng va c cp php vo Vit Nam v ang ch khai thc th trng tim nng  y trong xu hng n lnh mnh, b dng.</p><p>Hin nay sn phm nng sn M ch yu phn phi qua knh bn l hin i hoc h thng cc nh hng, khch sn cao cp.<br/></p><p><span style=\"\">\"Tng lp c thu nhp trung bnh ngy cng tng ti Vit Nam v h s dng mng x hi khng ch  theo di m cn nh hnh xu th.</span><span style=\"\">Vi hn 49 triu ngi s dng mng x hi, chng trnh mun truyn ti nhng cu chuyn v thc phm v nng nghip M ti cng chng mun tip cn v ha nhp vn ha a dng trn th gii\",</span><span style=\"\">ng Robert Hanson ni.</span></p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/nong-san-my-tung-chien-dich-tiep-can-nguoi-dung-viet-20210319083338667.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Nng sn M tung chin dch tip cn ngi dng Vit', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nong-san-my-tung-chien-dich-tiep-can-nguoi-dung-viet', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:36:26', '2021-03-20 11:36:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/nong-san-my-tung-chien-dich-tiep-can-nguoi-dung-viet/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
