(913, 1, '2021-03-20 11:39:06', '2021-03-20 11:39:06', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/photo-1-16161375676061413849287-1616142067127171754712.png\" id=\"img_7a935ea0-887d-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" w=\"675\" h=\"905\" alt=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: ng c nhng  ch cho tt c mi hon cnh - nh 1.\" title=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: ng c nhng  ch cho tt c mi hon cnh - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"172f55c0-8888-11eb-882d-d15eabac42b1\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/photo-1-16161375676061413849287-1616142067127171754712.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Ngh s lang thang Tun \"ln\"</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Nh l thng, sau vi bi bolero cng dm ly x , va h Hi Triu bng chc thnh ni tm s ca ti v anh, nhng k lng du, cng ly thnh ph ny lm ni tr ng.</p><p class=\"\"><b>Thng hiu Tun \"ln\"</b></p><p class=\"\">Tun \"ln\" sinh ra trc nm 1975, trong mt con hm nh G Vp, c tui th lang thang cc i l Nguyn Hu - L Li  kim sng v hc mt cc ngn n ca nhng ngh s lang thang. Rit ri am m, li c tri ph cho ging ht hi kh nng khi sng, rt hp vi nhng nhc phm v lnh. </p><p class=\"\">Anh li c tr nh bm sinh nn thuc rt nhiu bi, v vy theo thi gian, Tun \"ln\" tr thnh mt \"thng hiu\" ca cc qun m  h ph Si Gn, nht l cc t im ng dn nhu khuya nh Nguyn Trung Trc, Hi Triu hay Hm Nghi. </p><p class=\"\">Ting n ca anh nghe l, hi hng \"phi\" nn n gi vi nhc bolero v khng gian va h, m nhiu bc ti danh hc hnh nhc vin ra cng phi tm tc khen thm khi nhn bn tay kh sn mit trn phm g, ngn tay iu luyn lt trn dy to nn nhng m sc bp bng, ha quyn vi ging ht nha nha kh nng ca Tun. </p><p class=\"\">Mi ln ra y, thng ti s ngi nghe anh n dm bn nhc quen,  thy mt Si Gn rt khc thng hin v di chn cao c Bitexco hin i.   c nim vui, c ni nh, c bun thng, c day dt, c c nhng git nc mt ri cho nhng mnh i. </p><p class=\"\">Nhng bi ht mt thi chin tranh c Tun \"ln\" ht li trong mt thnh ph ha bnh, hin i, vn minh, c s hng ng ca nhiu tri tim  vng min Trung Nam Bc, sao m ngha tnh n th. </p><p class=\"\">u l con ng xa em i? u l ni mnh trng non tn trn h ph? u l qun na khuya n m hi khi cho m trung nin t tp trt tm t?  u cng c, nhng phi  trn mnh t ny. </p><p class=\"\">Thnh ph thn thng m rng vng tay cho m ngi l th, lu lc k h, n y dng bc nhn qu hng. Ti thm ngh, Si Gn khng ch l ca ring Tun \"ln\", ca ch T c Tm, ca d t m Nm, m Si Gn cn l ca ti, ca bn. D n sau, nhng tnh yu cho mnh t ny, chc ai  km hn ai?</p><p class=\"\">Nhng lc ngi trm mnh nghe ting n ca anh Tun \"ln\" ngm ngi bay chm chm ln hng me, ha vo khi thuc lng du, thch th v cng, thy nhng m Si Gn tht p.</p><p class=\"\"><b>Ting lng m </b></p><p class=\"\">Nhng ngh s lang thang lm cho thnh ph thm n tng vi du khch. D vy, cuc sng ca h tht bp bnh. Nh Tun \"ln\" d c gia nh nhng nh phi i mn, hng thng gp cho ch nh tin sinh hot, c bn ming n trng c vo cy n. Hm no tri ma hoc m nm nh l coi nh i. </p><p class=\"\">Thi thong c khch \"sp\" mi c nm by trm cho vi ting ng h n ch, cn khng c ti khn c cng ch c vi trm. Th nhng cng l tm n, v ging ca ca anh vn cn sc ht, v tha nhn trc sau vn cn trng ting n, nn cng cn thy vui vui. </p><p class=\"\">Gp ti ln no anh cng ci vui v, dng mp mp ln cn khng ln i u c. Ti mi n bt ph anh thng t chi, ni ti anh khng n.</p><p class=\"\">\"Mt cuc i di ngn c bao lu, m  nim vui gin on? - anh tm s - Anh tng tri qua cuc chin tranh, tng bit n ng la xanh la , tng lang thang thuc tng vin  lt va h, nn anh hiu gi tr ca nhng m vui. Gp ngi hiu ting n ca mnh, ta nh ng tri m tri k, u c quan trng chuyn tin bc. Thnh thong gp nhau, ng h anh l qu ri\". </p><p class=\"\">Ti nghe m xc ng. Ta nh c li c chuyn xa B Nha vi T K trn ph ma bay. Con ngi ny m cng ngha kh ho sng nh vy . M u phi ring anh, c l c Si Gn ny l vy, nu thc s l ngi Si Gn. </p><p class=\"\">Khng bn n tiu tit, chi ti bn, nhit tnh, y s v t. V su bn trong l mt s yu thng nhau n l, d l gia nhng con ngi khng cng mt xut thn.</p><p class=\"\">\"Tri cn thng th cn cho anh sc khe,  cn i ht kim tin. B con cng thng anh, nh em vy , th anh mi c tin  gp tr tin nh,  nui con. Thi chc em nm mi khe nghen, vn s nh , pht t!\".</p><p class=\"\">Anh tm bit ti ri i. Ti nhn theo bng anh bc v pha ng Hm Nghi. m  su nhng khch vn cn dm bn ang n ung. Ti thy anh ging nh cnh chim m ang xoi cnh gom tng cht thc n  nui t ca mnh. Mit mi. Nhn ni. N lc. Hi sinh. Ti tin chc iu may mn v tt p s n vi anh, nh iu anh tng tm nim.</p><p class=\"\">\"Si Gn ng c nhng y bao dung,  ch cho tt c mi hon cnh. Ch cn mnh c gng, Sn !\".</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\" data-back=\"#f2ecdd\" style=\"background-color: rgb(242, 236, 221); border-color: rgb(242, 34, 34); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\" data-border=\"#f22222\"><p class=\"\"><b><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"/>Mong tip tc nhn c bi vit ca bn c</b></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption active\" type=\"Photo\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/photo-1-16161376799301304584166.jpg\" id=\"img_bd9525d0-887d-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" w=\"586\" h=\"526\" alt=\"photo-1\" title=\"photo-1\" rel=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/photo-1-16161376799301304584166.jpg\" photoid=\"bd9525d0-887d-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/photo-1-16161376799301304584166.jpg\"/></div></div><p class=\"\">Tnh n ngy 19-3, a ch email saigon@tuoitre.com.vn ca cuc thi vit \"Si Gn bao dung<span> </span>- TP.HCM ngha tnh\"  nhn c 188 email ca bn c khp mi min t nc cng nh  nc ngoi gi nh, bi vit v d thi.</p><p class=\"\">Bo <i>Tui Tr</i> trn trng cm n s nhit tnh hng ng cuc thi v mong tip tc nhn c nhng bi vit t bn c.</p><p class=\"\"><b>Ngy 10-3: </b>inh Thnh Trung, Tuan Bui Thanh, Trng Trn Xun, Tam TranVan, B A, Bch Ngc, Ngoc Tam Dinh