(917, 1, '2021-03-20 11:40:09', '2021-03-20 11:40:09', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/20210319-tto-psn-anh-1-canh-nguoi-dan-nha-trang-khanh-hoa-cho-nhan-gao-cuu-tro-vi-dich-benh-covid-19-vao-thang-4-2020-anh-phansongngan-16161283450671602632357.jpg\" id=\"img_dc9c2170-886b-11eb-81c3-237203d6ead3\" w=\"1017\" h=\"626\" alt=\"Khnh Ha tnh chi 140 t tim min ph vc xin COVID-19 cho dn - nh 1.\" title=\"Khnh Ha tnh chi 140 t tim min ph vc xin COVID-19 cho dn - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"dc9c2170-886b-11eb-81c3-237203d6ead3\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/20210319-tto-psn-anh-1-canh-nguoi-dan-nha-trang-khanh-hoa-cho-nhan-gao-cuu-tro-vi-dich-benh-covid-19-vao-thang-4-2020-anh-phansongngan-16161283450671602632357.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Nhiu ngi dn ngho  TP Nha Trang (Khnh Ha) ch nhn go cu tr, v kh khn do dch bnh COVID-19 (thng 4-2020) - nh: PHAN SNG NGN</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Chiu nay 19-3, </span><span style=\"\">theo ng Trn Ngc Thanh - ch tch y ban Mt trn T quc Vit Nam tnh Khnh Ha, y ban Mt trn T quc</span>Vit Nam<span style=\"\">tnh s t chc vn  ng cc t chc, c nhn ng hnh vi tnh, </span><span style=\"\">c kh nng ng gp</span><span style=\"\"> nhm b li mt phn ngn sch mua vc xin COVID-19  tim min ph cho dn, theo k hoch  xut t UBND tnh Khnh Ha  c Ban Thng v Tnh y thng nht ch trng thc hin.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">ng Nguyn Tn Tun - ph b th Tnh y, ch tch UBND tnh Khnh Ha - cho bit k hoch mua v tim min ph </span><span style=\"\">vc</span><span style=\"\"> xin COVID-19 cho dn Khnh Ha, t 18 tui tr ln, d kin s c bt u thc hin t thng 6-2021.</span><br/></p><p class=\"\">Khnh Ha ang c khong 1 triu dn t 18 tui tr ln. D tnh tng s tin mua vc xin  tim min ph cho ton b dn s va nu khong 200 t ng.</p><p class=\"\">Khnh Ha l mt trong cc a phng c ng gp ngn sch cho trung ng nn theo quy nh s c Chnh ph h tr li 30% tng s tin mua vc xin  tim cho dn. S tin cn li tnh phi t lo,  mua vc xin nh va nu khong 140 t ng.</p><p class=\"\">Va qua, tnh  quyt nh khng t chc Festival bin Nha Trang - Khnh Ha trong nm 2021 theo nh k l nhm thc hin nghim vic phng nga dch bnh COVID-19, m bo an ton cho ngi dn v du khch. Nhng  cng cn do vic thu ngn sch ca tnh  b st gim rt nhiu, v nh hng dch bnh COVID-19 ko di t nm 2020 n nay. </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/20210318-tto-psn-2-bai-bien-nha-trang-va-nguoi-dan-muu-sinh-khi-dich-benh-covid-19-anh-phansongngan-16160583483761569743632.jpg\" id=\"img_db94e480-87c4-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" w=\"1024\" h=\"594\" alt=\"Khnh Ha tnh chi 140 t tim min ph vc xin COVID-19 cho dn - nh 2.\" title=\"Khnh Ha tnh chi 140 t tim min ph vc xin COVID-19 cho dn - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"db94e480-87c4-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/20210318-tto-psn-2-bai-bien-nha-trang-va-nguoi-dan-muu-sinh-khi-dich-benh-covid-19-anh-phansongngan-16160583483761569743632.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Bi bin Nha Trang vng khch du lch v dch bnh COVID-19, ngi bn hng mu sinh cng chu cnh kh khn theo - nh: PHAN SNG NGN</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Tuy nhin, theo ng Tun, \"vic tim min ph vc xin  gip ngi dn trong tnh phng nga, gp phn m bo an ton trc dch bnh COVID-19 l mc tiu  c tnh thng nht u tin hng u\".<br/></p><p class=\"\">ng thi, \" cng l cch gp phn gi cho mi trng du lch ca tnh an ton, thn thin trc dch bnh COVID-19,  du khch trong v ngoi nc an tm khi n du lch Nha Trang - Khnh Ha\".</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://dulich.tuoitre.vn/khanh-hoa-tinh-chi-140-ti-tiem-mien-phi-vac-xin-covid-19-cho-dan-20210319115613247.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Khnh Ha tim min ph vc xin COVID-19 cho dn, gip du lch an ton, hi phc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'khanh-hoa-tiem-mien-phi-vac-xin-covid-19-cho-dan-giup-du-lich-an-toan-hoi-phuc', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:40:09', '2021-03-20 11:40:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/khanh-hoa-tiem-mien-phi-vac-xin-covid-19-cho-dan-giup-du-lich-an-toan-hoi-phuc/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
