(921, 1, '2021-03-20 11:42:25', '2021-03-20 11:42:25', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh cho bit, ngy 16/3, khi sang nh hng xm chi, c T. b con ch (ging Bully nng hn 30kg) lao vo tn cng. Ch N.T.X., con gi c T cho bit, con cho khng c xch.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C T. nhp vin trong tnh trng vt thng dp nt cng tay tri, vt thng hm mt phc tp.  iu tr, cc bc s phi ct ct 1/3 phn di cnh tay tri, phu thut ct lc, x l vt thng hm mt phc tp.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 3 ngy phu thut, tnh trng sc khe ca bnh nhn n nh, tnh to, c th giao tip vi nhn vin y t. Bnh nhn tip tc c theo di v iu tr ti khoa Phu thut Chn thng chung, Bnh vin Hu ngh Vit c.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><img alt=\"C b 87 tui b ch 30kg cn nt tay v mt - 1\" height=\"495\" data-id=\"1548308\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"495\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/cho-cann-09422262.JPG\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"0\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">Bnh nhn vn ang c theo di sau khi b ch cn nguy kch.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngy 14/3, khi sang hng xm chi, chu P.H.C. (9 tui) n t Vnh Phc phi nhp vin do b ch  nh hng xm tn cng cn vo vng kn, gy vt thng dng vt cho bnh nhi.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hin nhiu gia nh vn c thi quen v s thch nui ch  gi nh, lm th cng. Nhng v ch quan ngh ch nh hin, khng cn ngi nn qun l cha st sao dn n nhng hu qu nng n, thm ch c trng hp t vong do ch cn. V vy, ngi dn cn nu cao cnh gic khi tip xc vi ch, mo  trnh nhng trng hp ng tic xy ra.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/cu-ba-87-tuoi-bi-cho-30kg-can-nat-tay-va-mat-ar601829.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'C b 87 tui b ch 30kg cn nt tay v mt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cu-ba-87-tuoi-bi-cho-30kg-can-nat-tay-va-mat', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:42:25', '2021-03-20 11:42:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/cu-ba-87-tuoi-bi-cho-30kg-can-nat-tay-va-mat/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(922, 1, '2021-03-20 11:43:36', '2021-03-20 11:43:36', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B Cng an va a ra d tho ln 2 Thng t quy nh chi tit thi hnh mt s iu ca Lut C tr 2020 (hiu lc t 1-7-2021). Theo d tho thng t ny, c mt s thng tin ng ch  lin quan n ngi dn.<br/>&#13;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Tip nhn h s v tr kt qu ng k c tr</b><br/>&#13;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vic tip nhn h s ng k c tr ca ngi dn c thc hin di hnh thc trc tip ti c quan ng k c tr hoc qua ng bu chnh hoc cng dch v cng. </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vic thng bo v kt qu ng k thng tr, ng k tm tr, gia hn tm tr, khai bo thng tin v c tr, iu chnh thng tin v c tr, tch h, xc nhn thng tin v c tr c thc hin di hnh thc vn bn trc tip hoc gin tip (qua ng bu chnh), tin nhn in t hoc cng dch v cng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Tip nhn v x l thng tin phn nh v c tr</b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi ngi dn c thng tin phn nh v vic c tr th c th thng qua cc knh nh trc tip ti c quan ng k c tr; in thoi, ng dy nng; Hm th gp , hp th in t; Cng dch v cng, Cng thng tin in t Chnh ph, Cng thng tin in t B Cng an v cc hnh thc khc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi tip nhn vc thng tin phn nh ca cng dn, h gia nh, c quan, t chc v c tr th c quan ng k c tr phi ghi li. Trong  th hin r thi gian, a im xy ra, ni dung, din bin lin quan n t chc, c nhn no.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi cng dn, h gia nh, c quan, t chc phn nh thng tin th cn  ngh h cho bit h tn, a ch, s in thoi lin h  c quan ng k, qun l c tr c vn bn tr li khi cn thit.</p>\n<p class=\"item-photo\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/w800/Uploaded/2021/xqeioxdrky/2021_01_04/luat-cu-tru-2020-bo-dang-ky-thuong-tru_iklg.jpg\" alt=\"Nm 2021: S c nhiu thay i v khai bo c tr  - nh 1\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/xqeioxdrky/2021_01_04/luat-cu-tru-2020-bo-dang-ky-thuong-tru_iklg.jpg\" cms-photo-caption=\"Theo  xut mi ca B Cng an, ngi dn c th gi h s v nhn kt qu ng k c tr qua cng dch v cng. nh minh ha\"/><br/>&#13;\n<em class=\"image_caption\">Theo  xut mi ca B Cng an, ngi dn c th gi h s v nhn kt qu ng k c tr qua cng dch v cng. nh minh ha</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Cc trng hp tm thi cha gii quyt th tc thay i ni c tr</b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhng trng hp di y, nu trong thi gian b hn ch quyn t do c tr th tm thi cha c gii quyt th tc thay i ni c tr (tr trng hp c s ng  cho thay i ni c tr bng vn bn ca Ta n, c quan khc c thm quyn  p dng bin php ):</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ngi b c quan, ngi c thm quyn tin hnh t tng p dng bin php cm i khi ni c tr, bin php tm gi, tm giam; ngi b kt n pht t nhng cha c quyt nh thi hnh n hoc  c quyt nh thi hnh n nhng ang ti ngoi hoc c hon chp hnh n, tm nh ch chp hnh n; ngi b kt n pht t c hng n treo ang trong thi gian th thch; ngi ang chp hnh n pht t, cm c tr, qun ch hoc ci to khng giam gi; ngi c tha t trc thi hn c iu kin ang trong thi gian th thch.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ngi ang chp hnh bin php gio dc ti x, phng, th trn, bin php a vo c s gio dc bt buc, a vo c s cai nghin bt buc, a vo trng gio dng; ngi phi chp hnh bin php a vo c s gio dc bt buc, a vo c s cai nghin bt buc, a vo trng gio dng nhng ang c hon chp hnh hoc tm nh ch chp hnh; ngi b qun l trong thi gian lm th tc xem xt, quyt nh p dng bin php x l hnh chnh a vo c s gio dc bt buc, a vo c s cai nghin bt buc, a vo trng gio dng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ngi b cch ly do c nguy c ly lan dch bnh cho cng ng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Cc trng hp khc theo quy nh ca lut...</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>ng k thng tr c yu t nc ngoi</b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Trng hp ngi nc ngoi c nhp quc tch Vit Nam th khi ng k thng tr phi c giy t, ti liu chng minh c quc tch Vit Nam theo quy nh php lut Vit Nam v quc tch.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Nu ngi Vit Nam nh c  nc ngoi cn quc tch Vit Nam c h chiu Vit Nam th phi c giy t xut nhp cnh do c quan c thm quyn ca Vit Nam cp cn gi tr s dng v c du kim chng nhp cnh Vit Nam ca n v kim sot xut nhp cnh. </p>\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ngi Vit Nam nh c  nc ngoi, khng c h chiu Vit Nam cn gi tr s dng,  nhp cnh v ang tm tr ti Vit Nam bng h chiu, giy t c gi tr i li quc t hoc giy t c gi tr thng tr  nc ngoi th phi c thm giy t, ti liu chng minh c quc tch Vit Nam.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Xa ng k thng tr</b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong thi hn 60 ngy, k t ngy c ngi thuc din xo ng k thng tr th i din h gia nh c trch nhim n lm th tc xo ng k thng tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong thi hn ba ngy lm vic, k t ngy nhn c h s hp l th c quan ng k thng tr phi xa tn cng dn trong C s d liu v c tr v s ng k thng tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong thi hn ba ngy lm vic, k t ngy xo ng k thng tr, c quan ng k c tr thng bo cho c quan Cng an lin quan thuc tnh iu chnh h s ng k thng tr trong tng th h s c tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>T</b><b>hng bo lu tr </b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vic thng bo lu tr c thc hin trc tip, bng in thoi, phng tin in t hoc phng tin khc. C quan ng k c tr c trch nhim thng bo a im, a ch mng internet, a ch mng my tnh, s in thoi ni tip nhn thng bo lu tr v hng dn cch thng bo lu tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi gian lu tr tu thuc nhu cu ca cng dn nhng khng qu 30 ngy. Ngi tip nhn thng bo lu tr phi ghi vo s tip nhn lu tr v khng cp gip t chng nhn lu tr cho cng dn.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<table cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border: 1px solid black; background-color: #eee; margin: 5px; border-collapse: collapse;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td style=\"background-color: #eee;\">&#13;\n            <p><b>y quyn ng k c tr</b></p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch h hoc ngi yu cu thc hin cc ni dung v ng k c tr theo quy nh ca Lut C tr c y quyn cho ngi khc thc hin thay; tr trng hp ngi khng c ni thng tr, ni tm tr th khng c y quyn cho ngi khc thc hin.</p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vic y quyn phi lp thnh vn bn, c chng thc theo quy nh ca php lut. Trng hp ngi c y quyn l thnh vin trong h gia nh ca ngi y quyn th vn bn y quyn khng phi chng thc<span style=\"text-align: center;\"/></p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Kim tra c tr</b></p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vic kim tra c tr c tin hnh nh k, t xut, hoc do yu cu phng, chng ti phm, gi gn an ninh, trt t.</p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">i tng kim tra c tr l cng dn, h gia nh, c s cho thu lu tr, c quan ng k, qun l c tr cc cp; c quan, t chc c lin quan n qun l c tr.</p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ni dung kim tra c tr bao gm kim tra vic trin khai v t chc thc hin cc ni dung ng k, qun l c tr; quyn v trch nhim ca cng dn, h gia nh, c quan, t chc; cc ni dung khc theo php lut c tr</p>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">					<article class=\"article-related clearfix cms-relate\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">                            <figure class=\"thumb\">                              <img src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/170x123/uploaded/2021/xqeioxdrky/2021_03_20/luatcutru2020bodangkythuongtruiklg_fnxq.jpg\" alt=\"B Cng an  xut ng k thng tr, tm tr qua mng\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/xqeioxdrky/2021_03_20/luatcutru2020bodangkythuongtruiklg_fnxq.jpg\"/>                            </figure>&#13;\n<header>&#13;\nB Cng an  xut ng k thng tr, tm tr qua mng&#13;\n</header>&#13;\n<p>(PLO)- B Cng an   xut thm mt hnh thc tip nhn h s ng k thng tr, tm tr l ng k qua cng dch v cng.</p>&#13;\n</article>				 				</p>\n\n</div><script>(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) return;\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v2.21&appId=178366485681696\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));</script><script>\n!function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)\n{if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?\nn.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};\nif(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version=\'2.0\';\nn.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;\nt.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];\ns.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, document,\'script\',\n\'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js\');\nfbq(\'init\', \'1739154382882652\');\nfbq(\'track\', \'PageView\');\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://plo.vn/thoi-su/nam-2021-se-co-nhieu-thay-doi-ve-khai-bao-cu-tru-973643.html\">PLO.VN</a>', 'Nm 2021: S c nhiu thay i v khai bo c tr | Thi s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nam-2021-se-co-nhieu-thay-doi-ve-khai-bao-cu-tru-thoi-su', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:43:36', '2021-03-20 11:43:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/nam-2021-se-co-nhieu-thay-doi-ve-khai-bao-cu-tru-thoi-su/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
