(923, 1, '2021-03-20 11:45:41', '2021-03-20 11:45:41', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<div>Vi 2 cuc thi D on kt qu cc trn V-League v Bnh chn i hnh tiu biu sau tng vng u, a phn bn c tham d u chung nhn xt cuc thi vi cch thc chi to s gn gi, st sn nn u mang li s phn khch cho ngi chi. Anh Nguyn Tng, c gi  Q.Bnh Thnh (TP.HCM) nh gi: Cch tnh thi gian v cch tnh im ca cuc thi d on rt chi tit gip cho ngi chi cm thy thoi mi. Nh d on t s v kt qu i thng, ha hoc thua, BTC quy nh kha s sau 15 pht l hp l v trong 15 pht u nhng ai say m bng  nhn cch chi ca 2 i cng c th hnh dung c phn no th trn v kt qu s nh th no. Cn cu th m t s kha s trc 15 pht cng khng sai v Bo Thanh Nin lun cung cp sm i hnh ra sn ca 2 i t trc khong 30 - 45 pht, nn da vo  cng on c phn no cu th c th m t s. Tuy nhin s hay hn nu BTC cho kha gn hn thm mt cht v nhng trn  lc 17 gi, mi ngi thng vo st gi  xem, t online trc nn c rt nhiu ngi khng kp xem i hnh xut pht, xem chn st no s chi. Nu kha s 5 pht trc khi bng ln theo ti s kch thch ngi chi nhiu hn.</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"Si ni cuc thi \'Si ng cng V-League 2021\' - nh 1\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/minhnguyet/2021_03_18/nkh_58502_oupu.jpg\" caption=\"Si ni cuc thi \'Si ng cng V-League 2021\' - nh 1\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Cao Vn Trin liu c ni bt  trn derby TP.HCM  vng 4?</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Cng chung suy ngh, bn V Nguyn Long  ng Nai khen cuc thi gip bn c thm say m V-League, mun chi tt bt buc phi theo di  c 7 trn d c th ch thch mt vi i. Theo anh Long, tnh im tng vng ri cng li thc s l mt cuc ua ho hng gay cn gia bn c. V tnh cht n s xuyn sut t vng ny qua vng khc khin th hng c th o ln bt k lc no. Ngi tm vt ln  vng th 3 va ri khng c ngha s duy tr c u th cho vng tip theo, nht l khi thng 3 cn 2 vng cc k quyt lit na. BTC hin cng s b cho bit s d on c im l 298, trong  d on thng xin ch mi l 15 ngi nn c hi vn chia u cho nhng ngi cha may mn khc.</p>\n<div>Vi cuc thi i hnh tiu biu, cc bn c  so k nhau tng im. Do trc trc k thut, vic cng b kt qu c cht nhm ln khi ci tn H Tn Ti (Bnh nh) b sai h thnh Nguyn Tn Ti dn n kt qu my chm b sai s, gy thc mc cho vi bn c. BTC  xin li v kp thi iu chnh  cho ra kt qu. Nhng phi ni l rt nhiu bn c v qun c 2 trn  sm trc tt nn bnh chn u b st 2 ci tn Trnh Vn Li ca Thanh Ha, ngi  chi rt hay trong trn thng Nam nh v  Merlo ca Si Gn FC  ghi bn quyt nh gip i bng TP.HCM thng SLNA. Do vy khi hi ng bnh chn cng b 11 ci tn trong i hnh tiu biu ch c 1 bn c 11 im, 1 bn khc xp sau c 10 im (sai 1 v tr) a phn cc bn d on ng di 6 v tr tp trung vo nhng ci tn Vn Ton, Qu Ngc Hi, Hng Dng, Xun T, Vn Xun, Hi Huy nhng t ai ch  Bi Tin Dng ca  Nng chi rt hay  vai tr trung v hay th mn Hoi Anh xut sc lm nn lng cc chn st ca TP.HCM.</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"Si ni cuc thi \'Si ng cng V-League 2021\' - nh 2\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/minhnguyet/2021_03_18/nguyencongphuong_10_aotrang_hagl_anhkhahoa021_xkwz.jpg\" caption=\"Si ni cuc thi \'Si ng cng V-League 2021\' - nh 2\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Cng Phng c mong i  xut hin trong i hnh tiu biu</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>Vng 4 V-League s bt u chiu nay, mi cc bn tip tc nhanh tay tham gia tip 2 cuc thi trn Thanh Nin Online (https://m.thanhnien.vn/the-thao/soi-dong-cung-vleague.html)  rinh v nhiu gii thng c gi tr l tin mt v o u ca cc CLB v i tuyn Vit Nam.</div>\n\n<!-- Begin Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n<!-- End Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div><script>\n//window.fbAsyncInit = function() {\n// FB.init({\n// appId : \'288067561729014\',\n// autoLogAppEvents : true,\n// xfbml : true,\n// version : \'v2.10\'\n// });\n// FB.AppEvents.logPageView();\n//};\n(function(d, s, id){\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) {return;}\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src = \"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));\n</script><script>\nwindow.fbAsyncInit = function() {\nFB.init({\nappId : \'288067561729014\',\nautoLogAppEvents : true,\nxfbml : true,\nversion : \'v3.1\'\n});\n};\n(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) { return; }\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src = \"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/the-thao/bong-da-viet-nam/soi-noi-cuoc-thi-soi-dong-cung-v-league-2021-131570t.html\">Bo Thanh Nin</a>', 'Si ni cuc thi \'Si ng cng V-League 2021\' | Bng  Vit Nam', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'soi-noi-cuoc-thi-soi-dong-cung-v-league-2021-bong-da-viet-nam', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:45:41', '2021-03-20 11:45:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/soi-noi-cuoc-thi-soi-dong-cung-v-league-2021-bong-da-viet-nam/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(924, 1, '2021-03-20 11:46:40', '2021-03-20 11:46:40', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/xet-xu-16161549826901911386881.jpg\" id=\"img_03ba9400-88a6-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" w=\"790\" h=\"450\" alt=\"Tuyn n cc b co n n vo xe ca thnh chi Dng Minh Tuyn - nh 1.\" title=\"Tuyn n cc b co n n vo xe ca thnh chi Dng Minh Tuyn - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"03ba9400-88a6-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/xet-xu-16161549826901911386881.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">B co Khoa v Linh ti phin ta - nh: VNH QUN</p></div></div><p>Hai b co b a ra xt x gm H Vn Khoa (29 tui, tr thn Thi Ph, x Mai nh, huyn Sc Sn, TP H Ni) v L Vn Linh (22 tui, tr thn 6, x Ba Tri, huyn Ba V, TP H Ni).  </p><p>Cn c ti liu v li khai nhn ca cc b co ti ta, hi ng xt x TAND huyn Thanh Min tuyn pht b co H Vn Khoa 39 thng t giam, trong  30 thng t v ti \"gy ri trt t cng cng\" v 9 thng t ti \"c  lm h hng ti sn\".</p><p>B co L Vn Linh nhn 30 thng t giam, gm 24 thng t v ti \"gy ri trt t cng cng\" v 6 thng t ti \"c  lm h hng ti sn\".  </p><p>Theo co trng, H Vn Khoa mu thun vi Dng Minh Tuyn (35 tui, tr khu 5, phng Tin An, TP Bc Ninh) trn mng x hi. Ngy 4-1, Tuyn v d tic tn gia nh ngi quen ti x on Tng, huyn Thanh Min.</p><p>Ti y, Tuyn khng thy Khoa n nh  hn trc nn  ln Facebook pht trc tip hn Khoa v gii quyt. Khoa sau  mang theo khu sng bn n ghm cng 5 vin n i taxi t H Ni v Hi Dng.  </p><p>Khi n Hi Dng, Khoa in thoi cho L Vn Linh bo i xe my t H Ni xung huyn Thanh Min n Khoa nhm bn cnh co Tuyn.<span style=\"\">Khong 21h30 cng ngy, Linh ch Khoa bng xe my n qun karaoke ti th trn Thanh Min th pht hin t ca Tuyn ang  gn  nn Khoa bn 3 pht n v pha t.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Hu qu, chic t h hng mt s ch nhng khng gy thng vong v ngi.</span><span style=\"\">Cng an tnh Hi Dng sau  xc nh v triu tp L Vn Linh n lm vic.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Sau 14 ngy ln trn, H Vn Khoa c ngi thn a n Phng cnh st kinh t Cng an TP H Ni u th.</span><span style=\"\">Kt qu gim nh xc nh t ca Tuyn h hng, thit hi khong 2,5 triu ng.</span></p><p>Trc , ngy 25-3-2014, H Vn Khoa tng b TAND huyn Sc Sn, TP H Ni x pht 14 thng t v ti cng ot ti sn.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/tuyen-an-cac-bi-cao-na-dan-vao-xe-cua-thanh-chui-duong-minh-tuyen-20210319190520592.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Tuyn n cc b co n n vo xe ca \'thnh chi\' Dng Minh Tuyn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tuyen-an-cac-bi-cao-na-dan-vao-xe-cua-thanh-chui-duong-minh-tuyen', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:46:40', '2021-03-20 11:46:40', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tuyen-an-cac-bi-cao-na-dan-vao-xe-cua-thanh-chui-duong-minh-tuyen/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(925, 1, '2021-03-20 11:48:40', '2021-03-20 11:48:40', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"content-id\">\n\n                                        \n                                        \n                                        <div class=\"content-news-detail old-news\" data-field=\"body\">\n                                            <p>Mt ngy sau khi nc M chn ng v v x sng hm 17-3  bang Atlanta khin 8 ngi cht, trong  c 6 ph n chu , tip tc c thm 2 ngi ln tui gc  tr thnh nn nhn ca 1 v hnh hung v c. <br/></p><p>Cnh st  xc nh nghi phm trong v tn cng l Steven Jenkins, 39 tui. Hn ang i mt vi cc co buc hnh hung v ngc i ngi cao tui. Theo iu tra, Jenkins l k tn cng c b 76 tui Xiao Zhen Xie v c ng 83 tui Ngoc Pham. </p><p>Cc nhn chng cho bit Jenkins  tham gia vo mt cuc hn chin  U.N. Plaza khong 30 pht trc khi tn cng 2 nn nhn ln tui. C th, sau khi ri U.N Plaza, hn tip cn v hnh hung ng Pham khi ng ang i ra t khu ch gn .<br/></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img id=\"img_12766f40-8951-11eb-b63e-bfc248b85846\" w=\"634\" h=\"356\" alt=\"Tnh ngi trong ln sng k th ngi gc   M - nh 1.\" title=\"Tnh ngi trong ln sng k th ngi gc   M - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"12766f40-8951-11eb-b63e-bfc248b85846\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" src=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/2021/3/20/photo-1-1616226683300473445243.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">ng Ngoc Pham, 1 trong 2 nn nhn ln tui b hnh hung hm 18-3. nh: Aw Journal</p></div></div><p>Mt nhn vin bo v nhn c tin bo v truy ui Jenkins. Trn ng b trn, hn tip tc  tn cng b Xiao v b b chng tr quyt lit. C 2 nn nhn u c a ti bnh vin v may mn khng b thng nguy him n tnh mng</p><p>Theo trang quyn gp cho ng Pham, ng vn ang nm vin v b gy xng mi v chn thng c. Trung tm Cng ng Thanh nin  San Francisco gip ng chi tr vin ph. n nay, ng Pham  nhn c hn 137.600 USD tin quyn gp. Trong khi , trang quyn gp ca b Xiao thu c hn 649.000 USD. </p><p>Thng k ca nhm Stop AAPI Hate cho thy k t thng 3-2020,  c gn 3.800 bo co v cc v vic th ght ngi chu  trn khp nc M, trong  cha bao gm nhng v c th khng b bo co.</p>\n\n                                            <!-- B&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u Dable / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                            \n                                            <!-- K&#7871;t th&uacute;c / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                        </div>\n\n                                        <span class=\"author fr\" data-field=\"author\">&#13;\n                                            Bo Hnh</span>\n                                        \n                                        <div class=\"sharemxh bottomshare\">\n                                            \n                                            \n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"print\">\n                                                &#13;\n                                                    <img src=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/web_images/icon-print-3.png\" class=\"iconprintdetailbot\"/>&#13;\n                                                \n                                            </div>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                    </div><script async defer crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v5.0&appId=889975511027097\"></script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://nld.com.vn/thoi-su-quoc-te/tinh-nguoi-trong-lan-song-ky-thi-nguoi-goc-a-o-my-20210320145819505.htm\">Bo Ngi Lao ng</a>', 'Tnh ngi trong ln sng k th ngi gc   M', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tinh-nguoi-trong-lan-song-ky-thi-nguoi-goc-a-o-my',