(926, 1, '2021-03-20 11:50:39', '2021-03-20 11:50:39', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><p>Hi ng qun tr FPT Online ang trnh c ng phng n dng li nhun cha phn phi tr c tc 2020 vi t l 200% bng tin mt.</p><div id=\"\">\n<p class=\"Normal\">Theo  xut chia c tc ti ti liu trnh i hi ng c ng thng nin cui thng ny, mi c phiu FOC ca Cng ty c phn Dch v trc tuyn FPT (FPT Online) c nhn 20.000 ng. Ngun tin  chia n t li nhun cha phn phi.</p><p class=\"Normal\">FPT Online cng trnh phng n chia c tc nm 2021 khng thp hn 50%. Cng ty ny tng tr c tc nm 2018 bng tin mt vi t l 130%. Nm 2019 l 150% bng tin mt v 25% bng c phiu.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Trn sn chng khon, c phiu FOC ang giao dch  vng gi 115.000 ng. Khi lng giao dch bnh qun t u nm n nay t gn 7.000 c phiu mi phin, tng mnh so vi mc bnh qun 1.660 c phiu ca nm ngoi.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/fptonline-4190-1616126159.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=NL04-TYFKFPK9XgtBBVO0w\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"720\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 59.982862039417%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/fptonline-4190-1616126159.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=99OfhRlNbYwXrfU6jvV8Fg 1x, https://i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/fptonline-4190-1616126159.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=AptFwB6jlTUhBa6CEv-0RQ 1.5x, https://i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/fptonline-4190-1616126159.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=YYmoHDWFCpxueti8MREr0w 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Vn phng Cng ty FPT Online ti H Ni. nh: Anh T.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/fptonline-4190-1616126159.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=99OfhRlNbYwXrfU6jvV8Fg\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Vn phng Cng ty FPT Online ti H Ni. nh: <em>Anh T.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">C tc 200% l mc cao so vi mt bng chung ca cc doanh nghip trn sn chng khon. Trc , ch vi ci tn c mc tr c tc cao hn nh Cng ty c phn Bn xe Min Ty (WCS) v Cng ty c phn Vinacafe Bin Ho ln lt tr c tc nm 2019 l 516% v 250% bng tin mt.</p><p class=\"Normal\">FPT Online thnh lp vo gia nm 2007 vi chin lc l cng ty truyn thng qung co s hng u, ng dng cng ngh vo lnh vc truyn thng xut bn. FPT Online l n v khai thc qung co, ng hnh cng Bo in t VnExpress, Ngi Sao, iOne, vn hnh chui gii chy VnExpress Marathon...</p><p class=\"Normal\">Nm ngoi, cng ty ghi nhn xp x 600 t ng doanh thu thun v 256 t ng li nhun trc thu. Li nhun sau thu cha phn phi n cui nm gn 600 t ng. Cng ty t mc tiu nm nay t doanh thu 700 t ng v li trc thu 310 t ng.</p><p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong>Phng ng</strong></p>\n</div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/fpt-online-chia-co-tuc-tien-mat-200-4250828.html\">VNEXPRESS.NET</a>', 'FPT Online chia c tc tin mt 200%', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fpt-online-chia-co-tuc-tien-mat-200', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:50:39', '2021-03-20 11:50:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/fpt-online-chia-co-tuc-tien-mat-200/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(927, 1, '2021-03-20 11:52:18', '2021-03-20 11:52:18', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <p><b>Tri nghim tin ch, nhanh chng v an ton</b></p><p>Gii php nh danh in t (eKYC) c xem nh bc ngot ln trong qu trnh s ha hot ng ngn hng, to iu kin cho ngn hng cung cp cc dch v s ti khch hng. Nhn thy tim nng v li ch ca eKYC cng nh xu hng chuyn i s Ngnh Ngn hng, VietinBank  nhanh chng a gii php ny vo ng dng VietinBank iPay Mobile, mang n tri nghim tin ch cho ngi dng.</p><p>Vi gii php eKYC, khch hng khng phi n quy giao dch  thc hin cc th tc ng k, xc minh thng tin, m hon ton c th ngi  bt c u v m ti khon ngay trn ng dng VietinBank iPay Mobile.</p><p>C th, khch hng ch cn chp nh giy t ty thn (cn cc cng dn/chng minh th nhn dn hoc h chiu), chp nh khun mt, h thng s kim tra cc thng tin hp l v tin hnh m ti khon cho khch hng ngay lp tc.</p> <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\">     <div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/1-16160605068821076880157.png\" id=\"img_24039450-87ca-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" w=\"1632\" h=\"959\" alt=\"VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC - nh 1.\" title=\"VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"24039450-87ca-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/1-16160605068821076880157.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>     <div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Ngi dng s dng eKYC  m ti khon</p></div> </div> <p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">VietinBank  ng dng cc cng ngh tr tu nhn to hin i nht trong qu trnh trin khai eKYC nh: Cng ngh c d liu hnh nh (OCR), cng ngh nhn din gng mt (FAC) y l cc cng ngh tin tin v ng tin cy, m bo tnh minh bch, nhanh chng, gip khch hng thun li hn khi thc hin m ti khon ngn hng.</span><br/></p> <p class=\"\">Gii php eKYC c nhn nh l nn tng thit yu  cc ngn hng tin hnh chuyn i s trong thi i 4.0, gip ngn hng n gin ha nhiu th tc v cc bc  m ti khon, ng thi gip khch hng tit kim thi gian v thun tin hn trong     cc giao dch.</p> <p class=\"\">Theo nh gi ca Ph thng c Ngn hng Nh nc Vit Nam Nguyn Kim Anh th vic thc hin eKYC trong thit lp mi quan h ln u vi khch hng c coi l \"ca ng\"  pht trin cc m hnh ngn hng s. c bit, vic nhn bit v xc minh thng     tin khch hng trong m ti khon thanh ton ng vai tr quan trng, gip khch hng tip cn v s dng cc dch v ngn hng, cho php cc ngn hng c th m rng khch hng v cung ng dch v ngn hng an ton, thun tin, hiu qu.</p> <p class=\"\">i din VietinBank cho bit: \"Trong qu trnh chuyn i s, VietinBank ch trng n tri nghim ca ngi dng, lin tc cp nht cc cng ngh mi nht, n lc a ra nhiu sn phm, dch v u vit.Vic ng dng eKYC l xu hng pht trin     tt yu, l c hi  VietinBank tng kh nng tip cn khch hng mi vi nhng tri nghim tt nht, t  khuyn khch ngi dng s dng cc dch v ngn hng s, gp phn thc hin mc tiu ti chnh ton din quc gia\".</p> <p class=\"\"><b>p dng cng ngh \'Face-Pay\' trong xc thc</b></p> <p>Song song vi vic trin khai gii php m ti khon trc tuyn, VietinBank  ng dng ng thi gii php \"Face-Pay\" vo xc thc thanh ton. Vi gii php ny, khch hng c th ci t xc thc thng qua khun mt cho 100% cc giao dch ti chnh ca khch hng trn ng dng.</p><p>\"Ti khon m bng khun mt no ch khun mt ca khch hng  mi c th thc hin giao dch chuyn tin i t ti khon,  l im ni bt ca cng ngh Face-Pay trn ng dng VietinBank iPay Mobile\", i din VietinBank cho bit.</p> <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\">     <div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/17/photo-1-16159642423911053970443.jpg\" id=\"img_fa8ba5d0-86e9-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" w=\"1431\" h=\"832\" alt=\"VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC - nh 2.\" title=\"VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"fa8ba5d0-86e9-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/17/photo-1-16159642423911053970443.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>     <div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Vi cc giao dch ti chnh trn VietinBank iPay Mobile ngi dng c thm mt phng thc xc thc \'Face-Pay\'</p></div> </div> <p class=\"\"><b><span style=\"\">H sinh thi ngn hng s a tnh nng vi nhiu u i hp dn</span></b></p> <p class=\"\">M ti khon thanh ton qua eKYC, khch hng s s hu ngay ti khon 0 ph. y l chnh sch u i ca VietinBank hng n khch hng nhm loi b lo lng ca khch hng v ph dch v. Theo , khch hng s c min tt c cc loi ph khi s dng     ti khon nh: Ph chuyn khon trong v ngoi h thng, ph duy tr ti khon, ph duy tr dch v iPay v ph thng bo bin ng ti khon.</p> <p class=\"\">Trong qu trnh pht trin ng dng, VietinBank  khng ngng nng cp, lm mi h sinh thi vi hn 130 tnh nng ti chnh, tiu dng ton din, em ti s thun tin v ti a ha li ch cho khch hng.</p> <p class=\"\">Cc tnh nng chuyn khoan nhanh 24/7, tnh nng nhc nh thanh ton cc loi ha n, np tin in thoi, chuyn khon nh k v t lch chuyn tin, dch v th n cc tin ch nh t v nh t v my bay, phng khch sn, tu - xe, v xem phim,     mua sm online  gp phn em n nhng tri nghim mi m cho ngi dng.</p> <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\">     <div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/17/photo-2-1615964242394605729763.jpg\" id=\"img_fa951bb0-86e9-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" w=\"880\" h=\"587\" alt=\"VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC - nh 3.\" title=\"VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"fa951bb0-86e9-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/17/photo-2-1615964242394605729763.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>     <div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Thanh ton VNPAY - QR em li s nhanh chng, an ton</p></div> </div> <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"wrapnote\" data-border=\"#ff9900\" style=\"border-color: rgb(255, 153, 0); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\">     <p>Bn cnh , nhm gip khch hng thun tin hn khi i mua sm m khng cn dng ti tin mt hay th, tin ch thanh ton QR Pay trn ng ng thng qua qut m VNPAY - QR s gip khch hng thc hin rt n gin, nhanh chng vi nhiu u i. Hin         ti  c hn 100.000 im chp nhn thanh ton VNPAY - QR trn ton quc v ph khp tt c cc ngnh ngh, dch v.</p>     <p> tri nghim ngn hng s a tin ch VietinBank iPay Mobile phin bn mi nht v cp nht eKYC, ngi dng c th ti ng dng ti link App Store hoc Google Play.</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/vietinbank-trien-khai-dinh-danh-khach-hang-truc-tuyen-ekyc-20210317140202425.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'VietinBank trin khai nh danh khch hng trc tuyn eKYC', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vietinbank-trien-khai-dinh-danh-khach-hang-truc-tuyen-ekyc', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:52:18', '2021-03-20 11:52:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/vietinbank-trien-khai-dinh-danh-khach-hang-truc-tuyen-ekyc/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(929, 1, '2021-03-20 11:56:41', '2021-03-20 11:56:41', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/img-1781-16160616639001961531477.jpg\" id=\"img_dd27c310-87d0-11eb-accd-4b65fc5be44e\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1500\" alt=\"Ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam: Xin tin l vic nh nhng hn cc nhim v khc - nh 1.\" title=\"Ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam: Xin tin l vic nh nhng hn cc nhim v khc - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"dd27c310-87d0-11eb-accd-4b65fc5be44e\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/img-1781-16160616639001961531477.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam Nguyn Quang Thiu cho bit ng mun y mnh x hi ha cc hot ng ca hi v kinh ph t ngn sch qu eo hp - nh: T.IU</p></div></div><p>Ti l ra mt trang thng tin in t vanvn.vn do Hi Nh vn Vit Nam t chc ngy 18-3  H Ni, ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam ni nhiu v cu chuyn x hi ha cc hot ng ca hi m ng ang tin hnh cng vi ban chp hnh hi.</p><p>Nhng nm qua, c nhiu  kin  xut t x hi cn tin ti xa b bao cp cho cc hi, t chc ngh nghip v c tho lun si ni khi c thng tin cho bit nu tnh c t ai, nh ca, xe c v cc ti sn khc, chi ph t ngn sch cho ton h thng cc hi on mi nm ln n hng chc ngn t ng.</p><p>ng Thiu cho bit ng mun \"x hi ha cng nhiu cng tt v kinh ph t ngn sch nh nc cho hot ng ca hi qu hp hi, khng lm c g\".</p><p>u tin, ng mun xin kinh ph x hi ha  ci to ngi bit th s 65 Nguyn Du hin ang l tr s ca Nh xut bn Hi Nh Vn - c quan cp hai ca Hi Nh vn Vit Nam -  ni y tr thnh khng gian sinh hot p, ngi nh m p ca cc nh vn, nh th.</p><p>Kinh ph cn thit s rt ln nhng ng Thiu tin nu c ban chp hnh hi ng thun, cc hi vin ng  th vic xin tin vi ng \"l vic nh nhng hn tt c nhng nhim v khc  hi\".</p><p>ng cng d nh t chc nhiu gii thng vn hc bng ngun x hi ha, trong  c bit sn sc ti cuc thi dnh cho cc cy vit tr v cuc vn ng sng tc cho thiu nhi.</p><p>Vi gii thng cho cc cy vit tr, ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam mong mun ngi tr  thc hn v sng to ca mnh, o su v ngh thut, o su s mnh ca mnh vi x hi, phn bin x hi, ln ting cho s tht, l cng bng,  vn ngh tr ln sng ng hn, to ra nhp iu khc trong sinh hot ca cc nh vn, nh th.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p>Ban chp hnh Hi Nh vn Vit Nam cng ang gp rt tin hnh ci t cc c quan cp hai ca hi gm: bo <i>Vn Ngh</i>, tp ch <i>Nh Vn V Tc Phm</i> (i thnh <i>Nh Vn V Cuc Sng</i>), nh xut bn Hi Nh Vn v trang thng tin in t ca hi l vanvn.net i thnh vanvn.vn.</p><p>V trang vanvn.vn ra mt hm nay, 18-3, nh th Phan Hong - ngi c giao ph trch trang thng tin ny - cho bit ngoi nhng chuyn mc thng tin v hot ng hi, tc phm mi, tc phm c li, vn hc nh trng, vn hc nc ngoi, vn ha v i sng, trang thng tin ny s dnh trng tm cho vn hc tr, vn hc thiu nhi, bin gii - hi o, vn hc Vit Nam xut bn song ng  gp phn qung b vn hc Vit Nam ra th gii.</p><p>Trang thng tin ny cng hng ti tr thnh th vin cc nh vn Vit Nam online bng n lc nhp liu tiu s vn hc ca tt c nh vn hi vin.</p><p>Sp ti, trang thng tin ny s t chc cuc thi vn hc Nam B, v sau  l cuc thi vn hc Ty Nguyn bng ngun kinh ph x hi ha.</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/chu-tich-hoi-nha-van-viet-nam-xin-tien-la-viec-nhe-nhang-hon-cac-nhiem-vu-khac-20210318170415743.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam: \'Xin tin l vic nh nhng hn cc nhim v khc\'', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chu-tich-hoi-nha-van-viet-nam-xin-tien-la-viec-nhe-nhang-hon-cac-nhiem-vu-khac', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:56:41', '2021-03-20 11:56:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/chu-tich-hoi-nha-van-viet-nam-xin-tien-la-viec-nhe-nhang-hon-cac-nhiem-vu-khac/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
