(931, 1, '2021-03-20 11:58:40', '2021-03-20 11:58:40', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616051964252537305777.jpg\" id=\"img_45c88c90-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"1536\" h=\"1024\" alt=\"Singapore tng bc m ca du lch gia i dch - nh 1.\" title=\"Singapore tng bc m ca du lch gia i dch - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"45c88c90-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616051964252537305777.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">S kin TravelRevive c din ra vi cc bin php m bo an ton ti a - Ngun: The Straits Times</p></div></div><p><b><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">im n an ton</span><br/></b></p><p>TravelRevive - s kin trin lm thng mi Singapore, t chc cui thng 11-2020 thu ht gn 1.000 khch tham d trc tip khin c th gii bt ng. y l s kin th im quy m cp quc gia u tin ti chu , th nghim giao thc hi ch thng mi theo m hnh hybrid kt hp trc tip - trc tuyn cho cc s kin doanh nghip an ton, l trnh an ton v h tr k thut s  Singapore.</p><p>Cc ni dung s kin ny  cp ti l trao i  tng, chia s kin thc v hnh dung li tng lai ca du lch, vic nay khin nhiu ngi bt ng v n c t chc trong thi im i dch COVID-19 din bin phc tp.</p><p>Thc t, s kin ny th im vic ng dng nhng sng kin cng ngh nh cng ngh khng tip xc, ng dng nht k trc tuyn, cng ngh trnh chiu 3 chiu to n tng din gi nh ang c mt ti hi ngh d pht biu t xa.</p><p>Tnh n ngy 31-12-2020, Singapore  thnh cng t chc 29 s kin MICE vi s kin u tin l Singapore International Energy Week vo thng 10-2020.</p><p>Ti sao Singapore m ca du lch trong khi ngnh cng nghip khng khi ny gn nh t lit trn th gii v COVID-19? Vn  nm  chnh sch mi ca Singapore, ti m ca du lch mt cch thn trng, an ton v vic khng ngng thit k nhng tri nghim mi cho du khch.</p><p>Singapore m u bng chin dch SG Clean - cc c s kinh doanh mun c hot ng tr li phi t c chng nhn SG Clean. y l chng nhn quc gia dnh cho nhng doanh nghip t c tiu chun nghim ngt v v sinh an ton.</p><p>SG-Clean p dng cho tt c cc khch sn, im tham quan, tour du lch Doanh nghip v cc im tham quan gii hn s ngi, cng sut phc v v phi chng minh c kh nng p ng, c phng php truy vt cn thit.</p><p>o quc s t cp th thng hnh du lch an ton (Safe Travel Pass - STP) cho khch c cc chuyn cng tc v du lch thit yu chnh thc. Bn cnh  l th thng hnh ng hng khng (Air Travel Pass- ATP) cho php tt c cc hnh thc du lch ngn hn t cc quc gia hoc khu vc c chp thun, bao gm c du lch gii tr n Singapore.</p><p>Tuy nhin,  cc quc gia c ca ly nhim COVID-19 mi trong cng ng vt mc an ton th Singapore tm ngng tip nhn cho n khi c thng bo mi.</p><p>ng Keith Tan, tng cc trng Tng cc  Du lch Singapore (STB) cho bit: \"STB vn t tin v vic Singapore l mt trong nhng im n gii tr v thng mi an ton v thu ht nht th gii cng nh nhng trin vng lu di ca ngnh du lch Singapore.</p><p>Trong khi du lch quc t ni chung c th s kh tr li chnh thc trong nm 2021 nhng STB s tip tc st cnh cng cc i tc ca chng ti  chun b sn sng cho s phc hi, xy dng mt tng lai tt p v bn vng hn cho ngnh du lch\".</p><p>Theo Tng cc du lch Singapore (STB), c quan ny  hp tc vi cc i tc trong ngnh  nng cao cc bin php an ton v bo v sc khe da trn cc tiu chun quc gia mi,  du khch c th yn tm tn hng hng lot tri nghim mi m ca o quc trong tng lai.</p><p><b>Tri nghim mi t sc mnh cng ngh</b></p><p>Du lch Singapore t cc tiu chun an ton lm c s  thu ht khch du lch v \"hnh dung li\" ngnh du lch  o quc ny.</p><p>Ngay t khi ti m ca trong i dch, hng lot sng kin mi v cng ngh  c p dng  Singapore. o quc p dng hng lot cc gii php t cng ngh khng tip xc, robot v sinh n ng dng v thit b truy vt TraceTogether (cng c truy vt tip xc k thut s cp quc gia u tin trn th gii).</p><p>Nn tng cng ngh khin o quc ny nm bt nhanh xu hng tri nghim trc tuyn, a im v m hnh t chc s kin hybdrid kt hp trc tip - trc tuyn. Ngay c nhn lc trong ngnh du lch cng c p dng cng ngh nh robot pha ch, phc v m ra cc phng thc mi  chinh phc du khch.</p><p>Chng han nh Tp on Zouk - tp on s hu nhng hp m ni ting  Singapore, ang dn chuyn khng gian hp m thnh cc dch v sng to khc  khch c nhng tri nghim khc l.</p><p> Capital Kitchen, tp on ny  bin khng gian tip khch thnh khu vc n ung pop-up c o vo thng 7-2020. Khng gian ny tr thnh ni phc v cc mn n chu  v phng Ty, cng vi cc loi ru sake, ru vang, ru mnh, cocktail ng chai.</p><p>Zouk cng ngay lp tc tp hp cc club li thnh Cloud Clubbing v cc DJ chi nhc pht trc tuyn. Cc rp chiu phim cng nhanh chng cho khch tri nghim in nh khng gian m pop-up</p><p>Hay t hp khu kinh doanh, ngh dng kt hp casino Marina Bay Sands  ra mt mt studio ng cp  pht sng cc s kin hybrid kt hp trc tip - trc tuyn u tin.</p><p>Studio cung cp kh nng pht trc tuyn vi cht lng pht sng ng cp v cc chc nng nh ba chiu. Sn khu trung tm c trang b thit k ba chiu cho c phng v nn sn khu  d dng ty chnh cho cc s kin khc nhau.</p><p>Studio cng c trang b tng cng nhng tnh nng s dng cng ngh thc t hn hp (MR), tch hp th gii o v thc t  mang n nhng mn tng tc sng ng. Trong tng lai, khch hng c th mong i nhiu s kin kt hp cng ngh hn vi cc gii php Thc t o (VR), Thc t tng cng (AR) v Thc t m rng (XR).</p><p>ng Lee Seow Hiang - gim c iu hnh Tp on sn bay Changi chia s: \"Mt trong nhng bi hc qu gi chng ti  rt ra c t i dch COVID-19 l sc mnh ca s i mi v th nghim. Ti sn bay Changi, chng ti phi ngh cch chuyn i nhng khu vc cm ng thnh khu vc khng tip xc.</p><p>Ngy nay, chng ti  chnh thc pht trin thnh sn bay khng tip xc, ni hnh khch c th thc hin ton b qu trnh lm th tc ln my bay m khng cn chm vo bt k b mt no. Mt tinh thn i mi tng t c p dng cho tt c cc lnh vc kinh doanh ca chng ti.</p><p>Khi ngnh du lch hi sinh, chng ti s sn sng mang n nhng tri nghim an ton v th v ng ngc nhin cho hnh khch nhp cnh ti sn bay Changi\".</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616051966783337241917.jpg\" id=\"img_4133bf00-87b6-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" w=\"1500\" h=\"1000\" alt=\"Singapore tng bc m ca du lch gia i dch - nh 2.\" title=\"Singapore tng bc m ca du lch gia i dch - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"4133bf00-87b6-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616051966783337241917.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Nhng quy lm th tc check-in c chuyn i t cm ng sang s dng m QR gim s tip xc ti a - Ngun: The Airline Passenger Experience Association</p></div></div><p><span style=\"\">Bn canh o, Singapore ang thit k tp trung vo yu t t nhin ti nhng danh thng ni ting nh Jewel Changi hay Gardens by the Bay.</span><br/></p><p>Chnh ph cn mong mun bin Singapore thnh \"thnh ph gia thin nhin\" trong 3 thp k ti.<span style=\"\">Trong , o quc ny s ci tin khu Pht trin du lch qun Jurong Lake tr thnh mt im n du lch v i sng ng cp th gii, va gn vi thin nhin theo tiu ch \"khu vn trong thnh ph\" va gn vi nhng tri nghim mi v khoa hc tin tin.</span></p><p>Khu Mandai Precinct cng dn c ti to  tr thnh khu vc sinh thi ng cp th gii, ni mang n cho du khch cc im tham quan ng vt hoang d mi cng nh hng lot dch v lu tr thn thin vi mi trng.</p><p>Theo b Sherleen Seah, trng i din Tng cc Du lch Singapore ti Vit Nam,  Vit Nam l th trng quan trng i vi ngnh du lch Singapore, vi gn 600.000 lt khch trong nm 2019 - ng th 11 trong tng s du khch n Singapore. Trong khi du lch ang gp nhiu thch thc do i dch, SingapoReimagine l mt minh chng cho nhng n lc khng ngng ca chng ti trong vic duy tr v th ca Singapore l im n hng u i vi khch du lch v doanh nhn Vit Nam.</p><p>\"Chng ti hy vng thng qua chin dch SingapoReimagine (Tm dch: Hnh dung li, tri nghim mi), du khch Vit Nam c th tri nghim v tn hng Singapore t xa v cng hnh dung li tng lai ca du lch trong khi ch i s tr li ca du lch quc t\" - b Sherleen Seah chia s.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://dulich.tuoitre.vn/singapore-tung-buoc-mo-cua-du-lich-giua-dai-dich-20210318143026667.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Singapore tng bc m ca du lch gia i dch', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'singapore-tung-buoc-mo-cua-du-lich-giua-dai-dich', '', '', '2021-03-20 11:58:40', '2021-03-20 11:58:40', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/singapore-tung-buoc-mo-cua-du-lich-giua-dai-dich/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
