(934, 1, '2021-03-20 12:00:50', '2021-03-20 12:00:50', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chiu 18/3, BS Nguyn Vit Nam, khoa Cp cu, Bnh vin Bnh Nhit i Trung ng cho bit, bnh nhn nam 63 tui,  Sc Sn, H Ni mc bnh nn tiu ng, tng huyt p.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">c bit, bnh nhn t mua thuc tiu ng dng vin bt v nh ung d khng h bit thnh phn ca thuc. Sau  ngy 15/3, ng nhp vin trong tnh trng tt huyt p, suy a tng, km theo suy thn. BS Nam cho bit, bnh nhn cn gp nguy kch khi mu chuyn sang tnh trng toan chuyn ha, kch thch rt nng, mch ri rc, nguy c ngng tim.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-holdclass=\"\"><img alt=\"T  mua thuc tr tiu ng cha cht cm, ngi n ng nguy kch - 1\" height=\"629\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"629\" data-id=\"1548184\" data-detail=\"1\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/cap-cuu-10-06222777.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"0\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\" data-holdclass=\"\">Bnh nhn hin ang iu tr ti khoa Cp cu, Bnh vin Bnh Nhit i Trung ng.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> kp bc s khoa Cp cu t ng ni kh qun, cho bnh nhn iu tr truyn thuc vn mch, b dch v lc mu. Sau 3 ngy lc mu, xu hng huyt ng ca bnh nhn cng ci thin hn, hin bnh nhn  ct c thuc vn mch, dng lc mu, cc toan chuyn ha, toan lactic  c bn n nh.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Khi nhp vin, nhn th trng bnh nhn to khe, chng ti chn on bnh nhn c th b chuyn ha, ng c nn x tr ng c cho bnh nhn trc. Khai thc tin s th c bit bnh nhn s dng thuc nam  iu tr tiu ng. Ngi nh a mu thuc bnh nhn  ung cho chng ti, sau  chng ti  gi mu thuc sang bn Vin Php y th kt qu 1 loi thuc l paracetamol, 1 loi l phenformin thuc iu tr tiu ng  b cm t lu,</em>BS Nam cho bit.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">BS Nam cng cho hay, bnh nhn ny nhp vin trong tnh trng rt nguy kch, ch chm t pht l c th khng cu c, v cng nguy him.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-holdclass=\"\"><img alt=\"T  mua thuc tr tiu ng cha cht cm, ngi n ng nguy kch - 2\" height=\"880\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"880\" data-id=\"1548185\" data-detail=\"1\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/z238592885055859ccb9969f4af1a554177bbf27e2a450-06222808.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"1\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\" data-holdclass=\"\">Loi thuc cha cht cm m bnh nhn  mua ung vi hy vng cha c bnh tiu ng.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cng theo BS Nam, thng thng ng c do phenformin s gy t l t vong rt cao, t 50-60% tr ln. Thuc ny ngoi gy tt ng huyt cn gy tc dng ph toan lactic, suy thn rt nng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">n nay cc ch s ca bnh nhn  n nh, chc nng thn v bnh thng, bnh nhn  c nc tiu. BS hy vng trong 1-2 ngy ti, bnh nhn s c rt ng ni kh qun v s iu tr tip  cc c quan ni tng tip tc hi phc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ThS.BS Nguyn Trung Cp, Ph Gim c Bnh vin Bnh Nhit i Trung ng, Trng khoa Cp cu cho bit, thnh phn phenformin trong thuc bnh nhn ung tng c ghi nhn gy nhiu trng hp ng c v t vong trn th gii. Do vy cht ny b cm s dng t nhng nm 1970 v c thay th bng nhiu loi thuc iu tr tiu ng khc an ton hn.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy  Vit Nam khng cho php lu hnh dc cht ny, nhng nhiu gian thng vn bn chui li di dng vin t khng r hm lng v qung co c th iu tr khi dt im bnh tiu ng nn nhiu ngi nh d  mua ung, gy nhiu trng hp ng c thng tm.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bnh tiu ng l bnh mn tnh cn iu tr v iu chnh ch  dinh dng, sinh hot lu di. V vy, ng khuyn co ngi dn mc cc bnh l mn tnh nn n cc c s y t chuyn khoa  khm, cha bnh  cc bc s c th ch nh cc bin php iu tr an ton v ph hp. Tuyt i khng nghe d d qung co v nhng phng thuc b truyn c th cha khi dt im bnh ny m dn n tin mt tt mang.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/tu-y-mua-thuoc-tri-tieu-duong-chua-chat-cam-nguoi-dan-ong-nguy-kich-ar601795.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'T  mua thuc tr tiu ng cha cht cm, ngi n ng nguy kch', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tu-y-mua-thuoc-tri-tieu-duong-chua-chat-cam-nguoi-dan-ong-nguy-kich', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:00:50', '2021-03-20 12:00:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tu-y-mua-thuoc-tri-tieu-duong-chua-chat-cam-nguoi-dan-ong-nguy-kich/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(935, 1, '2021-03-20 12:01:53', '2021-03-20 12:01:53', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>Nm 2008, huyn Quan Ha (Thanh Ha) l mt trong trong 62 huyn ngho nht v n nm 2018 Th tng iu chnh danh sch cc huyn ngho th Quan Ha vn nm trong nhm 1, nhm cc huyn vn ngho. Mi y, Quan Ha xin tnh u t tr s tr gi hn 30 t ng sau khi  thc hin mt lot sa cha, nng cp tr s c.</i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>L do m ch u t a ra l  nng cao hnh nh ca huyn y v huyn Quan Ha to tin  nng cao mc sng, xa i gim ngho i vi ngi dn trong huyn, gim s chnh lch giu ngho gia min xui v min ngc. </i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>L do ny na n l do m nm 2015 c ngi ly ra  bin minh cho vic bn pho hoa l Ngi ngho khao kht xem bn pho hoa. Nhng lc thng thc bn pho hoa gip h qun i ci ngho, ci kh.</i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>Thc t th nu c xy tr s th ch c tr s huyn l p, ch i sng nhn dn huyn chc khng ngy mt ngy hai m p c. Xy tr s mi, dn vn khng v th m c xa i gim ngho. Xy tr s mi chc ch gim chnh lch v quy m tr s huyn ny vi huyn khc, ch kinh t ca dn th cha chc kh hn cc huyn khc. </i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>Khng tm cch pht trin kinh t - x hi a phng  t mnh vn ln th khng ch Quan Ha m nhiu a phng khc s n ni th no vi cc a phng ang ng gp ngn sch cho trung ng  phn b cho cc tnh, huyn ngho? ng ni, nhng a phng nh TP.HCM chng hn, trong khi vn phi gng mnh iu tit ngn sch v trung ng th tr s cc c quan nh nc  y vn rt c, thm ch c khi phng ca ph gim c s cn di tiu chun cho php. </i></p>\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>Trung ng tht ra cng kh x khi yu cu nhiu a phng iu tit ngn sch v trung ng trong khi nhiu a phng c trung ng h tr, rt ngn sch ch chm chm   xy tr s, tng i? Th tng Nguyn Xun Phc mi y  Hi ngh tng kt nm nm hot ng ca T cng tc ca Th tng cn nu tnh trng mt s a phng bo co gim ngho tt nhng vn xin tin cao.</i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>C l vi nhng a phng cn ngho th vic tit kim phi c t ln hng u cng vi vic chm lo pht trin kinh t, t lc, t cng. Trng ban T chc Trung ng Phm Minh Chnh nhng nm trc y khi pht biu  Quc hi  thng k: Ch cn tit kim chi thng xuyn 1%/nm th c nc tit kim c 10.000 t. </i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>Tng t, nu tit kim c nhng vic khng hn l cp thit nht nh xy tr s  Quan Ha th c nc cn tit kim c bit bao nhiu. Ngun lc tit kim y  dnh cho u t pht trin th chc ri nhng huyn nh Quan Ha s t t t xy c tr s. </i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>ng mng l trn tinh thn thc hin ch trng tit kim, khi nghe v vic xin xy tr s mi (ch cha nhn vn bn  xut chnh thc ca huyn), Ch tch UBND tnh Thanh Ha  Minh Tun gt ngay:  thi im hin ti, tnh ang u tin pht trin kinh t - x hi cho vng su, vng xa, nng cao i sng ca ngi dn  cc huyn. Quan im tnh khng thng nht v  xut ny. </i></p>\n\n</div><script>(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) return;\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v2.21&appId=178366485681696\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));</script><script>\n!function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)\n{if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?\nn.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};\nif(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version=\'2.0\';\nn.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;\nt.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];\ns.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, document,\'script\',\n\'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js\');\nfbq(\'init\', \'1739154382882652\');\nfbq(\'track\', \'PageView\');\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://plo.vn/thoi-su/theo-dong-thoi-su/tru-so-to-co-lam-dan-giau-len-973614.html\">PLO.VN</a>', 'Tr s to c lm dn giu ln? | Theo dng thi s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tru-so-to-co-lam-dan-giau-len-theo-dong-thoi-su', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:01:53', '2021-03-20 12:01:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tru-so-to-co-lam-da