(937, 1, '2021-03-20 12:02:22', '2021-03-20 12:02:22', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/logo-loa-keo-keo-4-16160659556291625789056.jpeg\" id=\"img_d67\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1500\" alt=\"Vo ch loa ko ko, loa n, loa i y ry, vang xa c... cy s - nh 1.\" title=\"Vo ch loa ko ko, loa n, loa i y ry, vang xa c... cy s - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"d67\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-loa-keo-keo-4-16160659556291625789056.jpeg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Ca hng loa kim tra chic loa ko ko cng sut \"6.000W\" cho khch hng - nh: NGC HIN</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><b><span style=\"\">Vo vng quc loa, l</span><span style=\"\">oa ko ko ht to c no cng c?</span></b></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Con ng Nht To chuyn mua bn cc loi loa my nhn nhp bc nht TP.HCM, xp xnh ting nhc t hng chc ca hng vo bui tra gia tun. Ngay t u ng, cc ca hng  trng ra hng chc mu loa ko ko ln nh vi  thng hiu,  sc mu.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">X toc chic mng co bc v loa mang nhn hiu C. c gii thiu l \"hng California\", nhn vin ca ca hng N. bt </span>bluetooth<span style=\"\"> th chic loa cng sut 100W cho khch hng. </span></p><p class=\"\">Nhc va vang ln cu ht <i>\"mt i lnh nh trng tay yu em nhiu bao nm ngi ci...\"</i>, nam nhn vin lin vn volume ln v tr max v qu quyt m thanh ca chic loa \"xn\" ny vang xa c... cy s. t pht sau, nam nhn vin chuyn tng sang nhc sn, chic loa vang m m khin mng co ca nhng chic loa khc cng git lia la. </p><p class=\"\">\"Loa ko ko ny anh ht gia nh cng sng m chi nhc sn cng ph lun, m thanh sng nn vang i xa lm\" - nam nhn vin ny ni. Vi gi \"cht n\" 8 triu ng, nam nhn vin ny cho bit s bo hnh loa mt nm song khng bo hnh pin.<br/></p><p class=\"\">Cch  khng xa, ca hng Q. cng l ni chuyn bn cc loi loa ko, loa vali, loa bluetooth vi hng hot sn phm xp trn ra ng. M bn beat bn nhc \"<i>Tin bit</i>\", ch qun cm i micro khng dy gii thiu chic loa di ng \"cht\" nht ca hng di c mt vi thi lng pin \"tru\" ln n 5 ting d y l loa i 4 tc. </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/logo-loa-keo-keo-1-16160659564851051222685.jpeg\" id=\"img_decc\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1500\" alt=\"Vo ch loa ko ko, loa n, loa i y ry, vang xa c... cy s - nh 2.\" title=\"Vo ch loa ko ko, loa n, loa i y ry, vang xa c... cy s - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"decc\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-loa-keo-keo-1-16160659564851051222685.jpeg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\"> loi loa,  cng sut v  thng hiu c mt ca hng cho bn vi gi ch 4-5 triu ng/ci. Trong nh: nhn vin ca hng th  vang ca loa cho ngi mua - nh: NGC HIN</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\"><b>Hng Trung Quc, lp rp Vit Nam?</b></span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Theo ch qun, y l chic loa chuyn bn cho nhng ngi mua v cho thu loa ko ko bi cng sut ln ln n \"6.000W\". D loa mang thng hiu, mu logo ca hng loa Bose song ch ca hng cng thng thng chia s y khng phi l hng chnh hng m l hng Trung Quc.</span><br/></p><p class=\"\">\"Hng Bose my chc triu mt ci loa nh xu, lm g c chuyn Bose bn loa ko ko kiu ny. Bo mch, ph kin ca loa c nhp khu t Trung Quc, cn mu m v thng loa c ng, lp rp  Vit Nam\" - ch ca hng ni. </p><p class=\"\">Vi chic loa ny, ca hng ra gi 7,2 triu ng, giao hng tn nh v cam kt \"ht to c no cng c\". Ngoi loa khng ny, ca hng cng bn hng chc mu loa khc vi gi ch t 300.000 ng - 5 triu ng ty theo cng sut v kch c. Theo ch ca hng, rt nhiu loi loa  y  c bn s i cc ni  cho thu ht ko ko, ch thi gian ngn l b li gi vn.</p><p class=\"\">Trong khi , cng vi mu loa i cng sut \"6.000W\", mt ca hng khc li cho gi ch 5 triu ng. \"Mu ny c ch ging nhau, c nhp linh kin t Trung Quc v, rp ln thi. Ch khc nhau mt cht mu m bn ngoi, cn cht lng ging nhau\" -  v ch ca hng L. ni.</p><p class=\"\">D cc loi loa ca ca hng u dn thng hiu cc mu loa uy tn nh JBL, Bose hay cc mu c logo tng t cc thng hiu trn song ch ca hng tha nhn u l hng nhp linh kin v t lp rp.  </p><p class=\"\">Tng t, i din ca hng bn loa T. cng khng nh hin nay rt nhiu loi loa ko ko cng sut ln c cc cng ty nhp bo mch, linh kin v lp rp  Vit Nam, khi b h hng cng phi ch bo mch thay th t Trung Quc.  </p><p class=\"\">Theo tm hiu ca <i>Tui Tr Online</i>, trong danh mc cc sn phm loa ko ko mang cc thng hiu ni ting u khng c mu m, kiu dng nh sn phm \"chnh hng\" ang c nhiu ca hng ti ch Nht To kinh doanh.</p><p class=\"\">Vo nm 2019, Cc iu tra chng bun lu (Tng cc Hi quan) cng  ra quyt nh khi t hnh s v hnh vi bun lu i vi mt doanh nghip ti TP.HCM v hnh vi bun lu loa thng khi nhp hn 600 loa mi 100% t Trung Quc nhng  in sn mt thng hiu Vit Nam. </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p><b>Phn n vi loa ko ko khp ph phng</b></p><p>Hng trm bn c <i>Tui Tr Online</i> v cng phn n vi vic s dng i tr loa cng sut ln ti cc h gia nh, ca hng, siu th, ch, qun nhu hin nay, v t vn volume v khng ai x l. \"Ni  m nh hi ch\".</p><p>C bn c i cm bn, cm xi loa lun; c bn c i nh thu cao; c bn c i kinh doanh loa phi a vo danh mc kinh doanh c iu kin. C bn c  ngh ngang nhin qu th tch thu ht i.</p><p>\"C nh thu loa ko ko tht cao vo, 300-400% l xong\" - bn c Cao Thang  ngh rt ngn gn.</p><p>Ti sao pho cm c m loa ko khng cm c? - bn c Van Chinh hi ngn gn.</p><p>\"V  mu sinh ti lm ngh ny nhng hin ti  ngng, thc s m ni v loa c th di ng nn qu tin li, hu nh nh no gi cng c, to hay nh, nu khng thch mua th thu.  hn ch bt tnh trng ht trn lan ba bi, ti ngh phi c mt s lnh cm, v d nh cm nhp v sn xut loa ko (d to hay nh), cm cho thu hay mua bn, cm ht  khu cng cng, cm ht vo gi ngh tra v n 21h phi kt thc\" - bn c Thienbaongoc.</p></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p><b>a phng cn ra tay quyt lit vi \"Karaoke hung thn\"</b></p><p>Trao i vi <i>Tui Tr Online</i>, i biu Quc hi Phm Vn Ha cho rng cn qun l mnh  gc  nhng ngi mua cc sn phm loa ko ko v  ht h gy ri trt t, an ninh a phng, khu dn c... khi m qu ln, khng tun th quy nh gi gic. </p><p>Theo ng Ha, chnh quyn a phng phi c trch nhim, ra tay v x l nghim khc th \"hung thn karaoke\"  cc a phng s gim. ng Ha cho rng khng nn x l ting n karaoke theo kiu \"u voi ui chut\" m cn lm mt cch thng xuyn, lin tc  khp cc a phng trn c nc  gim mc  nhim ting n t karaoke n mc thp nht.</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/vao-cho-loa-keo-keo-loa-don-loa-doi-day-ray-vang-xa-ca-cay-so-20210318182339557.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Vo ch loa ko ko, loa n, loa i y ry, vang xa c... cy s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vao-cho-loa-keo-keo-loa-don-loa-doi-day-ray-vang-xa-ca-cay-so', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:02:22', '2021-03-20 12:02:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/vao-cho-loa-keo-keo-loa-don-loa-doi-day-ray-vang-xa-ca-cay-so/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(939, 1, '2021-03-20 12:05:01', '2021-03-20 12:05:01', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/dpnhidong23-2read-only-1616038403467951530690.jpg\" id=\"img_d691ba00-879a-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" w=\"1024\" h=\"576\" alt=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: Ngi TP.HCM qu i m p - nh 1.\" title=\"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: Ngi TP.HCM qu i m p - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"d691ba00-879a-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/dpnhidong23-2read-only-1616038403467951530690.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Em nh khm bnh ti khoa h hp Bnh vin Nhi ng 2 (Q.1, TP.HCM) - nh: DUYN PHAN</p></div></div><p>Hng ngy ti vn thng c u  trn Facebook hay nhng trang mng khc v nhng v vic cp git, mc ti... xy ra  ni y. </p><p>Ti  tng ngh ti khng n thnh ph u, s lm! Th nhng, khi ti khng mun n th cuc sng li a y ti phi n. Ti n thnh ph  cha bnh cho con.</p><p>Khi bit tin ti a con ln TP.HCM cha bnh th m ti - ngi cha tng n Si Gn - mi ngy gi in cho ti my ln ch v lo lng ti s gp ngi xu ni t khch. </p><p>Ti vn thng nghe k v taxi thnh ph ny. Nu khng thuc ng, ti x s i lng vng mi mi a mnh n ni cn n. Qu thc, ti cng c phn lo lng. Th nhng, Si Gn chng phi vy!</p><p>Gia nh ti i t sn bay v Bnh vin Nhi ng 2 ht 120.000. Trn ng i, ti ng ngn hi bc ti: \"T y v bnh vin xa khng bc?\". Bc ti x mm ci: \"Hai m con ch cn chp mt mt ci l n  m!\". </p><p>n ni, ti nhn ng h, 6km. Bc ti x a ti tin tha km chai nc lc: \"Chu cm m ung ko bng b con nh th kia, i mua vt v!\". ! u c nh ngi ta vn n kho nhau v taxi Si Gn!</p><p>Khi ang b con t cng bnh vin vo khu khm bnh th ti nghe ting gi git li t pha sau, bc ti x Grab cha v pha ti chic m vi v bo \"Che cho thng b, ko nng!\".</p><p>Ch Chu, ngi c con cng phng bnh vi con ti, nh  y. Nhng lc ngi nh ch ln i ca trng con cho ch v nh, ch li hi \"Trong phng ai cn g khng,  ti mang ln!\".</p><p>Gn hai thng cng con  bnh vin, chng ti chia s vi nhau t hp cm, chai nc lc n ch nm cho con khi phng bnh qu ti. Hai thng, thi gian khng di nu ni l c sng  TP.HCM nhng khng phi l ngn ngi vi nhng ai phi sng  bnh vin. </p><p>Nhng g ng li trong ti v Si Gn l tnh ngi, s m bc, s chia... m by gi, khi ri xa Si Gn v vi qu hng mnh, mi lc c dp ti vn thng ni vi bn b, ngi thn ti rng \"Ngi Si Gn qu i m p!\".</p><p>Si Gn trong ti l chai nc lc ngt mt gia tra nng ca bc ti li taxi. L hp cm nng hi, thm ngon km theo n ci m p ngha tnh ca nhng tm lng nhn i trao gi ni cng bnh vin trong sut nhng thng ngy ti cng con  li bnh vin. </p><p>L<span style=\"\"> cu ni rt i gn gi ca ch va mi quen trn cng chuyn bay t Pleiku xung Si Gn: \"m nay hai m con  c ch no ngh cha, hay l v nh ch!\"</span></p><p>Th y, lm sao ti c th khng yu thnh ph ny cho c?! M khi  l yu Si Gn ri ti li thy thng Si Gn bao nhiu, bi Si Gn lc no cng nh phi gng ln  bao dung, m bc ht thy. Qu ti ngi. Qu ti xe. Qu ti khi bi </p><p>Trong gn mt thng tri con ti nhp vin ti khoa tim mch Bnh vin Nhi ng 2, hng ngy phi chng kin cnh cc con 3-4 a chung 1 ging bnh, phi k ging hnh lang m vn khng  ch. </p><p>Bc s cha xong bnh nhn ny th bnh nhn khc li cn... m ti li c: Gi nh tnh l ni ti sng c th san s bt cho thnh ph ny mt cht thi nhng cht chi, nhng gp gp, qu ti...</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p><b>Mong tip tc nhn c bi vit ca bn c</b></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/11/vig-saigon-bao-dung-2-16154357913961963459857.jpg\" id=\"img_c2c883d0-821f-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"720\" h=\"646\" alt=\"LOGO Saigon bao dung\" title=\"LOGO Saigon bao dung\" rel=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/11/vig-saigon-bao-dung-2-16154357913961963459857.jpg\" photoid=\"c2c883d0-821f-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/11/vig-saigon-bao-dung-2-16154357913961963459857.jpg\"/></div></div><p>Tnh n ngy 17-3, a ch email saigon@tuoitre.com.vn ca cuc thi vit \"Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh\"  nhn c 170 email ca bn c khp mi min t nc cng nh  nc ngoi gi nh, bi vit v d thi.</p><p>Bo Tui Tr trn trng cm n s nhit tnh hng ng cuc thi v mong tip tc nhn c nhng bi vit t bn c.</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/sai-gon-bao-dung-tp-hcm-nghia-tinh-nguoi-tp-hcm-qua-doi-am-ap-20210318103551769.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Si Gn bao dung - TP.HCM ngha tnh: Ngi TP.HCM qu i m p', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sai-gon-bao-dung-tp-hcm-nghia-tinh-nguoi-tp-hcm-qua-doi-am-ap', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:05:01', '2021-03-20 12:05:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/sai-gon-bao-dung-tp-hcm-nghia-tinh-nguoi-tp-hcm-qua-doi-am-ap/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(940, 1, '2021-03-20 12:08:28', '2021-03-20 12:08:28', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/thanh-pho-thong-minh-da-lat-1read-only-161603445586311033008.jpg\" id=\"img_a4447360-878d-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" w=\"1024\" h=\"575\" alt=\"Hng ti Vit Nam s: Doanh nghip t  ng vai tr dn dt - nh 1.\" title=\"Hng ti Vit Nam s: Doanh nghip t  ng vai tr dn dt - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a4447360-878d-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/thanh-pho-thong-minh-da-lat-1read-only-161603445586311033008.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Trung tm iu hnh thng minh ti thnh ph  Lt (Lm ng) do VNPT xy dng v vn hnh - nh: THANH H</p></div></div><p> n do B K hoch v u t xy dng. By doanh nghip nh nc ang c  xut tham gia th im u l nhng ci tn ni bt  bn lnh vc cng nghip cng ngh cao, nng lng ti to, cng bin v logistics, ti chnh - ngn hng.</p><p><b>Thc y i mi<span style=\"\">sng to</span></b></p><p>ng L Mnh Hng, cc trng Cc Pht trin doanh nghip (B K hoch v u t), cho bit  n tp trung vo hai mc tiu chnh.</p><p>Th nht, cng c, pht trin mt s tp on kinh t quy m ln trn c s hnh thnh cc chui lin kt, chui gi tr, thc y i mi sng to vi nh hng s dng hiu qu ngun lc cha khai thc ht ca doanh nghip nh nc, thu ht cc ngun lc ca khu vc t nhn  thc hin vai tr dn dt.</p><p>Th hai, hnh thnh c ch, chnh sch nhm to iu kin thun li  Nh nc/doanh nghip nh nc tham gia u t pht trin trong mt s ngnh, lnh vc c tnh cht m ng, bt ph nhm thc hin mc tiu ca chin lc pht trin kinh t - x hi ca t nc.</p><p>Vi bn tiu ch la chn ngnh, lnh vc nghin cu th im bao gm c tnh cht m ng, dn dt, hng ti lm ch cng ngh s, ng thi c vai tr cn thit trong pht trin, nh hng cng nghip v cn thit duy tr s hin din ca Nh nc, cc doanh nghip nh nc c la chn nghin cu th im phi c tng ti sn trn 20.000 t ng, chim th phn t 30% tr ln, bo m cc quy nh v cnh tranh; c qun tr tt trn c s nguyn tc OECD...</p><p>Da trn cc tiu ch ny, B K hoch v u t cho bit ang  xut la chn bn lnh vc v  xut by doanh nghip nh nc tham gia th im.</p><p>C th nhn thy s k vng vo vai tr dn dt, m ng ca cc doanh nghip nh nc, nht l hng ti lm ch cng ngh s  mt trong ba doanh nghip thuc lnh vc cng nghip cng ngh cao c la chn th im l Tp on Bu chnh vin thng Vit Nam (VNPT).</p><p>VNPT l doanh nghip nh nc  ng  top 3 trong s 50 thng hiu gi tr nht Vit Nam, theo kt qu ca tp ch Forbes Vit Nam.</p><p>Trc , theo bo co ca Brand Finance - nh t vn nh gi thng hiu hng u th gii, VNPT l thng hiu tng trng n tng nht trong s 150 nh mng ln trn ton cu v c mc tng hng mnh nht trong top 4 thng hiu vin thng ln nht Vit Nam.</p><p><b>Ch ng<span style=\"\">trong chuyn i s</span></b></p><p>Trong bi cnh th trng vin thng  chng li v cnh tranh gay gt, Tp on VNPT  chuyn i mnh m t nh cung cp dch v vin thng thnh tp on cng ngh cao, nh cung cp dch v s, tin phong trong chuyn i s quc gia.</p><p>Chnh s nhanh nhy, quyt lit, ch ng v sng to ca lnh o tp on khi la chn hng i, c nhng bc t ph  to ra bc chuyn i mang tnh quyt nh ny.</p><p>\"VNPT  sm xy dng v tp trung trin khai chin lc VNPT 4.0 vi mc tiu chuyn i s VNPT t nh cung cp dch v vin thng sang nh cung cp dch v s, phn u tr thnh nh cung cp dch v s hng u ti Vit Nam v tch cc tham gia trong cc hot ng chuyn i s chnh quyn cc cp, chuyn i s cc doanh nghip\" - ng Phm c Long, ch tch VNPT, chia s..</p><p>Tp on  ch ng tham gia cc chng trnh s ha quc gia, khng nh vai tr dn dt, ch lc ca mt doanh nghip nh nc trong vic xy dng, cung cp dch v, h thng s, CNTT cho cc c quan chnh ph, cc doanh nghip...</p><p>Trong  phi k n nhng nn tng s quan trng nht ca quc gia nh Trc lin thng vn bn quc gia; H thng thng tin bo co quc gia v Trung tm thng tin, ch o, iu hnh ca Chnh ph, Cng dch v cng quc gia, C s d liu quc gia v dn c...</p><p>ng Hunh Quang Lim - quyn tng gim c Tp on VNPT - cng cho bit: n nay, Trung tm iu hnh thng minh (IOC)  c VNPT trin khai cho khong 30 tnh, thnh ph trn ton quc. Trong  nhiu tnh thnh  a vo vn hnh nh: Lm ng, H Nam, Cao Bng, TP H Giang, Ty Ninh, Ph Th, Tr Vinh, Kon Tum, Qung Bnh, Qung Nam, Bnh Phc, Ha Bnh, Kin Giang, Lo Cai, Bc Kn...</p><p>\"Khng ch tin phong, pht huy vai tr dn t trong chuyn i s quc gia, VNPT cn ch ng chuyn i s chnh mnh  tr thnh in hnh, m hnh mu trong vic chuyn i s doanh nghip. Chng ti ang hng n mc tiu tr thnh nh cung cp dch v s hng u ti Vit Nam vo nm 2025 v tr thnh trung tm s (digital hub) ca chu  vo nm 2030\" - ng Lim khng nh.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p><b>B trng B K hoch v u t Nguyn Ch Dng:</b></p><p><b>Hnh thnh chui gi tr</b></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption active\" type=\"Photo\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/bo-truong-bo-khdt-nguyen-chi-dung-anh-viet-dung-1472114760-1read-only-1616034479074719305440.jpg\" id=\"img_b20d59d0-878d-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" w=\"1024\" h=\"576\" alt=\"bo-truong-bo-khdt-nguyen-chi-dung-anh-viet-dung-1472114760 1(read-only)\" title=\"bo-truong-bo-khdt-nguyen-chi-dung-anh-viet-dung-1472114760 1(read-only)\" rel=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/bo-truong-bo-khdt-nguyen-chi-dung-anh-viet-dung-1472114760-1read-only-1616034479074719305440.jpg\" photoid=\"b20d59d0-878d-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/bo-truong-bo-khdt-nguyen-chi-dung-anh-viet-dung-1472114760-1read-only-1616034479074719305440.jpg\"/></div></div><p>\"Ti mun nhn mnh vai tr ca doanh nghip nh nc phi thc s l nhng con chim u n, dn dt, lan ta khu vc doanh nghip khc. Mi tp on, tng cng ty phi l mt trung tm i mi sng to, y mi l mang tnh dn dt. </p><p>ng thi phi xy dng c mt h sinh thi, hnh thnh c chui gi tr  cc thnh phn kinh t khc bm theo v pht trin. Ngoi ra, phi h tr, tng tc, b sung cho cc khu vc kinh t khc, nht l khu vc kinh t t nhn trong nc\".</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://congnghe.tuoitre.vn/huong-toi-viet-nam-so-doanh-nghiep-ti-do-dong-vai-tro-dan-dat-202103180931373.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Hng ti Vit Nam s: Doanh nghip t  ng vai tr dn dt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'huong-toi-viet-nam-so-doanh-nghiep-ti-do-dong-vai-tro-dan-dat', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:08:28', '2021-03-20 12:08:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/huong-toi-viet-nam-so-doanh-nghiep-ti-do-dong-vai-tro-dan-dat/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
