(942, 1, '2021-03-20 12:09:38', '2021-03-20 12:09:38', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HIV/AIDS l cn bnh khin nhn loi au u bi cha th tm ra cch tiu dit hon ton. Mt khi b nhim, ngi bnh s phi chung sng c phn i cn li vi virus. Thuc c ch virus l th duy nht c th ngn HIV nhn ln v hn ch nguy c bnh chuyn sang giai on cui - AIDS. Vic pht hin ngi b HIV/AIDS cng kh kh khn, nht l khi nhiu trng hp pht trin bnh m thm hng thp k.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai on khng triu chng</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pht hin ngi nhim HIV gp kh khn  ch a phn  giai on u, bnh nhn thng khng pht hin mnh b bnh. Theo Trung tm Kim sot v Phng nga Dch bnh M (CDC), cc triu chng HIV giai on u (giai on nguyn pht) c th xut hin t 2-4 tun sau khi mt ngi tip xc ngun ly. Nhng triu chng ny c th ko di vi tun.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhin, mt s trng hp ch c biu hin trong vi ngy hoc thm ch khng xut hin triu chng lm sng. D vy, h vn c th truyn virus cho ngi khc thng qua cc con ng nh quan h tnh dc, mu, ly t m sang con</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thng k t CDC cho thy hu ht (hn 80%) ngi b nhim HIV giai on u s c triu chng tng t cm, bao gm: St, au hng, pht ban trn c th, s mi, mt mi, au khp, au c, vim</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">y l du hiu cho thy h thng min dch ang chin u  chng li virus. Tuy nhin, iu  khng c ngha mi ngi c triu chng trn u l bnh nhn HIV. Nhng triu chng ny cn tng ng vi ngi mc COVID-19, cm cm, nhim trng</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nu gp cc triu chng trn v cho rng mnh c nguy c nhim HIV, bn nn i xt nghim sng lc. Bi sau , c th s tri qua giai on khng triu chng, khin chng ta v tnh b st c hi vng  iu tr.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-holdclass=\"\"><img alt=\"Du hiu cnh bo HIV ang pht trin m thm trong c th - 1\" height=\"440\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"440\" data-id=\"1548181\" data-detail=\"1\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/shutterstock1147672529-06192937.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"0\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\" data-holdclass=\"\"> giai on u, nhiu bnh nhn HIV gp triu chng tng t cm nh st, pht ban trn da, au ngi, mt mi... (nh: Shutter Stock).</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai on mt tri qua, hu ht ngi nhim HIV s tr li bnh thng, cm thy khe hn. Nhng iu  khng c ngha virus bin mt. S bo v mnh m ca h min dch trn mi c th s lm gim s lng cc ht virus trong mu v chuyn sang giai on nhim HIV khng triu chng. Cc bc s cn gi y l giai on nhim HIV mn tnh hay tim n.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo T chc HIV M, thi gian ly nhim HIV tim n c th ko di 10 ti 15 nm. Nhim trng tim n v mt lm sng c th pht trin n giai on 3 v giai on cui ca HIV - cn gi l AIDS. Nguy c din bin nng l rt cao nu bnh nhn khng c iu tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong giai on nhim HIV mn tnh, nng  virus tng dn trong c th, n ph hy t bo min dch T-CD4. S lng CD4 st gim nhanh chng, cho thy tn thng ngy cng nng. Bnh nhn cn phi c iu tr bng thuc khng virus (ART)  ngn khng cho virus tip tc tn cng h min dch.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nu khng c iu tr, HIV thng pht trin thnh AIDS (hi chng suy gim min dch mc phi) sau 8-10 nm. Lc ny, s lng t bo CD4 gim xung mc di 200 t bo/1 mm3 mu, qu trnh min dch b v hiu ha v xut hin cc nhim trng do vi sinh vt c hi gy ra.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bnh nhn s gp phi triu chng st, mt mi, sng hch bch huyt, tiu chy, st cn bt thng, nhim trng ming (ta li, ming), zona thn kinh (herpes zoster), vim phi... Ngoi ra, h cng c kh nng b nhim trng do vi khun, virus, nm gy ra v c th khng  sc chng li cc tc nhn nguy him.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chng c gi l bnh nhim trng c hi, bao gm sarcoma Kaposi (mt dng ung th da); nhim nm Cadida species gy nm ming hoc nhim vi khun hiu kh Mycobacterium tuberculosis gy bnh lao. Sau , cc virus Herpes tim n s c kch hot gy ti pht ngy cng nng nhng tn thng do Herpes simplex, bnh zona thn kinh, ung th hch bch huyt do virus Epstein-Barr hoc ung th Kaposis sarcoma.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Trung tm Kim sot v Phng nga Dch bnh M, nu khng c iu tr, nhng ngi b AIDS thng ch sng st thm khong 3 nm.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-holdclass=\"\"><img alt=\"Du hiu cnh bo HIV ang pht trin m thm trong c th - 2\" height=\"438\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"438\" data-id=\"1548182\" data-detail=\"1\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/rokkols7vi-06192962.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"1\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\" data-holdclass=\"\">Bnh nhn HIV cng iu tr sm, c hi ko di s sng v ngn bnh chuyn thnh AIDS cng cao. (nh: Shutter Stock).</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lm g khi b nhim HIV?</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bt k ai cng c nguy c nhim virus HIV khi tip xc mt s loi dch c th mang trng nh mu, tinh dch, dch tin tinh hon, dch m o, dch trc trng v sa m. Ri ro ln nht gy nhim HIV l quan h tnh dc khng an ton hoc dng chung kim tim vi ngi nhim bnh.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi pht hin b nhim HIV, bn cng khng nn bi quan. Bi n ch n thun l cn bnh m khoa hc cha tm ra thuc cha tr. Kt qu xt nghim dng tnh vi HIV cho thy ang c virus ny  trong mu ca bn. Thc t, nhiu ngi nhim HIV vn sng hon ton bnh thng khe mnh trong nhiu nm.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti liu ca Cc phng, chng HIV/AIDS, B Y t, php lut Vit Nam quy nh sau khi pht hin b nhim HIV, bnh nhn cn c trch nhim thng bo cho v hoc chng v iu ny. Tuy nhin, bn khng c ngha v phi ni iu  cho bt k ai khc v vn c th lm vic, tham gia cc hot ng x hi bnh thng, ngoi tr nhng trng hp c quy nh trong php lut.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngi nhim HIV cng cn ch ng hn ch mt s hot ng hoc p dng bin php phng nga  khng lm ly nhim HIV/AIDS cho ngi khc nh quan h tnh dc phi s dng bao cao su; khng nn c con; khm sc khe nh k; tham kho  kin bc s  c ch dn mt s loi thuc nh AZT (Zidovudine), DDI (Didanosin), Lamivudine, Indinaviz, c tc dng lm chm qu trnh pht trin ca virus.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/dau-hieu-canh-bao-hiv-dang-phat-trien-am-tham-trong-co-the-ar601794.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'Du hiu cnh bo HIV ang pht trin m thm trong c th', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dau-hieu-canh-bao-hiv-dang-phat-trien-am-tham-trong-co-the', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:09:38', '2021-03-20 12:09:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/dau-hieu-canh-bao-hiv-dang-phat-trien-am-tham-trong-co-the/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(943, 1, '2021-03-20 12:10:45', '2021-03-20 12:10:45', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chiu 19-3, B Ni v t chc hp bo nh k cung cp thng tin cho bo ch. Nhiu cu hi lin quan n trng hp b nhim b Trn Huyn Trang, con gi b th Tnh y Vnh Phc, lm ph gim c S KH&amp;T khi mi 31 tui v tnh trng lon vn bng, chng ch  c nu ra.</p>\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"item-photo\"><img alt=\"S sa quy nh v cc chng ch lin quan n vin chc - nh 1\" src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/w800/Uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/p4chinh_ueuz.jpg\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/p4chinh_ueuz.jpg\" cms-photo-caption=\"B Ni v tr li bo ch chiu 19-3. nh: TN\"/><br/>&#13;\n<em class=\"image_caption\">B Ni v tr li bo ch chiu 19-3. nh: TN</em></p>\n<p><b style=\"text-align: justify;\">S lm r tiu chun gim c, ph gim c s</b><br/>&#13;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V trng hp tnh Vnh Phc b nhim ph gim c S KH&amp;T l con gi b th Tnh y khi mi 31 tui, V trng V Cng chc, vin chc Trng Hi Long cho hay theo quy nh ca ng v php lut hin hnh v cng tc cn b, chc danh ph gim c s thuc thm quyn quyt nh ca Ban Thng v Tnh y v UBND cp tnh. </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vic b nhim phi bo m ng cc quy nh ca ng, Chnh ph v quy nh ca a phng v cng tc cn b - ng Long ni.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C th, v tiu chun, theo ng Long, B Chnh tr c Quy nh 89 v khung tiu chun chc danh, nh hng khung tiu ch nh gi i vi cc chc danh lnh o qun l cc cp. Theo , tiu chun chung gm tiu chun v chuyn mn, chnh tr, trnh  qun l nh nc v tiu chun v ngoi ng, tin hc ph hp.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy nh 89 cng giao tnh y, thnh y quy nh c th tiu chun cc chc danh do c quan ny qun l nhng khng c thp hn quy nh chung ca ng v Chnh ph.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cc b, ngnh, a phng c quyn quy nh tiu chun cao hn. Khi p dng, h phi thc hin theo ng quy nh ca mnh, khng th vin l do v quy nh chung khng c nn khng thc hin - vn li ng Long.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ng Long thng tin thm: Tnh y Vnh Phc  c vn bn gi B Ni v v cc c quan c thm quyn ca ng (Ban T chc Trung ng, y ban Kim tra Trung ng, Ban Tuyn gio) lin quan n cng tc b nhim cn b thuc trng hp Ban Thng v Tnh y qun l. Trong vn bn ny c bo co lin quan n trng hp b Trn Huyn Trang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V Cng chc, vin chc  lm vic vi cc c quan chuyn mn ca tnh,  ngh r sot, bo co cc trng hp tng t  Vnh Phc. B Ni v s kim tra, nh gi, bo co cp c thm quyn v thng tin cho bo ch sau - ng Long ni.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gii p thm sau , Th trng Ni v Nguyn Duy Thng cho bit b trng Ni v  ban hnh quy nh v v tr vic lm cc c quan hnh chnh ca cc tnh. Ngh nh 62 ca Chnh ph phn cp li cho cc a phng c th iu chnh tiu chun .</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> ngh V Cng chc, vin chc, Thanh tra b trao i thm vi Vnh Phc xem v tr vic lm, tiu chun c th gim c, ph gim c s yu cu ngch cng chc ti thiu l g. Nu cha c quy nh c th ca a phng th phi cn c theo quyt nh ca b trng Ni v - ng Thng ni.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Chng ch ngh nghip: Rc ri do thiu quy nh chuyn tip</b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cng ti cuc hp bo, bo ch nu nhiu cu hi lin quan n nhng bt cp trong vic yu cu cc chng ch chc danh ngh nghip ca vin chc, trong  c gio vin. </p>\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sng 19-3, Th tng va ch o B Ni v ch tr, phi hp vi cc b, ngnh sa Ngh nh 101 ca Chnh ph v o to, bi dng cn b, cng chc, vin chc v cc quy nh khc c lin quan n cc chng ch thng hng vin chc, trong  c gio vin. Vy vic sa i ngh nh ny s c thc hin ra sao, theo hng no? - bo ch hi.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr li, Th trng Ni v Nguyn Duy Thng cho bit vic ny lin quan n Ngh nh 18/2010 (sau l Ngh nh 101/2017) c ban hnh trn c s Lut Vin chc 2010.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nm 2019, Quc hi sa Lut Cn b, cng chc; Lut Vin chc c nhiu im mi. Theo , Chnh ph ban hnh Ngh nh 106 v Ngh nh 62 v v tr vic lm i vi cng chc v vin chc, trong  quy nh v tr vic lm gm m t cng vic, xc nh khung nng lc Ngh nh cng phn cp thm quyn cho b qun l chuyn ngnh quy nh c th v tr vic lm v m t, xc nh khung nng lc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ng Thng, i vi gio vin, B GD&amp;T chu trch nhim vic ny v ng nhin phi thng nht vi B Ni v. Ti ch lu  V Cng chc, vin chc khi xy dng cc vn bn, k c ngh nh, thng t, phi c ni dung quy nh chuyn tip. Tt c phn nh c vn  hin nay l do thiu quy nh chuyn tip - ng Thng ni.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dn chng vic mt chuyn vin cao cp chng may thiu chng ch chuyn vin chnh, bt h hc li chuyn vin chnh l khng thc tin, ng Thng nhn mnh nu khng c quy nh chuyn tip c ngha l vn bn c hiu lc hi t.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th trng Ni v cng nhc li tinh thn ch o ca Th tng yu cu r sot tng th cc chng ch  xc nh chng ch no dng  b nhim, nng ngch; chng ch no mang tnh cht bi dng nghip v, chuyn mn vi ngha cp nht kin thc; ci no bt buc, ci no khuyn khch. Cng chc chuyn ngnh ca cc b nh thu, hi quan, kho bc, ngn hng, thanh tra cng cn tng r sot ton b - ng Thng ni.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border: 1px solid black; background-color: #eee; margin: 5px; border-collapse: collapse;\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td style=\"background-color: #eee;\">&#13;\n            <p><b>Vnh Phc cha c bo co mi v v vic</b></p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V trng hp  Vnh Phc, bo ch truy: C th v quy trnh khng sai nhng ch trong by nm, t mt chuyn vin ln ti v tr ph gim c, tnh c thi gian i hc, nh vy c m bo theo quy nh ca lut? </p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th trng Ni v Nguyn Duy Thng cho bit Quy nh 105 nm 2017 ca B Chnh tr v phn cp qun l cn b v b nhim, gii thiu cn b ng c; Ngh nh 138 v tuyn dng, s dng v qun l cng chc khng quy nh tui ti thiu khi b nhim, ch quy nh  tui ti a. ng thi, khng quy nh c th v thi gian cng tc. </p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bo ch truy tip: Cch y t ngy, c thng tin Tnh y Vnh Phc  hp v a ra hng x l i vi trng hp b Trang. B  nhn c bo co v hng x l ca tnh cha?.</p>&#13;\n            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V trng V Cng chc, vin chc khng nh B Ni v cha nhn c bo co mi ca Vnh Phc v vic ny.</p>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">					<article class=\"article-related clearfix cms-relate\">                            <figure class=\"thumb\">                              <img src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/170x123/uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/ongnguyenduythangqzkithumb_fpfb.jpg\" alt=\"Vnh Phc cha bo co v b nhim con gi B th Tnh y\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/ongnguyenduythangqzkithumb_fpfb.jpg\"/>                            </figure>&#13;\n<header>&#13;\nVnh Phc cha bo co v b nhim con gi B th Tnh y&#13;\n</header>&#13;\n<p>(PLO)- Cc cu hi lin quan n trng hp b nhim b Trn Huyn Trang - Ph Gim c S 31 tui, con gi B th Tnh u Vnh Phc lm nng cuc hp bo nh k ca B Ni v.</p>&#13;\n</article></p>\n\n</div><script>(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) return;\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v2.21&appId=178366485681696\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));</script><script>\n!function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)\n{if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?\nn.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};\nif(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version=\'2.0\';\nn.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;\nt.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];\ns.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, document,\'script\',\n\'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js\');\nfbq(\'init\', \'1739154382882652\');\nfbq(\'track\',