(945, 1, '2021-03-20 12:11:43', '2021-03-20 12:11:43', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<div>Kt qu trn c PSSI thng bo sau khi c kt qu xt nghim vo ti 19.3. Ngay sau ,, PSSI lp tc a ra cc bin php ra sot nhm trnh ly lan Covid-19 trong ni b thnh vintuyn Indonesia.</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"HLV ngi Hn Quc ca tuyn Indonesia bt ng dnh Covid-19 - nh 1\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/taynguyen/2021_03_20/pssi_uxgu.jpeg\" caption=\"HLV ngi Hn Quc ca tuyn Indonesia bt ng dnh Covid-19 - nh 1\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Cc tuyn Indonesia ang cho thy s tin b di thi HLV Shin Tae-yong</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>\"Lc u, ng Shin Tae-yong hm 18.3 cho bit rng ng y khng c khe. Sau , theo ch o ca Ch tch PSSI, ng y  c kim tra PCR. Kt qu ch c cng b vo ti th su (19.3), quyn Tng th k PSSI Yunus Nusi cho bit. Theo PSSI, sau khi kt thc t hun luyn vo hm 8.3, cc cu th, hun luyn vin v quan chc ca tuyn U.23 Indonesia cng  c yu cu kim tra PCR. Cc kt qu u m tnh, nn cc cu th, HLV v cc quan chc tr v nh, trong  c ng Shin Tae-yong.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, hm 18.3, HLV Shin Tae-yong  ni cho bc s ca i tuyn quc gia bit ng khng c khe. Bc s sau   lm xt nghim PCR v kt qu a ra vo ti 19.3 v kt qu l dng tnh.</p>\n<div>Yunus tin rng trong th gii th thao, c bit l bng , cc cu th v HLV nhim Covid-19 l iu khng c g ng lo ngi. Siu sao ca Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo v tin o Zlatan Ibrahimovic ca AC Milan cng  nhim vi Covid-19 v n khng mt nhiu thi gian  hi phc. Tng t, HLV Mikel Arteta ca Arsenal cng b nh hng v bnh phc. Nu mt VV hoc mt cu VV nh trng hp HLV Shin Tae-yong b nhim, ti chc chn rng ng y s nhanh chng hi phc. iu quan trng nht l phi iu tr ngay lp tc, ng Yunus ni thm.</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"HLV ngi Hn Quc ca tuyn Indonesia bt ng dnh Covid-19 - nh 2\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/taynguyen/2021_03_20/beto-dl_krie_uavl.jpg\" caption=\"HLV ngi Hn Quc ca tuyn Indonesia bt ng dnh Covid-19 - nh 2\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Tuyn Indonesia (o ) s ti u vi Vit Nam vo thng 6</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>Hin ti, HLV Shin Tae-yong ang nhn c nhiu k vng ca PSSI  vc dy cc tuyn quc gia. Ngoi vic sm chun b cho tuyn U.22+2 nhm n chic huy chng vng SEA Games nm nay ti Vit Nam, tuyn quc gia nc ny c th s c ci t di thi chin lc gia ngi Hn Quc, trong  trc mt l 3 trn u cn li bng G vng loi th 2 World Cup 2022/VCK Asian Cup 2023 (thi u th thc tp trung ti UAE) ln lt gp Thi Lan (ngy 3.6), Vit Nam (7.6) v ch nh UAE (11.6). </div>\n<p>Hin  bng G, Indonesia ang ng cui bng sau khi cha c im no vi 5 tht bi.</p>\n\n<!-- Begin Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n<!-- End Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div><script>\n//window.fbAsyncInit = function() {\n// FB.init({\n// appId : \'288067561729014\',\n// autoLogAppEvents : true,\n// xfbml : true,\n// version : \'v2.10\'\n// });\n// FB.AppEvents.logPageView();\n//};\n(function(d, s, id){\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) {return;}\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src = \"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));\n</script><script>\nwindow.fbAsyncInit = function() {\nFB.init({\nappId : \'288067561729014\',\nautoLogAppEvents : true,\nxfbml : true,\nversion : \'v3.1\'\n});\n};\n(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) { return; }\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src = \"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/the-thao/bong-da-quoc-te/hlv-nguoi-han-quoc-cua-tuyen-indonesia-bat-ngo-dinh-covid-19-131729t.html\">Bo Thanh Nin</a>', 'HLV ngi Hn Quc ca tuyn Indonesia bt ng dnh Covid-19 | Bng  Quc t', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hlv-nguoi-han-quoc-cua-tuyen-indonesia-bat-ngo-dinh-covid-19-bong-da-quoc-te', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:11:43', '2021-03-20 12:11:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/hlv-nguoi-han-quoc-cua-tuyen-indonesia-bat-ngo-dinh-covid-19-bong-da-quoc-te/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
