(947, 1, '2021-03-20 12:12:13', '2021-03-20 12:12:13', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"VideoStream\" data-advmode=\"5\" data-src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=tuoitre&amp;new_info_domain=true&amp;stgdmn=hls.tuoitre.vn&amp;vid=tuoitre/2021/3/18/video-xe-buyt-chen-nhau-1616055248331280858583-074f3.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;poster=https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/xebuytdoanhoa-16160554031361668889421.png&amp;_info=f55f664087c111eb8dbdd5e95a2108c7\" data-width=\"600px\" data-height=\"400px\" id=\"videoid_104795\" videoid=\"104795\" videoexternalid=\"0\"><div class=\"VideoCMS_Caption\"><p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Hai xe but chn nhau trn quc l 1 - VIDEO: HNG PHNG</p></div></div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"\">Chiu 18-3, thng tin t i cnh st giao thng, trt t Cng an TP Vinh, Ngh An cho bit n v ny  lp bin bn, a hai chic xe but ca hai hng chn nhau trn quc l 1 v tr s  x l.</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Trc , trn mng x hi xut hin mt on video di gn 2 pht ghi li cnh hai chic xe but rt ui, chn nhau trn quc l 1, on qua ng Trn Ph, TP Vinh vo sng 18-3.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong on video, chic xe but ca hng Khanh Qunh chy tuyn TP Vinh -  Lng t nhin tng tc vt ln chic xe but chy cng chiu ca hng Thch Thnh.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi vt ln, chic xe but hng Khanh Qunh quay cho xe, chn p xe but ca hng Thch Thnh. C nhng thi im chic xe dng hn, chnngang ng khin cc phng tin khc khng th lu thng.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Khng t ln chic xe but hng Thch Thnh tm cch lch ra ri vt ln i tip. Mt lc sau chic xe but Khanh Qunh mi  cho xe but Thch Thnh i.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">S vic din ra trong khong 20 pht khin ngi i ng b mt phen tht tim.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/logo-xebuytdoanhoa-16160555608021130977946.png\" id=\"img_edf5\" w=\"1366\" h=\"920\" alt=\"Hai xe but chn nhau nh phim trn quc l, ngi i ng khip va - nh 2.\" title=\"Hai xe but chn nhau nh phim trn quc l, ngi i ng khip va - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"edf5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-xebuytdoanhoa-16160555608021130977946.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Hai xe but chn nhau trn quc l 1, on qua ng Trn Ph, TP Vinh khin nhiu ngi i ng bc xc - nh: H.PHNG</p></div></div><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Nhiu ngi dng mng x hi by t bt bnh trc hnh vi coi thng php lut, coi thng tnh mng hnh khch v ngi tham gia giao thng ca cc ti x, ng thi yu cu lc lng chc nng phi x l nghim.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ch P.H. - ngi i xe my gn hai chic xe but - k li: \"Sng nay ti va thot cht. Khi va ch con i hc v, ti i qua ng Trn Ph, thy hai xe but vt v ui nhau, cng p chn ga nh phim hnh ng. Nu ti khng x l kp thi th by gi  vo vin ri. Ti ngh trng hp ny ch hay xem trn mng, nhng khng ng mnh gp  ngoi ng\".</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo gim c ca hai nh xe xc nhn c s vic trn, tuy nhin v vic khng phi do tranh ginh khch m xut pht t va chm giao thng trc  gia hai xe but. Hai nh xe ny ang yu cu hai ti x tng trnh  x l.</p><div type=\"RelatedOneNews\" class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\">              <img style=\"float: left; width: 150px; height: 120px; margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/150_120/2020/11/3/hailong-1604409373117560967629-crop-1604409471447198992173.jpg\" alt=\"Xe but cha hiu qu\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/150_120/2020/11/3/hailong-1604409373117560967629-crop-1604409471447198992173.jpg\"/>     Xe but cha hiu qu     <p class=\"VCObjectBoxRelatedNewsItemSapo\">TTO - Ti k hp th 17 HND TP.HCM din ra vo cui nm 2019, thng tin v tnh trng  nhim, gim c S TN-MT cho bit TP.HCM c hin tng m quang ha bi  nhim t giao thng.</p> </div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/hai-xe-buyt-chen-nhau-nhu-phim-tren-quoc-lo-nguoi-di-duong-khiep-via-20210318151822536.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Hai xe but chn nhau nh phim trn quc l, ngi i ng khip va', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hai-xe-buyt-chen-nhau-nhu-phim-tren-quoc-lo-nguoi-di-duong-khiep-via', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:12:13', '2021-03-20 12:12:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/hai-xe-buyt-chen-nhau-nhu-phim-tren-quoc-lo-nguoi-di-duong-khiep-via/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
