(949, 1, '2021-03-20 12:12:48', '2021-03-20 12:12:48', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/logo-dscf3364-1-1616056441515659234088.jpg\" id=\"img_1cc5\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"VN-Index vt 1.200 im - nh 1.\" title=\"VN-Index vt 1.200 im - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dscf3364-1-1616056441515659234088.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">\"Gic m\" vt 1.200 im  chnh thc thnh hin thc trong phin giao dch 18-3 - nh: BNG MAI</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Ngay khi m u phin giao dch, cc ch s chng khon u din bin trong sc xanh, dng tin  vo dn dp y hng lot c phiu tng gi mnh. </p><p class=\"\">Trong , cng u gip th trng tng trng tt thuc v nhiu gng mt ca nhm ngn hng nh Vietcombank (VCB), BIDV (BID), Techcombank (TCB), Vietinbank (CTG), VPBank (VPB)...</p><p class=\"\">Lc y th trng i ln cn nh vo dng tin chy mnh v mua c phiu ca cc doanh nghip c vn ha ln nh <span style=\"\">Vingroup (VIC), Vinamilk (VNM), Cng nghip cao su Vit Nam (VNM), Vietnam Airlines (HVN)...</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Tri qua ging co, b p lc khng nh n t tnh trng nghn lnh trn sn HSX do S Giao dch chng khon TP.HCM (HOSE) qun l, nhng cui cng</span><span style=\"\"> VN-Index cng cng ph thnh cng ct mc lch s, vn ln </span><span style=\"\">1.200,94 im (</span><span style=\"\">+14,85 im, +1,25%). Tng gi tr giao dch ton sn t hn </span><span style=\"\">15.406 t ng. </span><span style=\"\">Ln u VN-Index t mc ny l vo ngy 9-4-2018 nhng khng gi c lu.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">R VN30 tng 18,09 im (+1,52%) ln 1.211,54 im, vi 24/30 thnh vin tng gi. Sn HNX v r HNX30 tng ln lt 0,93 im (+0,34%) ln 277,48 im v 5,57 im (+1,39%) ln</span><span style=\"\">405,27 im.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">C th thy nh u t c nhn trong nc c cng rt ln trong vic nng  th trng. Bi ring hm nay, khi ngoi  bn rng hn</span><span style=\"\"> 343 t ng, ng thi hm nay cng tr thnh phin 20 lin tip khi ngoi rt rng khi chng khon Vit Nam vi tng gi tr khong 11.500 t ng.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">ng Nguyn Th Minh - gim c phn tch Cng ty chng khon Yuanta Vit Nam - nhn nh trong khong 2</span><span style=\"\"> phin giao dch gn y th trng c im sng l dng tin quay li mua c phiu vn ha ln, trong  tp trung vo c phiu ngn hng, iu ny  gp phn gip VN-Index tng ln 1.200 im. </span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Tuy nhin, </span><span style=\"\"> nh gi VN-Index c th vt hon ton mc 1.200 im, tin ln nhng mc cao hn hay khng phi ch thm vi phin tip theo, khi ch s ny tng thm 7 - 10% so vi mc 1.200 km thanh khon cao.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">\"Vic VN-Index vt qua 1.200</span><span style=\"\"> s gip gii ta tm l lo s ca nh u t, nhiu ngi c chin lc mi, mnh dn mua vo v nm gi c phiu. Tnhtheo thanh khon bnh qun giao dch trong ngy, nh u t nc ngoi chim xp x 10 - 12%. Do </span><span style=\"\"> nh u t trong nc ang nm vai tr ch o, hm nay  lp cng ln a th trng i ln\", ng Minh phn tch.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Trong ngy, xt theo lnh vc, nhm tng trng mnh theo th t tng dn ln lt thuc v nhm cng ngh thng tin, nguyn vt liu, cng nghip, hng tiu dng, bt ng sn, hng tiu dng thit yu, ti chnh. </span></p><p class=\"\">Ring nhm chm sc sc khe, dch v tin ch, nng lng vn  chiu i xung. </p><p class=\"\">Thanh khon ton th trng bao gm sn HSX, HNX v UPCoM t hn 18.982 t ng.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/vn-index-vuot-1-200-diem-20210318160558654.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'VN-Index vt 1.200 im - Tui Tre Online', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vn-index-vuot-1-200-diem-tuo%cc%89i-tre%cc%89-online', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:12:48', '2021-03-20 12:12:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/vn-index-vuot-1-200-diem-tuo%cc%89i-tre%cc%89-online/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
