(956, 1, '2021-03-20 12:15:08', '2021-03-20 12:15:08', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/1-16160522009822070698267.jpg\" id=\"img_f7b3bab0-87ba-11eb-accd-4b65fc5be44e\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 1.\" title=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"f7b3bab0-87ba-11eb-accd-4b65fc5be44e\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/1-16160522009822070698267.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">ng Nguyn nh Trung - ch tch tp on Hng Thnh v PGS.TS V Hi Qun - gim c HQG TP.HCM thc hin nghi thc k kt hp tc</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Theo tha thun hp tc (</span><span style=\"\">giai on 2021 - 2023), trong</span><span style=\"\">nm 2021, tp on Hng Thnh s dnh ngn sch 20 t ng ti tr cho vic qun l v nghin cu khoa hc cng ngh ti</span><span style=\"\">H Quc gia TP.HCM</span><span style=\"\">(HQG-HCM), cc n v thnh vin v trc thuc. Ngoi ra, HQG-HCM cng cho bit s trch khon ti tr ny  khen thng ging vin c thnh tch ging dy xut sc ca trng.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Hai bn s hp tc nghin cu trong cc lnh vc nh: trin khai cc  ti nghin cu v d liu ln (Big Data), tr tu nhn to (AI), cng ngh Blockchain (hng n vic ng dng Blockchain trong chng khon ha bt ng sn), cng ngh iu khin cng nghip 4.0, qun l d n v k thut thi cng xy dng, vt liu mi, cc gii php thng minh (Smart Solution), cc ng dng qun l ta nh, xy dng nn tng k thut s, chuyn i s, phi hp xy dng v tin hnh cc hot ng phc v cng ng, thc hin trch nhim x hi.</span><br/></p><p class=\"\">Ngoi ra hai bn cng s phi hp  xy dng chnh sch u i i vi nhu cu nh  ca i ng ging vin, cng nhn vin chc ca HQG-HCM v cc trng trc thuc, t  phc v mc tiu chung l thu ht nhn ti cho ton Khu  th HQG-HCM - Trung tm cng ngh gio dc (G1) ca TP. Th c.</p><p class=\"\">Vic trin khai thc hin gi ngn sch ti tr s do Hung Thinh Technology - n v thnh vin ca tp on Hng Thnh v qu pht trin HQG-HCM m nhim. Ngn sch ti tr cho cc nm tip theo s c hai bn tha thun theo tng giai on c th.<br/></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/2-16160525196101373166488.jpg\" id=\"img_b5c82900-87bb-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1312\" alt=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 2.\" title=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"b5c82900-87bb-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/2-16160525196101373166488.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">B Trn Thng Thu Giang - ph tng gim c tp on Hng Thnh kim Ch tch HQT Hung Thinh Technology v PGS.TS Nguyn nh T - chnh vn phng HQG-HCM kim gim c qu pht trin HQG-HCM thc hin nghi thc k kt tha thun hp tc</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">ng Nguyn nh Trung - ch tch tp on Hng Thnh chia s: \"Sau khi ti cu trc chuyn i ln m hnh tp on, Hng Thnh  rt coi trng chin lc pht trin v ng dng cng ngh theo hai mc tiu r rt,  l tin hnh chuyn i s nng cao nng lc qun l, kinh doanh v nng cao hm lng cng ngh trong tri nghim ca khch hng i vi cc sn phm dch v do tp on cung cp.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">c bit, chng ti ang hng n vic a vo vn hnh mt nn tng bt ng sn cng ngh Proptech kt hp Fintech trong nm nay vi mong mun lm minh bch hn th trng bt ng sn Vit Nam.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Do , Hng Thnh tin tng vic hp tc vi HQG-HCM - mt trong nhng trung tm gio dc o to ln nht v c th mnh hng u v khoa hc, cng ngh ti Vit Nam hin nay s to ra nhng bc i chin lc nhm y mnh s pht trin trong k nguyn s, a cc nghin cu khoa hc tr thnh cc gii php k thut, cc sn phm, dch v cht lng cao  c th gii thiu ra th trng trong thi gian ti\".</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">\"Bn cnh , chng ti cng mong mun to iu kin h tr nhiu hn cho ccsinh vin, gip cc em c thm nhiu kinh nghim thc t trn hnh trang bc vo i. Thng qua ngun ngn sch ti tr cho HQG-HCM, chng ti cng hy vng s lan ta tinh thn ny n cc doanh nghip bt ng sn khc,  ngy cng c nhiu doanh nghip ti u t thng d bt ng sn vo x hi, cng pht trin t nc\" - ng Trung chia s.</span><br/></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/photo-2-1616051820910818892901.jpg\" id=\"img_0e902f20-87b6-11eb-93c3-1f527ce33fae\" w=\"1000\" h=\"667\" alt=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 3.\" title=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"0e902f20-87b6-11eb-93c3-1f527ce33fae\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/photo-2-1616051820910818892901.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">PGS.TS Dng Anh c - Thnh y vin, ph ch tch UBND TP.HCM pht biu ti bui l</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Chng trnh c s tham gia ca PGS.TS Dng Anh c - Thnh y vin, Ph ch tch UBND TP.HCM. ng chc mng v nhn nh s hp tc gia tp on Hng Thnh v HQG-HCM cng ph hp vi nh hng ca thnh ph<span style=\"\">trong vic y mnh chuyn i s v thc hin mc tiu tr thnh  th thng minh.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">PGS.TS V Hi Qun - gim c HQG-HCM cho bit: \"Vi vai tr l mt trung tm i hc a ngnh, a lnh vc, cht lng cao, nh hng nghin cu, HQG-HCM lun xc nh pht trin nghin cu khoa hc l mt trong nhng nhim v hng u c u tin pht trin. y mnh hp tc vi cng ng doanh nghip, trong  c tp on Hng Thnh nhm hng n xy dng v pht trin khoa hc v cng ngh bn vng trn c s bm st v gp phn gii quyt hiu qu cc vn  thc tin ca doanh nghip v cng ng. HQG-HCM nh gi cao s hp tc tch cc ny\".</span><br/></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/6-16160540244331754703795.jpg\" id=\"img_2ffe6f50-87bb-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1361\" alt=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 4.\" title=\"Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc - nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"2ffe6f50-87bb-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/6-16160540244331754703795.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">ng Nguyn nh Trung trao qu lu nim cho PGS.TS V Hi Qun</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Bn cnh tha thun hp tc  k kt, trong khun kh phin tho lun ti s kin, hai bn  cng bn bc v c hi hp tc trin khai cc trung tm nghin cu khoa hc cng ngh tin tin v trung tm h tr khi nghip ti TP.Quy Nhn, tnh Bnh nh.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/tap-doan-hung-thinh-va-dai-hoc-quoc-gia-tphcm-ky-ket-hop-tac-chien-luoc-20210318150206887.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Tp on Hng Thnh v i hc Quc gia TP.HCM k kt hp tc chin lc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tap-doan-hung-thinh-va-dai-hoc-quoc-gia-tp-hcm-ky-ket-hop-tac-chien-luoc', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:15:08', '2021-03-20 12:15:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tap-doan-hung-thinh-va-dai-hoc-quoc-gia-tp-hcm-ky-ket-hop-tac-chien-luoc/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
