(958, 1, '2021-03-20 12:15:10', '2021-03-20 12:15:10', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3001-16160439347021172088932.jpg\" id=\"img_b218\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 1.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"b218\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3001-16160439347021172088932.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Bn trong khng gian trng by \"Mt thi si ni\" - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">S kin nhm hng ti k nim 90 nm Ngy thnh lp on Thanh nin cng sn H Ch Minh (26-3-1931 - 26-3-2021), c khai mc sng 18-3 ti khu di tch nh t Ha L (ph Ha L, Hon Kim, H Ni).</span></p><p class=\"\">Xuyn sut khng gian trng by k cu chuyn v k c mt thi si ni ca la thanh nin Vit Nam sinh ra trong thi chin v giai on hin nay. </p><p class=\"\">Vi bu mu nng v tri tim rc la, bao th h thanh nin  dng cm xng pha ni chin trng c lit, rn luyn bn lnh trong cc nh t thc dn,  quc hay dn thn vt mi th thch trong thi i mi  bo v v xy dng T quc thn yu. </p><p class=\"\">Mt thi si ni ca lp lp thanh nin \"p nh hoa hng, cng hn st thp\"  tr thnh nim t ho ca c dn tc.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3134-1616043935455142447359.jpg\" id=\"img_ac99\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 2.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"ac99\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3134-1616043935455142447359.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Bui trng by thu ht s ch  ca nhiu cu chin binh, thanh nin xung phong thi chin v cc bn on vin, thanh nin tr - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Ti bui trng by, b  Hng Phn (sinh nm 1933, H Ni) - c n sinh H thnh tiu biu ca ngi trng Chu Vn An - cho bit b rt xc ng khi xem nhng hnh nh gi nh nhng k nim v qung i hc sinh, b tham gia hot ng khng chin v b bt nht ti nh t Ha L.</p><p class=\"\">\"Thi im  chng ti c nhng nim au kh ring ca ngi n l, nh Cch mng Thng Tm, nhng a tr nh ti mi bit mnh l mt nc thuc a. Vy nn  thi thc chng ti dn thn, ln ng bo v T quc\", b Phn xc ng.</p><p class=\"\">B Phn cho bit thm nim au u ln nht ca bn thn l mong t nc Vit Nam cng pht trin, ha bnh, tim cn cc nc pht trin trong tng lai gn. <span style=\"\">\"iu  ty thuc rt ln vo th h tr ngy nay\", b Phn ni.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Bn Tng Th Qu (19 tui, sinh vin Hc vin Thanh thiu nin) chia s rt xc ng, t ho khi c ha mnh vo khng gian ca mt thi mu la.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">\"Thi xa ng cha  rt kh khn, gian kh  ginh ly c lp nn chng em phi trn trng nhng pht giy ha bnh hin ti. Ti y em nh c sng li, cng tri qua mt thi mu la ca ng cha...\", Qu chia s.</span></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc2994-16160439362601787403610.jpg\" id=\"img_ad66\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 3.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"ad66\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc2994-16160439362601787403610.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Nhiu ngi ti d bui trng by tranh th ghi li nhng thng tin, t liu qu v \"Mt thi si ni\" - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Trng by \"Mt thi si ni\" c th hin qua hai ni dung ln: <i>nh la t tri tim</i> v <i>c vng xy i.</i></p><p class=\"\"><i>nh la t tri tim</i> l cu chuyn ca tui tr Vit Nam trn chng ng u tranh gii phng dn tc. Vi nim tin tt thng vo cch mng, bao lp thanh nin  vt qua mi gian kh, hi sinh; xng pha ni chin trng c lit; hng say lao ng ni hu phng hay kin trung, bt khut ni ngc t thc dn,  quc.</p><p class=\"\">Vi phn <i>c vng xy i</i>s l nhng hot ng ca tui tr Vit Nam hm nay  v ang gp phn ni di thm nhng chin cng, t thm thm truyn thng v vang ca dn tc.<br/></p><p class=\"\">Nhng thanh nin tr th h mi  bin ngn la nhit huyt, rc chy trong tim mnh thnh nhng hnh ng, vic lm thc t, sng to, hiu qu.<span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc2992-16160439369621562377082.jpg\" id=\"img_e975\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 4.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"e975\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc2992-16160439369621562377082.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Chic m ci t ngay ngn cnh quyn sch ca anh lnh tn binh gi li ngy ln ng nhp ng - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3041-1616043937730359581902.jpg\" id=\"img_b0c3\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1359\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 5.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 5.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"b0c3\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3041-1616043937730359581902.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Hai bc cu chin binh cng xem li nhng hnh nh ca cuc Cch mng Thng Tm y bi trng - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3147-16160439392241746877843.jpg\" id=\"img_5234\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 6.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 6.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"5234\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3147-16160439392241746877843.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\" spellcheck=\"true\">Trng by ti hin khung cnh anh b i Trng Sn xa vn lc quan, yu i d trong khi la chin tranh - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3164-1616043940249125646645.jpg\" id=\"img_1fd8\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 7.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 7.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"1fd8\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc3164-1616043940249125646645.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Nhiu ngi vui v khi c sng li thanh xun vi nc ch xanh cng lng kh qun nhu trn ng hnh qun - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/18/logo-dsc2960-16160439410122064535087.jpg\" id=\"img_e631\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 8.\" title=\"Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by Mt thi si ni - nh 8.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"e631\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/logo-dsc2960-16160439410122064535087.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\" spellcheck=\"true\">Bo Nha Sng, c in u n hng thng, mi s bo ra 300 - 400 t t nm 1952  tuyn truyn, phc v cch mng - nh: PHM TUN</p></div></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/di-tich-nha-tu-hoa-lo-vua-ra-mat-trung-bay-mot-thoi-soi-noi-20210318114439899.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Di tch nh t Ha L va ra mt trng by \'Mt thi si ni\'', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'di-tich-nha-tu-hoa-lo-vua-ra-mat-trung-bay-mot-thoi-soi-noi', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:15:10', '2021-03-20 12:15:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/di-tich-nha-tu-hoa-lo-vua-ra-mat-trung-bay-mot-thoi-soi-noi/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(959, 1, '2021-03-20 12:18:16', '2021-03-20 12:18:16', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/159611832258139125859708914574106663047697n-2read-only-16159016099611071247795.jpg\" id=\"img_7789b690-8658-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" w=\"1000\" h=\"664\" alt=\"Lng ng M ng lng cu bo ch - nh 1.\" title=\"Lng ng M ng lng cu bo ch - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"7789b690-8658-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/159611832258139125859708914574106663047697n-2read-only-16159016099611071247795.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Cc c quan bo ch  M ang gp rt nhiu kh khn v ngun thu v Facebook, Google - nh: Bloomberg</p></div></div><p>Cc ngh s ng h d tho o lut Bo tn v cnh tranh bo ch (JCPA) ca M cho rng gi  l lc khng th chm tr hn na trong vic to ra mt c ch php l  bo v bo ch truyn thng, gip ngnh ny tn ti c lp v mnh m nh lu nay.</p><p><b>Khng th chm hn</b></p><p>Nhng t bo, knh truyn hnh v cc hng tin tc M, vn chng kin ngun thu st gim gh gm do cc nn tng online nh Facebook v Google, ang k vng s sm nhn c s tr gip t Quc hi M, cn c vo d lut JCPA ang c mt ln na  trnh v thc y ti y.</p><p>JCPA tun qua c  trnh ti Thng vin v H vin M, vi s ng h t c hai ng Dn ch v Cng ha. Theo Hng tin Bloomberg, vic lng ng ng h JCPA cho thy M s tr thnh \"mt trn tip theo\" ca cuc chin gia ngnh cng nghip tin tc vi cc ng ln cng ngh nh Google, Facebook.</p><p>Bt u t ngy 12-3, tiu ban chng c quyn thuc y ban T php H vin M  t chc iu trn v JCPA, d lut do thng ngh s Amy Klobuchar v dn biu David Cicilline (c hai u thuc ng Dn ch)  trnh. Mt phin iu trn na ca tiu ban chng c quyn ti h vin lin quan ti JCPA cng  c ln k hoch trong ngy 18-3.</p><p>Nu c thng qua, JCPA s cho php cc hng tin tc, bo ch c min thc thi lut chng cnh tranh trong bn nm  tp hp li vi nhau thnh mt lc lng, m phn vi cc hng cng ngh  v ang s dng ni dung ca h. Trc y, theo lut chng c quyn ca M, cc hng tin tc khng c php lin kt li  m phn vi cc nn tng s.</p><p>Cc ngh s  xut JCPA cho rng vic cn c gii php gip  bo ch trong bi cnh hin nay l khng th chm tr hn na. \"R rng chng ta phi lm g  v ngn hn  cu bo ch xc tn trc khi mt n vnh vin\", dn biu ng Dn ch David Cicilline, ch tch tiu ban chng c quyn ca H vin M, ni trong phin iu<span style=\"\">trn ngy 12-3.</span></p><p>\"Nu khng c mt th trng t do cnh tranh hay hnh ng ca Quc hi, s tip tc din ra s hp nht hng lot v sa thi (nhn vin) trn quy m ln\", v dn biu ny cnh bo.</p><p><b>Thay i<span style=\"\">t ng Cng ha</span></b></p><p>Trn thc t, cc ngh s ng h JCPA  tng thc y vn  ny trong nhiu nm qua song vn cha nhn  s phiu ng h  thng qua d lut, nht l t cc ngh s Cng ha. Gn y nht, thng 4-2019, d lut JCPA tng c  trnh ln Quc hi M nhng bt thnh.</p><p>Tuy nhin, theo cc ngh s Cng ha ng h JCPA, thc t ny ang thay i v h hi vng nm nay s c gp i s dn biu Cng ha ng h JCPA so vi nm ngoi.</p><p>Thi gian qua ng Cng ha tng nhiu ln bc xc v vic cc hng cng ngh nh Facebook, Google \"kim duyt\" nhng quan im theo xu hng bo th. Thm na, vic chnh quyn c  chnh thc ph chun v thc thi lut bt cc hng cng ngh phi tr tin bo ch cng l din bin gp phn tc ng ng k ti nhng ng thi ti<span style=\"\">M lin quan JCPA.</span></p><p>Dn biu Cng ha Ken Buck cho rng cc hng cng ngh ln ang kim sot vic tranh lun ca cng chng cng nh th trng online. \"Quc hi  ngi im nh phng trong khi cc nn tng ny tr thnh nhng th lc c quyn\",<span style=\"\">ng Buck bnh lun vi t Wall Street Journal.</span></p><p>B Amy Klobuchar, thng ngh s bang Minnesota, cho rng ln ny JCPA c kh nng s c thng qua v nhn c s ng h ca cc lnh o ch cht thuc lng ng ti Quc hi M nh thng ngh s Mitch McConnell - lnh o phe thiu s (ng Cng ha) ti Thng vin, hay dn biu Ken Buck - thnh vin cp cao ca ng Cng ha ti tiu ban chng c quyn ca H vin.</p><p>D vy vn cn mt s ngh s Cng ha, trong  c dn biu Jim Jordan ca bang Ohio, cn chn ch v vic trao thm quyn lc cho ngnh truyn thng m nhiu ngh s theo quan im bo th cha tin tng.</p><p>Theo Hng tin Bloomberg, d lut JCPA ca M s khng bao gm iu khon ging nh lut ca c l buc cc hng cng ngh v cc c quan bo ch, truyn thng phi tun theo mt c quan trng ti do chnh ph ch nh nu hai bn khng th t t c tha thun vi nhau v vic cung cp ni dung v chia s li nhun lin quan.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\" data-back=\"#cfe2f3\" style=\"background-color: rgb(207, 226, 243);\"><p><b>Facebook t tha thun vi News Corp</b></p><p>Tp on News Corp ca ng trm truyn thng Rupert Murdoch ngy 16-3 thng bo  t c tha thun cung cp ni dung trong nhiu nm vi cng ty mng x hi Facebook ti c.</p><p>Theo Hng tin Reuters, tha thun ny (khng tit l cc iu khon c th) xc nhn News Corp l hng truyn thng ln u tin t c tha thun vi Facebook theo lut mi thng qua ti c c ni dung buc cc hng cng ngh phi tr tin cho bo ch  s dng tin tc ca h.</p></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\" data-back=\"#fce5cd\" style=\"background-color: rgb(252, 229, 205);\"><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>2.100</b></h2><p><i>T nm 2004 - 2019, khong 2.100 t bo ca M  dng xut bn v t nht c thm 60 t na  ng ca k t khi bng pht i dch COVID-19.</i></p><p><i>Dn biu ng Dn ch David Cicilline cho bit trong 15 nm qua, 1/5 t bo  M  ng ca v s nh bo  gim mt na.</i></p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://congnghe.tuoitre.vn/luong-dang-my-dong-long-cuu-bao-chi-20210316203756854.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Lng ng M ng lng cu bo ch', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'luong-dang-my-dong-long-cuu-bao-chi', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:18:16', '2021-03-20 12:18:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/luong-dang-my-dong-long-cuu-bao-chi/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
