(961, 1, '2021-03-20 12:19:28', '2021-03-20 12:19:28', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo bo co ca Tiu ban iu tr, Ban Ch o quc gia phng, chng dch COVID-19, hin Vit Nam cha khi cho 2.198 bnh nhn mc COVID-19.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><img alt=\"Sng 19/3, Vit Nam khng c ca COVID-19 mi, hn 27.000 ngi c tim vaccine - 1\" height=\"395\" data-id=\"1548159\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"395\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/thong-ke-06022952.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"0\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">S liu thng k ca B Y t.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s nhng trng hp mc bnh ang iu tr ti nc ta, 37 ngi c kt qu m tnh ln 1. Ngoi ra, 18 ngi m tnh ln 2 v 63 bnh nhn m tnh ln 3 vi SARS-CoV-2.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S ca t vong v COVID-19  nc ta n nay l 35, gm 31 ngi ti  Nng, 3 ngi  Qung Nam v 1 ngi  Qung Tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phn ln trong s h l ngi cao tui, c bnh l nng nh suy thn mn giai on cui, ung th mu giai on cui khng p ng ho cht, hi chng mch vnh, suy h hp cp, thoi ho a khp, tng huyt p, suy thng thn mn, tiu ng type 2, nhim trng huyt, vim phi, suy kit, suy a tng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Chuong trinh Tiem chung Mo rong quoc gia (TCMR) trong ngay 18/3 a trien khai tiem chung vaccine phong COVID-19 tai 4 tinh: Ha Giang ( tim cho 70 ngi), ien Bien (56), Ba Ria - Vung Tau (87) va Binh Duong (84).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">en cuoi gio chieu 18/3 co them 3.492 nguoi uoc tiem chung vaccine COVID-19, nang tong so nguoi a uoc tiem vaccine phong COVID-19 len 27.546 nguoi. Tat ca eu la can bo, nhan vien y te ang truc tiep ieu tri benh nhan COVID-19, cac nhan vien y te thuc hien cac nhiem vu nhu lay mau benh pham, xet nghiem, truy vet, thanh vien cac to COVID-19 cong ong va Ban Chi ao phong chong dich cac ia phuong.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/sang-19-3-viet-nam-khong-co-ca-covid-19-moi-hon-27-000-nguoi-duoc-tiem-vaccine-ar601788.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'Sng 19/3, Vit Nam khng c ca COVID-19 mi, hn 27.000 ngi c tim vaccine', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sang-19-3-viet-nam-khong-co-ca-covid-19-moi-hon-27-000-nguoi-duoc-tiem-vaccine', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:19:28', '2021-03-20 12:19:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/sang-19-3-viet-nam-khong-co-ca-covid-19-moi-hon-27-000-nguoi-duoc-tiem-vaccine/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(962, 1, '2021-03-20 12:20:54', '2021-03-20 12:20:54', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngy 19-3, Thng trc UBND TP.HCM t chc hi ngh s kt hot ng ca T cng tc v u t sau ba nm thnh lp vi s tham gia ca nhiu tp on, doanh nghip (DN) trong v ngoi nc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti hi ngh,Ch tch UBND TP.HCMNguyn Thnh Phong nghe S KH&amp;T TP trnh by d tho k hoch nhng nhim v, gii php ch yu  ci thin mi trng kinh doanh, nng lc cnh tranh quc gia nm 2021.</p>\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"item-photo\"><img alt=\"TP.HCM n lc ci thin mi trng u t - nh 1\" src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/w800/Uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/p3-cai-thien-moi-truong_bkhh.jpg\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/p3-cai-thien-moi-truong_bkhh.jpg\" cms-photo-caption=\"Ch tch UBND TP.HCM Nguyn Thnh Phong trao i vi cc nh u t, doanh nghip bn l hi ngh. nh: THANH TUYN\"/><br/>&#13;\n<em class=\"image_caption\">Ch tch UBND TP.HCM Nguyn Thnh Phong trao i vi cc nh u t, doanh nghip bn l hi ngh. nh: THANH TUYN</em></p>\n<p><b style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cn tp trung ci thin th tc hnh chnh</b><br/>&#13;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ng Nguyn Vn B, i din Hip hi Cc khu ch xut, cho rng  ci thin mi trng u t th TP.HCM phi quan tm n ba vn  chnh l quy hoch t ai, c ch chnh sch v th tc hnh chnh. Theo ng B, hin c nhiu th tc ko di thi gian, cc th tc v giy php u t, mi trng, th tc lao ng c khi ko di qu lu. </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lin quan n vn  ny, i din Hip hi Cc DN TP cho rng cc khu cng nghip  TP.HCM ang pht trin vo mt phn khc ln, tuy nhin th tc lin quan n khu cng nghip li chm. Chnh iu ny lm cho cc nh u t, sn xut v ch bin c xu hng  v cc tnh v th tc ca h nhanh, n gin hn. </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ng cng  xut TP cn c data ca cc DN u t ti TP.HCM trong 5-10 nm. Cng  l tp trung vo cc khu cng nghip chuyn ngnh, c cng ngh mi, s dng ngun nhn lc cht lng cao, tp trung chuyn mn v k thut </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B Mary Tarnowka, Gim c iu hnh AmCham Vit Nam, c  kin rng vic n gin ha quy trnh th tc, h s cho DN l iu m TP.HCM cn quan tm nhiu hn. B cng cho rng TP cn c h thng qun l logistics hiu qu, tp trung pht trin h tng x hi, tng cng hp tc quc t vi cc nh u t  xy dng lc lng lao ng cht lng cao</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nghe cc  kin gp , ng Nguyn Thnh Phong  yu cu S KH&amp;T ghi nhn v c iu chnh. ng nh gi  kin ca DN, nh u t l cht liu quan trng  TP b sung, hon thin k hoch ci thin mi trng u t, nht l trong nm 2021.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ng  ngh cc c quan nh S KH&amp;T, S Ti chnh, S QH-KT, S Xy dng, S TN&amp;MT phi i u trong vic ci cch hnh chnh v ng dng cng ngh thng tin, ng thi tip tc ci thin mi trng u t, y mnh h tr DN cho n khi cc d n i vo hot ng. Trng hp cc kh khn, vng mc vt thm quyn th khn trng bo co,  xut vi TP. Tuyt i khng  xy ra tnh trng ngm h s, nhng nhiu gy kh khn cho DN - ng Phong ni.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ng cng nhn mnh: Chnh quyn TP lun cu th v mong mun gii quyt mi kh khn chnh ng ca DN bng nhng hnh ng thc cht, c th  c thm nhiu d n c tho g thng qua c ch hot ng ca T cng tc v u t, gp phn xy dng mi trng u t ca TP ngy cng minh bch, thng thong.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Cn gim 30% thi gian x l phn nh ca doanh nghip </b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trao i vi cc DN, nh u t quc t ti hi ngh, ng Nguyn Thnh Phong cho bitTP xc nh nm 2021 l nm ch  thc hin Xy dng chnh quyn  th v ci thin mi trng u t, do  TP  a ra k hoch v 10 nhm gii php ci thin mi trng u t, tng nng lc cnh tranh. </p>\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ng cng gi m thm cc gii php v yu cu S KH&amp;T a vo k hoch. Th nht, nu qu 15 ngy lm vic, c quan ly  kin khng tr li bng vn bn th xem nh  ng  v phi chu trch nhim v cc ni dung c lin quan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th hai,thc hin thanh tra, kim tra theo ng quy nh ca php lut khng qu mt ln trong nm; kt hp thanh tra, kim tra lin ngnh, nhiu ni dung trong mt t thanh tra, kim tra, tr trng hp thanh tra, kim tra t xut khi c du hiu vi phm php lut r rng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th ba,yu cu sa i, b sung h s ch thng bo mt ln bng vn bn cho DN, nh u t.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th t,<i></i>ng yu cu cc s, ngnh nghin cu gim t nht 30% thi gian x l kin ngh ca DN so vi quy trnh ca c quan, n v ang trin khai thc hin.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch tch UBND TP.HCM nhn mnh: ng hnh cng DN l mc tiu xuyn sut trong cng tc lnh o v ch o iu hnh ca chnh quyn TP. Chng ti s lm tt hn trong thi gian ti, nht l trong nm 2021  p li s mong mi, k vng ca ngi dn, DN. TP cng mong mun s to mi trng u t kinh doanh thng thong, bnh ng  tt c DN cnh tranh lnh mnh v pht trin i ln cng TP.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border: 1px solid black; background-color: #eee; margin: 5px; border-collapse: collapse;\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td style=\"background-color: #eee;\">&#13;\n            <p>G<b> vng cho 35 d</b><strong> n ca </strong><b>TP</b></p>&#13;\n            <p>Sau hn ba nm hot ng, T cng tc v u t trn a bn TP.HCM do ng Nguyn Thnh Phong, Ch tch UBND TP, lm t trng  kt lun hng x l vng mc i vi 92 d n. Trong  c 51 d n bt ng sn; 21 d n lin quan pht trin h tng k thut, giao thng; 18 ni dung lin quan n pht trin h tng x hi, phc v ngi dn v hai d n lin quan n hot ng sn xut.</p>&#13;\n            <p>Ngoi ra, 108  xut, kin ngh ca DN, nh u t cng c t cng tc tip nhn, phn loi v x l.</p>&#13;\n            <p>T cng tc v u t  tp trung tho g vng mc cho 35 d n vi tng mc u t hn 320.000 t ng, n nay c bn thc hin xong ni dung ch o, cc kh khn  c tho g, ang trin khai thc hin cc bc u t tip theo.</p>&#13;\n            <p>i vi 57 d n cn li, cc c quan chc nng ang cn nh gi li php l, ch o cc c quan chuyn mn ly  kin hng dn ca cc b, ngnh hoc xin  kin ch o ca Th tng  cng c h s php l, lm c s tip tc trin khai d n.</p>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">					<article class=\"article-related clearfix cms-relate\">                            <figure class=\"thumb\">                              <img src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/170x123/uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/plohncaithienmoitruongdautu3svog_mbux.jpg\" alt=\"TP.HCM: Quyt khng  ngm h s, nhng nhiu doanh nghip\" class=\"cms-photo\" data-photo-original-src=\"https://photo-cms-plo.zadn.vn/Uploaded/2021/bzivycwk/2021_03_19/plohncaithienmoitruongdautu3svog_mbux.jpg\"/>                            </figure>&#13;\n<header>&#13;\nTP.HCM: Quyt khng  ngm h s, nhng nhiu doanh nghip&#13;\n</header>&#13;\n<p>(PLO)- Ch tch UBND TP.HCM nhn mnh, TP.HCM s to mi trng u t kinh doanh thng thong, bnh ng, cnh tranh lnh mnh, i ln cng TP.</p>&#13;\n</article></p>\n\n</div><script>(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) return;\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v2.21&appId=178366485681696\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));</script><script>\n!function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)\n{if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?\nn.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};\nif(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version=\'2.0\';\nn.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;\nt.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];\ns.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, document,\'script\',\n\'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js\');\nfbq(\'init\', \'1739154382882652\');\nfbq(\'track\', \'PageView\');\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://plo.vn/thoi-su/tphcm-no-luc-cai-thien-moi-truong-dau-tu-973608.html\">PLO.VN</a>', 'TP.HCM n lc ci thin mi trng u t | Thi s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tp-hcm-no-luc-cai-thien-moi-truong-dau-tu-thoi-su', '', ''