(964, 1, '2021-03-20 12:21:55', '2021-03-20 12:21:55', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><p>D EU tuyn b vaccine AstraZeneca an ton, nhiu chuyn gia s rng  mun  ni li tim chng v ngi dn lung lay nim tin vo vaccine.</p><div id=\"\">\n<p class=\"Normal\">C quan Qun l Dc phm chu u (EMA) ngy 18/3 kt lun vaccine Covid-19 ca AstraZeneca an ton v hiu qu sau khi nhiu quc gia bo co tnh trng ng mu. </p><p class=\"Normal\">Song cc chuyn gia cho rng ng thi ny  mun, vic ngng s dng trc  khin nhiu ngi lung lay lng tin i vi vaccine AstraZeneca. Trong nhng tun gn y, hu nh ton b Ty u  nh ch tim chng, ngay khi ln sng Covid-19 th ba manh nha ko n. Ngay t u, ng thi ny b cc chuyn gia y t cng cng ch trch.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Trong khi Anh  tim c hn 11 triu liu vaccine, cc nh lnh o EU i mt vi cu hi lm th no  xy dng li nim tin vo AstraZeneca  mt trong vi tun qua.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Mt cuc thm d ca t Elabe trong tun ny cho thy ch 22% dn s Php tin dng vaccine AstraZeneca.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Remi Salomon, thnh vin cp cao ca mt bnh vin nc ny, cho bit: \"Mi ngi ang cn trng qu mc\". ng s rng cng ng s hiu sai lch v quyt nh nh ch s dng vaccine.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Michael Head, chuyn gia nghin cu v Y t ton cu ti i hc Southampton, Anh, cho bit thm: \"Ni s hi kiu ny c th khin h do d vi vaccine. Cn phi tht nhanh chng trin khai li vic tim chng\". </p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/merlin-180213495-1db99cf7-de7f-6422-7449-1616121258.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=AdusUCHdNTBp6zv_9TwMWg\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1199\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"800\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/merlin-180213495-1db99cf7-de7f-6422-7449-1616121258.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Ajv5VS31JiNlBjl4JUZDUg 1x, https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/merlin-180213495-1db99cf7-de7f-6422-7449-1616121258.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=03nRMI-mu9OfFyi8c7wa-w 1.5x, https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/merlin-180213495-1db99cf7-de7f-6422-7449-1616121258.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Kd9oLVo7lE0nJANPOsb-pg 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Tnh nguyn vin tham gia th nghim lm sng vaccine Covid-19 ca AstraZenenca, thng 10/2020. nh: NY Times\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/merlin-180213495-1db99cf7-de7f-6422-7449-1616121258.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Ajv5VS31JiNlBjl4JUZDUg\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Tnh nguyn vin tham gia th nghim lm sng vaccine Covid-19 ca AstraZenenca, thng 10/2020. nh: <em>NY Times</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Chng trnh tim vaccine AstraZeneca trn ton lc a gp v vn trc tr. Mt s nc nghi ng v tc dng ca n vi ngi cao tui. Chuyn gia sau  kt lun vaccine  hiu qu. EU cng phi ginh git ngun cung hn ch khi AstraZeneca cho bit khng th cung cp  lng hng  cam kt trc . Italy chn xut khu sang Australia vi ngy trc khi ngng tim chng.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Gi y, gii chc y t chu u <strong>n lc tim chng  b p thi gian  mt.</strong></p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Chng ta phi tim vaccine cng nhanh cng tt\", Michel Chassang, bc s a khoa ngi Php, ch tch Lin on Y t Php, chia s. \"Cch duy nht  ngn chn virus ly lan l m bo tt c mi ngi c tim chng\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">\"iu ny s khng d dng cht no. Chng ti phi li ngc dng, v vaccine ny  b mang ting xu k t khi bt u trin khai\", ng tha nhn.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Ti <strong>Anh</strong>, Th tng Boris Johnson s tim vaccine AstraZeneca ngy 19/3. Pht biu ti cuc hp giao ban v Covid-19, ng cho rng phn quyt ca EMA l \"rt quan trng i vi cc nc lng ging chu u\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Vaccine Oxford (AstraZeneca) an ton, vaccine Pfizer an ton, th duy nht nguy him l Covid-19. Mi ngi nn tip tc tim chng khi n lt\", ng ni.</p><p class=\"Normal\">D liu thc t t Anh cho thy mt liu vaccine gim hn 80% nguy c nhp vin do Covid-19  ngi trn 80 tui. Tin s Sabine Straus, ch tch y ban nh gi Ri ro Dc Phm ca EMA (PRAC), cng khng nh vaccine khng gy ng mu.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/24virus-briefing-astrazeneca-v-6721-6720-1616121258.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=_Acq5sj7O_KXgiMoQeTgxA\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"675\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/24virus-briefing-astrazeneca-v-6721-6720-1616121258.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=v0JlCCyZfgV62t6iSTeZwg 1x, https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/24virus-briefing-astrazeneca-v-6721-6720-1616121258.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=eZ-HT8q8QjSdE1HEYeBupA 1.5x, https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/24virus-briefing-astrazeneca-v-6721-6720-1616121258.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=PHg0nxCTuAujifGFBdRBxw 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Cc chuyn gia nh gi hiu qu ca vaccine AstraZenenca ti i hc Oxford. nh: NY Times\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-suckhoe.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/24virus-briefing-astrazeneca-v-6721-6720-1616121258.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=v0JlCCyZfgV62t6iSTeZwg\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Cc chuyn gia nh gi hiu qu ca vaccine AstraZenenca ti i hc Oxford. nh: <em>NY Times</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Thc t, trong hn 10 quc gia ngng s dng vaccine, cc trng hp ng mu rt him. C 7 ngi b mu ng trong mch (ng mu ni mch lan ta) v 18 ngi c cc mu ng trong no (CVST). Tng s ca ng mu trc, trong v sau tim chng l 469, trong  191 trng hp xy ra  EU. Theo EMA, con s ny thm ch thp hn c tnh chung.</p><p class=\"Normal\">C quan lu  c \"rt t trng hp b ng thi ng mu v gim tiu cu\" sau tim chng. Nhng ca ny hu ht xy ra  ph n di 55 tui. Chuyn gia y t ng tnh rng tnh trng ny him gp, nhiu ngi  by t ngc nhin khi cc nc EU ngng tim vaccine.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Jon Gibbins, Gim c Vin Nghin cu Tim mch v Chuyn ha ti i hc Reading, cho bit: \"Cc con s thng k rt nh, khng cao hn mt bng chung dn s. Khi bt u tim chng cho hng triu ngi, khng th trnh khi iu ny xy ra. Nhng n khng c ngha vaccine gy ra ng mu\".</p><p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong>Thc Linh</strong> (Theo <em>CNN</em>)</p>\n</div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/chau-au-va-niem-tin-muon-mang-vao-vaccine-covid-4250771.html\">VNEXPRESS.NET</a>', 'Chu u v nim tin mun mng vo vaccine Covid', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chau-au-va-niem-tin-muon-mang-vao-vaccine-covid', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:21:55', '2021-03-20 12:21:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/chau-au-va-niem-tin-muon-mang-vao-vaccine-covid/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
