(965, 1, '2021-03-20 12:22:02', '2021-03-20 12:22:02', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/2/24/logo-chot-kiem-soat-hp-1-1614169730359335695472.jpg\" id=\"img_86dd\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1077\" alt=\"Hi Phng m hn i vi xe ch hng t Hi Dng - nh 1.\" title=\"Hi Phng m hn i vi xe ch hng t Hi Dng - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"86dd\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/2/24/logo-chot-kiem-soat-hp-1-1614169730359335695472.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Hi Phng iu chnh cho php phng tin ch hng ha lu thng trn quc l 5  gii quyt tnh trng n  ti nt giao cao tc H Ni - Hi Phng vi quc l 10 - nh: TIN THNG</p></div></div><p>Chiu 24-2, ng Nguyn Vn Tng - ch tch UBND TP Hi Phng - tip tc ch tr hi ngh giao ban trc tuyn trin khai cng tc phng chng dch COVID-19 trn a bn.</p><p>Lin quan cng tc m bo lu thng hng ha, ng Tng ch o xe ch hng ha xut khu, phc v sn xut t Hi Dng sang Hi Phng v t Hi Phng i cc tnh khc c i qua quc l 5. Ring xe ch khch vn i qua ng cao tc H Ni - Hi Phng.  </p><p>ng ch , li xe v ph xe ca phng tin ch hng ha xut khu, phc v sn xut t Hi Dng khi vo Hi Phng phi c giy xt nghim m tnh vi COVIDD-19 nhng c thi hn trong 5 ngy, k t khi c kt qu. Trc , TP Hi Phng yu cu ch c thi hn trong 3 ngy.</p><p>Ngoi ra vn phi m bo iu kin c hp ng, n hng c th (ni sn xut, ni giao hng, ni nhn hng)  lc lng chc nng kim tra, gim st.</p><p>i vi li xe, ph xe ch hng ha t Hi Phng vo Hi Dng phi c xc nhn ca ch phng tin hoc UBND x, phng, th trn, khi tr v phi  khu tp trung do ch phng tin b tr v phi ly mu xt nghim.</p><p>Trng hp c tnh vi phm hoc b v nh s bt buc vo ni cch ly tp trung v phi tr chi ph cch ly cng nh x l nghim theo quy nh.  </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/2/24/logo-chot-kiem-soat-hp-6-16141697312931411647248.jpg\" id=\"img_c93f\" w=\"2000\" h=\"948\" alt=\"Hi Phng m hn i vi xe ch hng t Hi Dng - nh 2.\" title=\"Hi Phng m hn i vi xe ch hng t Hi Dng - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"c93f\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/2/24/logo-chot-kiem-soat-hp-6-16141697312931411647248.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Theo iu chnh mi, li xe v ph xe ch hng ha t Hi Dng vo Hi Phng cn c giy xt nghim m tnh vi COVIDD-19 trong thi gian 5 ngy, k t khi c kt qu xt nghim - nh: TIN THNG</p></div></div><p>Trn thc t, t nhiu ngy nay lng xe ti trn ng t cao tc H Ni - Hi Phng tng t bin gy n tc ti nt giao quc l 10. Vic cho php xe ch hng i qua quc l 5  ra vo Hi Phng s gip gim ti, gii quyt vn  ny.  </p><p>Lin quan n 3 ca dng tnh mi xut hin trn a bn TP, cc a phng  truy vt pht hin tng s 499 trng hp F1, 2.077 trng hp F2. Tt c cc trng hp ny u  c cch ly, qun l, gim st cht ch v ly mu xt nghim.</p><p>100% mu xt nghim din rng ti cc khu dn c phong ta c kt qu m tnh, gm 1.782 mu ti thn 4, x Hong ng, huyn Thy Nguyn v 830 mu ti l 112 khu cng nhn D Hng, qun L Chn. Ngnh y t tip tc ly mu, xt nghim m rng ti cc a phng.</p><p>C quan chc nng TP Hi Phng bc u xc nh ngun ly chm ca bnh COVID-19 va pht hin trn a bn l t huyn Cm Ging, tnh Hi Dng - qu ca bnh nhn N.V.Q..</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/hai-phong-mo-hon-doi-voi-xe-cho-hang-tu-hai-duong-20210224192913705.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Hi Phng \'m\' hn i vi xe ch hng t Hi Dng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hai-phong-mo-hon-doi-voi-xe-cho-hang-tu-hai-duong', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:22:02', '2021-03-20 12:22:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/hai-phong-mo-hon-doi-voi-xe-cho-hang-tu-hai-duong/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(966, 0, '2021-03-20 12:22:03', '2021-03-20 12:22:03', '', 'chot-kiem-soat-hp-4-16141694222391711789266-crop-1614169747854294994332.jpg', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'chot-kiem-soat-hp-4-16141694222391711789266-crop-1614169747854294994332-jpg', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:22:03', '2021-03-20 12:22:03', '', 965, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/bao-nhanh/uploads/2021/03/chot-kiem-soat-hp-4-16141694222391711789266-crop-1614169747854294994332.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(967, 1, '2021-03-20 12:22:23', '2021-03-20 12:22:23', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/untitled-1-copy-1615880498938580797636.jpg\" id=\"img_55cd5a60-8627-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" w=\"1024\" h=\"756\" alt=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 1.\" title=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"55cd5a60-8627-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/untitled-1-copy-1615880498938580797636.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">T phim Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, sc nng ca dng phim am m cha bao gi gim st - nh: Sina</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Nm 2019, b phim <i>Trn tnh lnh</i> pht sng ln u tin  dy ln ln sng am m trn th trng phim truyn hnh Trung Quc, ng thi to nn nhng ngi sao \"nng bng tay\" nh Tiu Chin, Vng Nht Bc</p><p class=\"\">B phim <i>Sn h lnh</i> chnh thc ln sng t cui thng 2 va qua v cn st bng pht vo thng 3 khi trang Douban chm 8.6 im, hai din vin chnh Trng Trit Hn v Cung Tun cng lp tc bc vo thi \"thnh th\" khi c fan sn n, tr thnh hai m nam \"hot\" nht hin nay.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"VideoStream\" data-advmode=\"5\" data-src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=tuoitre&amp;new_info_domain=true&amp;stgdmn=hls.tuoitre.vn&amp;vid=tuoitre/2021/3/16/-word-of-honorx-16158815512011518197988-026f5.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;poster=https://video-thumbs.tuoitre.vn/tuoitre/2021/3/16/-word-of-honorx-16158815512011518197988-026f5.jpg&amp;_info=cc1261f0862911eb909569233539f8d9\" data-width=\"600px\" data-height=\"400px\" id=\"videoid_104736\" videoid=\"104736\" videoexternalid=\"0\"><div class=\"VideoCMS_Caption\"><p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Trailer b phim Sn h lnh</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Cng tm m ni, <i>Trn tnh lnh</i> c ra mt trong giai on thm d, s thn trng ca bin kch v o din xut pht t vic nh gi thp mc  ci m ca khn gi i vi vn ha am m.</p><p class=\"\">Cch khc ha ca <i>Trn tnh lnh</i> vi am m nhn vo cng ging huynh  ng sinh cng t, tnh cm am m c th hin v cng hm xc; cn trong <i>Sn h lnh</i>, tnh cm am m c khc ha bo dn hn, li thoi biu l tnh yu r rng hn, khin khn gi c th cm nhn c tc ng su sc m vn ha am m mang ti.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/untitled-2-copy-16158807330122038026124.jpg\" id=\"img_e12bc240-8627-11eb-bebd-f3ded52639a3\" w=\"1024\" h=\"768\" alt=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 3.\" title=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"e12bc240-8627-11eb-bebd-f3ded52639a3\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/untitled-2-copy-16158807330122038026124.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">So vi Trn tnh lnh, Sn h lnh c cch th hin tnh cm am m bc bch hn - nh Zhihu</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Vn ha am m, t c ch kim, t phng ng n phng Ty, vn lun tn ti, mc  n nhn cng khc nhau, rt nhiu ngi khi ni n ch  am m u t ra ngi ngng, th nhng t cn st ca <i>Trn tnh lnh</i> v <i>Sn h lnh</i> trn mn nh nh Hoa ng,  ti ng tnh ngy cng nhn c nhiu s ch , c l  ti ng tnh s khng cn l iu g  gh gm m mi ngi u lng trnh.</p><p class=\"\"><b>Dng phim am m m ra bc tin ln trn mn nh nh Hoa ng</b></p><p class=\"\">Hai nm nay, cc nn tng xem phim trc tuyn ua nhau khai thc dng phim am m, knh no cng mun ginh ly mt phn trong ming bnh ny, m nguyn nhn khin  ti am m ngy cng chim c nhiu th phn l s a dng.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/untitled-3-copy-16158808241021887037607.jpg\" id=\"img_17724270-8628-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" w=\"1024\" h=\"673\" alt=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 4.\" title=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"17724270-8628-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/untitled-3-copy-16158808241021887037607.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">n theo cn st phim am m l s ni ting ca dn m nam Tiu Chin, Vng Nht Bc - nh: bilibili</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Th nht, tnh cm gia nam v nam i lp hon ton vi quan nim truyn thng, m s i lp lun d dng gy ch  v tranh ci; </p><p class=\"\">Th hai, theo quy nh ca Tng cc Pht thanh v truyn hnh Trung Quc, khng cho php xut hin tnh cm ng tnh trn phim nh, v th vic chuyn th kch bn c yu cu cao v kh khn hn, nhng c kh khn th s c im xem v c sc ht.</p><p class=\"\">Bn cnh , s n r ca phim tnh cm lng mn, n quyn, tin hip  bo ha th trng phim nh, khn gi cng cm thy nhm chn, s xut hin ca dng phim am m va ng lc m ra th trng mi, cng em n tri nghim mi cho khn gi.</p><p class=\"\">Nguyn nhn cui cng, cng l quan trng nht, cht lng ca tiu thuyt nguyn tc, bt k th no, ni dung vn l yu t ginh chin thng cui cng, m trong lnh vc tiu thuyt am m c rt nhiu tc gi ni ting, s lng ln tiu thuyt am m kinh in  cung cp mt nn tng khch quan, nhng nguyn nhn ny khin th trng phim am m ngy cng ln, thu ht vn u t ngy cng nhiu.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/untitled-4-copy-1615880878910621042776.jpg\" id=\"img_3807c820-8628-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" w=\"1024\" h=\"577\" alt=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 5.\" title=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 5.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"3807c820-8628-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/untitled-4-copy-1615880878910621042776.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Dng phim am m mang n cho khn gi nhng tri nghim mi - nh: bilibili</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Ngoi hai tc phm tiu biu <i>Trn tnh lnh</i> v <i>Sn h lnh</i>, cn c rt nhiu b phim am m c chuyn th t tiu thuyt n khch nh: <i>Vai tri c cu</i> ci bin t nguyn tc <i>Tt d, Ho y hnh</i> ci bin t <i>Husky v s tn mo trng ca hn, Trn hn, Bn tc mai khng phi hi ng hng</i></p><p class=\"\">S bng n dng phim am m  mt mc  no   cho thy suy ngh ca mi ngi  ci m v bao dung hn, mc  chp nhn v hiu bit v vn ha a dng  tng ln, c th ni y l mt bc tin ln.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/untitled-5-copy-16158809236031031478056.jpg\" id=\"img_52a215a0-8628-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" w=\"1024\" h=\"436\" alt=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 6.\" title=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 6.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"52a215a0-8628-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/untitled-5-copy-16158809236031031478056.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Trc s ln ngi ca th loi phim am m, vic  vn u t vo dng phim ny ang l xu hng m cc nh lm phim nhm n - nh Zhihu</p></div></div><p class=\"\">\"Bn c th khng thch n, nhng vn chp nhn s tn ti ca n\", d l phim truyn hnh th loi no, phc v cho khn gi, c khn gi yu thch th l phim hay, phim am m  m ra mt hng i mi cho th trng phim truyn hnh, tr thnh im nng u t v tiu th mi, khin mn nh nh Hoa ng ngy cng a dng v pht trin.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/untitled-6-copy-161588096351097953249.jpg\" id=\"img_6a6c5330-8628-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" w=\"1024\" h=\"685\" alt=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 7.\" title=\"Trn tnh lnh n Sn h lnh, vn mn cn st th loi phim am m - nh 7.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"6a6c5330-8628-11eb-a337-0fa6b0a69fda\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/untitled-6-copy-161588096351097953249.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Hai m nam Trng Trit Hn v Cung Tun  nh thnh cng vang di ca Sn h lnh tr thnh ngi sao n khch - nh Bazaar</p></div></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/tran-tinh-lenh-den-son-ha-lenh-ven-man-con-sot-the-loai-phim-dam-my-20210316150351436.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', '\'Trn tnh lnh\' n \'Sn h lnh\', vn mn cn st th loi phim am m', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tran-tinh-lenh-den-son-ha-lenh-ven-man-con-sot-the-loai-phim-dam-my', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:22:23', '2021-03-20 12:22:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/tran-tinh-lenh-den-son-ha-lenh-ven-man-con-sot-the-loai-phim-dam-my/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(968, 1, '2021-03-20 12:22:38', '2021-03-20 12:22:38', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-16158900109612048549734.jpg\" id=\"img_57896040-863d-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1480\" alt=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 1.\" title=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"57896040-863d-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-16158900109612048549734.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Dn nhn vt trong phim By ngt ngo</p></div></div><p>Chiu 16-3, phim <i>By ngt ngo</i> ra mt bo ch vi dn din vin Quc Trng, Bo Anh, Minh Hng, Diu Nhi, Thun Nguyn v o din inh H Uyn Th. V yu t bo lc, tnh dc cng nh ch  dnh cho ngi trng thnh, phim xp hng C18.</p><p><span style=\"\">L din vin nam chnh ca b phim, Quc Trng gy ch  trong trailer khi nhn vt ng Minh ca anh c tit l l k bo hnh, thao tng tinh thn ngi v Camy (Bo Anh). Nhn vt ca Quc Trng c nhiu cnh nh p, cng hip v uy hip ngi v.</span></p><p><b>Tng gp nhiu n ng bo hnh, trng hoa</b></p><p><i>By ngt ngo</i> xoay quanh nhm bn thn lu nm gm Camy, Qunh Lam (Minh Hng), Linh an (Diu Nhi) v Ken (Thun Nguyn). Camy ly chng sm nht nhm, tng nh hnh phc vi ng Minh - chng trai giu c v thnh t.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-5-16158904773581446493728.jpg\" id=\"img_4b04a050-8642-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1318\" alt=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 2.\" title=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"4b04a050-8642-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-5-16158904773581446493728.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Dn din vin trong bui hp bo gii thiu phim By ngt ngo: Bo Anh, Quc Trng, Minh Hng, Diu Nhi - nh: MI LY</p></div></div><p>Nhng khng ng anh ta li l k thng xuyn nh p v, coi v nh cng c tnh dc  mnh mc sc ch p. Camy nh b cm t trong cuc hn nhn.<br/></p><p>\"<span style=\"\">Ti khng ngi ni mnh tng gp nhiu ngi n ng nh vy trong cng vic kinh doanh. Nhng ngi quen bit ti nu nghe iu ny m git mnh th ng l h c tt. Ti lun t nh mnh khng bao gi c nh vy\" - Quc Trng ni vi </span><i style=\"\">Tui Tr Online</i><span style=\"\">.</span></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-2-16158904773651592571285.jpg\" id=\"img_4aa912d0-8642-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" w=\"1400\" h=\"941\" alt=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 3.\" title=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"4aa912d0-8642-11eb-88e0-e518e8c60761\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-2-16158904773651592571285.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Quc Trng trong vai ngi chng bo hnh ng Minh, Bo Anh trong vai ngi v Camy</p></div></div><p>Quc Trng tha nhn vi mt ngi n ng, vt qua ham mun tnh dc l iu kh khn. Nhng n ng phi lm c v tn trng ngi ph n ca mnh.</p><p> ha thn vo nhn vt bo hnh v, Quc Trng  hc hi din xut thng qua cc b phim nc ngoi.</p><p>Anh cho bit: \"Ti khng th ha thn vo mt hnh mu ngoi i nn tham kho din xut thng qua cc b phim  hiu c nhn vt, hiu c ngi ph n b bo hnh. o din inh H Uyn Th v bn din Bo Anh, mt ngi bn thn ca ti,  gip  ti rt nhiu. Cm n Bo Anh, c b mong manh  b Quc Trng - ng Minh hnh h trong phim\".</p><p><b>Bo Anh ng phim v thng ngi m b bo hnh</b></p><p>Bo Anh nhn li ng vai ngi v Camy b bo hnh v l do rt ring t: c c m rut cng l ngi gp hon cnh tng t.</p><p>\"Ch mt thng quay phim, b bo hnh trong phim thi m ti  thy qu mt mi, au kh. Vy nhng ngi ph n b bo hnh thc s ngoi x hi s cm thy nh th no?</p><p>ng ra ti khng nn ni iu ny. Nhng l do ti nhn vai din l m ti cng tng b bo hnh. Ti chia s iu ny ra s nh hng n cha ca mnh. Ti  dng nhng cm xc tht ca mnh  ha thn vo vai din. Ti tng chng kin s au kh, tht vng v nhu nhc ca m. Tt c iu  u c th hin trong phim\", Bo Anh chia s.</p><p>Sau khi ng phim, Bo Anh mt mt thng  thot vai v nhn vt Camy qu m nh vi c.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-4-161589047736142555550.jpg\" id=\"img_6e905860-863e-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" w=\"1300\" h=\"867\" alt=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 4.\" title=\"Bo Anh ng phim 18+ By ngt ngo v thng ngi m b bo hnh - nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"6e905860-863e-11eb-bf18-0fd9b7ebf2aa\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/bay-ngot-ngao-4-161589047736142555550.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Nhm bn thn 4 ngi trong By ngt ngo</p></div></div><p>Minh Hng, n din vin kim nh u t ca <i>By ngt ngo</i>, tm c vi ch  bo hnh v y l ch  t c phim in nh Vit  cp.</p><p>C ni: \"y l ni au m phim nh cn m x. C nhng ngi trong chng ta tng tri qua. Ti tm thy ting ni chung vi o din inh H Uyn Th v cng nhau ng gp cho kch bn\".</p><p>Minh Hng cho bit vi nhng cnh bo lc, tnh dc, kip chp nhn <i>By ngt ngo</i> c th b xp hng C18. Phim c nhiu cnh nng nhng khng th ct b  k trn vn cu chuyn ca phim.</p><p><i>By ngt ngo</i> ra rp ngy 14-5.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/bao-anh-dong-phim-18-bay-ngot-ngao-vi-thuong-nguoi-me-bi-bao-hanh-20210316164831422.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Bo Anh ng phim 18+ \'By ngt ngo\' v thng ngi m b bo hnh', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bao-anh-dong-phim-18-bay-ngot-ngao-vi-thuong-nguoi-me-bi-bao-hanh', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:22:38', '2021-03-20 12:22:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/bao-anh-dong-phim-18-bay-ngot-ngao-vi-thuong-nguoi-me-bi-bao-hanh/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(969, 1, '2021-03-20 12:22:46', '2021-03-20 12:22:46', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <p>Trong <i>Minari</i>, phim ly bi cnh thp nin 1980, ngi cha vt v gy dng cnh ng rau Hn Quc  bn cho cng ng ngi Hn ti M, nhm nui sng gia nh. </p><p>Anh vp phi nhiu kh khn, tht bi, trong  tm ngun nc l sng cn. C lc anh tng nh tn gia bi sn, nhng  ch khng h b khut phc.</p><p>Cn b ngoi tm mt con sui nh trong rng, ni ngun nc di do, trng mt vt cn nc (minari) - loi rau \"nui sng rt nhiu ngi Hn Quc\". Khng cn chm bm, minari mc xanh tt, lan nhanh nh sc sng kin cng ca nhng con ngi b nh trn min t mi mnh mng.</p><p><span style=\"\"><b>Gic m M qua cp mt tr th</b></span></p><p>Cng l gic m M, cng l cuc sng ca ngi nhp c trn t M - ch  quen thuc trong nhiu b phim, nhng <i>Minari </i>c o vi im nhn ring c: thng qua cp mt ca mt a tr, cu b David Yi (Alan Kim ng).</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/minari-2-16158658209701695698730.jpeg\" id=\"img_0a8a0cf0-8605-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" w=\"1920\" h=\"1081\" alt=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 2.\" title=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"0a8a0cf0-8605-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/minari-2-16158658209701695698730.jpeg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Din vin nh Alan Kim trong vai cu b David, \"i mt\" ca Minari - nh: A24</p></div></div><p><span style=\"\">a tr pht m ting Anh chun hn so vi th ting Anh lai Hn ca cha m chng, kt bn vi m tr con ngi M khi cn rt nh. Nhiu kh nng, cu b s ln ln v tr thnh mt ngi n ng m cht M hn ngi cha Jacob Yi (</span><span style=\"\">Steven Yeun).</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Nhng khc bit gia cu b v b ngoi Soon Ja (</span><span style=\"\">Youn Yuh Jung), ngi mi n t Hn Quc, cng c t m trong phim. Lc vui nhn, lc </span><span style=\"\">au thng, David nhn mi th bng tm hn thun khit, c phn lm lnh, tinh qui, ranh ma nhng vn rt ngy th.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Cu b David chnh l hin thn ca o din </span><span style=\"\">Lee Isaac Chung, chng nhn cho hnh trnh i tm gic m M ca cha m anh. Chung chng kin ton b s hi sinh ca cha m  cc con c cuc sng tt trn t M. Anh cm ng v khc ghi,  ri chuyn ti vo phim nh.</span></p><p>\"Thi nin thiu, ch em ti lun bit rng cuc sng ca cha m c cht tha hip,  khng chnh xc l nhng g h mong mun. Cuc sng khng din ra nh h  k vng. V vy, ti v ch ti c mt nim kht khao su thm,  l khin cho s hi sinh ca cha m khng b ung ph\" - o din Lee Isaac Chung ni vi PBS NewsHour.<span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/minari-3-1615865988211598998622.jpg\" id=\"img_6e08a1b0-8605-11eb-882d-d15eabac42b1\" w=\"700\" h=\"790\" alt=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 3.\" title=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"6e08a1b0-8605-11eb-882d-d15eabac42b1\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/minari-3-1615865988211598998622.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Vai din ngi b Soon Ja sng ng  mang v cho ngi sao 73 tui Youn Yuh Jung  c Oscar N din vin chnh xut sc - nh: A24</p></div></div><p>Ni tht vng v tha hip c th hin r nht qua ni tm ca ngi m Monica Yi (Han Ye Ri), m ca David. Monica tht vng trin min vi cuc sng ti M, c khng ngng trch chng trong thinh lng v qua nhng cuc ci v ny la. Cch th hin no cng ng s ngang nhau, ng bun nh nhau.</p><p>\"Chng ta khng th che ch cho nhau, nhng tin li c th ?\" - li cay ng Monica ni vi chng  phi by ni au trong c, ngi ph n v mng gic m M.<br/></p><p>Khn gi Rosann Tung, mt ngi nhp c gc Hoa, ng cm vi gc nhn ca <i>Minari</i>: \"Ti nhn thy c quan st va hi hc va au n ca <i>Minari </i>v s khc bit gia Hn Quc v M, thng qua i mt tr th. Nhng a tr nh chi bp bnh gia cha m, ng b mnh v cng ng bn ngoi: s khc bit th hin r qua ngn ng, ngoi hnh, hnh vi.</p><p>Ti cng gp p lc phi ha nhp, ng ngha vi vic nh mt dn ngn ng v bn sc Trung Quc v cha bao gi c c cm gic thc s thn thuc (vi cng ng  M)\".</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/minari-4-16158661607161097404657.jpeg\" id=\"img_ab2a5d00-8609-11eb-81f1-91864e4a64d8\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1334\" alt=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 4.\" title=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"ab2a5d00-8609-11eb-81f1-91864e4a64d8\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/minari-4-16158661607161097404657.jpeg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Steven Yeun v Han Ye Ri ng iu trong vai i v chng nhp c y lo toan, tht vng. Steven Yeun c  c Oscar Nam din vin chnh xut sc - nh: A24</p></div></div><p><b>Phim ni bng ngn ng ca tri tim</b></p><p>Vic Qu cu vng  c v trao gii cho <i>Minari</i>  hng mc Phim ni ting nc ngoi hay nht vn cn gy tranh ci. L do qu r rng: y l mt b phim rt M, do M sn xut, o din kim bin kch l ngi M, hu ht dn din vin (ch tr 2 ngi) u c quc tch M, ni ln mt vn  ca nc M.</p><p>\"<i>Minari</i> l b phim v mt gia nh, mt gia nh c gng hc ngn ng ca ring n. Ngn ng  su sc hn so vi ngn ng ting Anh hay bt c ngn ng no.  l ngn ng ca tri tim\" - o din Lee Isaac Chung, ngi c c ting Anh ln ting Hn trong tn gi, l gii.</p><p>Trong phim, mt gia nh nhp c M gc Hn vt ln vi chuyn mu sinh v ro cn ngn ng, vn ha  ha nhp vi vng t nng thn Arkansas. Ngoi i, gii Qu cu vng tht bi trong vic vt qua ro cn ngn ng  cng nhn <i>Minari</i> l mt b phim M c lm nn bi nhng ngi M n t mt x s ca chu , mang dng hnh chu .</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/980/2021/3/16/minari-5-16158663246001083546596.jpeg\" id=\"img_0cbc15e0-860a-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" w=\"1250\" h=\"735\" alt=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 5.\" title=\"Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr - nh 5.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"0cbc15e0-860a-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/minari-5-16158663246001083546596.jpeg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">o din Lee Isaac Chung (tri) v dn din vin, trong  ti t Steven Yeun ni ting vi lot phim The Walking Dead - nh: DEADLINE</p></div></div><p>V nc M l ngi nh chung ca nhng con ngi n t mi quc gia, chu lc, nn cu chuyn ca h, s vt ln ca h cng chnh l mt cu chuyn M. <span style=\"\">Vic mt b phim M b y ra hng mc \"ting nc ngoi\" ch v ni th ting ca cng ng nhp c cho thy Hollywood li mt ln na y ngi nhp c ra ra.</span></p><p>Nhng gii Oscar  trao cho <i>Minari </i> c Phim hay nht, hng mc danh gi nht m b phim xng ng gp mt cng nhng phim M chnh hiu khc.</p><p>Bn cnh  l 5  c Oscar thuc 5 hng mc ln: o din xut sc cho Lee Isaac Chung, Nam din vin chnh xut sc cho Steven Yeun, N din vin ph xut sc cho Youn Yuh Jung, gii Kch bn gc xut sc v Nhc nn xut sc.</p><p><i style=\"\">Minari </i><span style=\"\">ra rp Vit Nam vo ngy 2-4.</span></p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/minari-giac-mo-my-dau-thuong-thuan-khiet-qua-mat-tre-20210306084901215.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Minari: Gic m M au thng, thun khit qua mt tr', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'minari-giac-mo-my-dau-thuong-thuan-khiet-qua-mat-tre', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:22:46', '2021-03-20 12:22:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/minari-giac-mo-my-dau-thuong-thuan-khiet-qua-mat-tre/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(970, 1, '2021-03-20 12:23:00', '2021-03-20 12:23:00', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/raya-5-15-3-1read-only-copy-1615864402666536248206.jpg\" id=\"img_b5203f40-8605-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"1024\" h=\"576\" alt=\"Du n Vit trong bom tn M - nh 1.\" title=\"Du n Vit trong bom tn M - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"b5203f40-8605-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/raya-5-15-3-1read-only-copy-1615864402666536248206.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Nhn vt Raya c truyn cm hng mt phn t Hai B Trng, hnh nh non nc xanh ngt, chic bnh chng, rng tre... u kh c trng Vit Nam</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Trong Raya v rng thn cui cng, vng t Kumandra c v nh mt con rng thn vi 5 x, mi x mang tn mt b phn ca rng thn. Rng l loi vt linh thing  cc quc gia ng Nam , mang  ngha cao p v s sng, s hnh thnh. Rng trong Raya gn vi nc l khi ngun ca s sng.</span><br/></p><p class=\"\">Biu tng rng cng rt  ngha vi ngi dn Vit Nam ni ring bi chng ta c truyn thuyt \"Con Rng chu Tin\".</p><p class=\"\"><b>Du n Vit Nam v ng Nam  m </b></p><p class=\"\"> l Long Tm  vng tri tim rng, vng ng bng tr ph ti p vi dng sng cun chy, chnh l sng Mekong chy qua hu ht quc gia ng Nam  v Vit Nam. L Long V  vng sa mc kh cn, v Long Tro vi ch ni v ch m c trng.  l Long Ct vi rng tre trc khng l - Hollywood Reporter nhn mnh tre l loi cy c trng ca Vit Nam. V Long Nha - x s ca thnh quch, n i c knh c truyn cm hng t Angkor Wat.</p><p class=\"\">Long Tm, qu nh ca cng cha Raya, c ly cm hng t cc vng chu th ven sng Mekong v vnh H Long ca Vit Nam trong hnh hi ni non, sng nc. Khng ch Long Tm, hnh nh sng nc tri di khp cc x ca Kumandra chnh l hnh tng ca nn vn minh la nc  ng Nam . Vua cha c Raya gi l \"ba\", t quen thuc trong ting Vit.</p><p class=\"\">V hnh tng Raya - nng cng cha chin binh, nhn vt chnh ca b phim - b i bin kch Qui Nguyen v Adele Lim cho bit ngun cm hng n t nhng n chin binh uy dng trong lch s v huyn s ng Nam , trong  c Hai B Trng ca Vit Nam.</p><p class=\"\">\"Trong vn ha Vit Nam c cu chuyn ni ting v Hai B Trng. H l nhng anh hng ni ting ca Vit Nam m ti ngh n khi vit kch bn\" - bin kch gc Vit Qui Nguyen ni.</p><p class=\"\">B phim cng c ca ngi v nhng chi tit nh, tinh t khi m t phong tc, li sng ca ngi ng Nam . Khi bc vo khng gian linh thing, h u b giy dp  th hin s tn knh vi thn linh, t tin.</p><p class=\"\">Khi Raya i tm rng thn Sisu, c by ra nhng mn  cng trong  c bnh chng ca Vit Nam. Trn hnh trnh y, Raya t nui sng mnh bng mn mt sy ph bin vi ngi Vit, ng Nam . Cc loi tri cy nh su ring, thanh long, mt xut hin trong phim nh mn qu ho sng ca x s nhit i.</p><p class=\"\">V cng ca cc nhn vt cng c chm cht rt k lng theo k thut ca pencak silat (Indonesia), muay Thai (Thi Lan) v vovinam (Vit Nam).</p><p class=\"\"><b>Ri \"ci ti\"  hng n \"ci ta\" rt </b></p><p class=\"\">Mt im ni bt ca Raya v rng thn cui cng, khin b phim khng ch tt m cn su sc v khc bit vi nhng b phim Disney khc, chnh l tinh thn hng n \"ci ta\" r nt.</p><p class=\"\">Trong nhng b phim Disney v Hollywood trc y, ch ngha c nhn v ci ti c t m. Nhn vt chnh thng chin thng nh tin vo chnh mnh, chng t c sc mnh u vit v chin thng k th, ln lt c ng minh v lun l s 1. H cng thng mt mnh cu th gii v c tung h mt mnh.</p><p class=\"\">Cn trong Raya v rng thn cui cng, chng ta chng kin chin thng m p ca \"ci ta\", ca nim tin dnh cho nhng ngi xung quanh v tinh thn cng ng.</p><p class=\"\">Do , thng ip ca Raya rt  ngha, rt  ng v cng rt thi s trong mt th gii y chia r nh hin nay. Nu khng tin tng v on kt, 5 x s Long Tm, Long V, Long Tro, Long Ct, Long Nha rt d ri vo con ng dit vong. Ch khi on kt li, nm ly tay nhau v tha th cho nhau, h mi tm thy con ng  pht trin bn vng trong ha bnh v thnh vng.</p><p class=\"\">Cch lm ca Raya khng ch l lp ghp nhng yu t b mt ca ng Nam  vo phim mt cch kh cng. B phim thc s  o su xung nhng tng va v vn ha, tm linh, trang phc, li sng, tnh cch v con ngi ng Nam  cng nh gi c nt mt ng Nam  ca cc nhn vt ch khng h \"u ha\". Phim l mt bc tin ln trn hnh trnh a din mo khu vc ny tr nn r nt trong in nh phng Ty.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/dau-an-viet-trong-bom-tan-my-20210316101627015.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Du n Vit trong \'bom tn\' M', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dau-an-viet-trong-bom-tan-my', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:23:00', '2021-03-20 12:23:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/dau-an-viet-trong-bom-tan-my/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(971, 1, '2021-03-20 12:23:09', '2021-03-20 12:23:09', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/cong-bo-ket-qua-2-16158434553461276127093-16158434807351727449678.png\" id=\"img_ce0d2120-85d4-11eb-bdd8-b769aacbcc27\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1347\" alt=\"Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i - nh 1.\" title=\"Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"0c568d30-85d1-11eb-9d2b-83022bf8f2b5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/cong-bo-ket-qua-2-16158434553461276127093-16158434807351727449678.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Ngc Phc ng quang qun qun Ci xuyn Vit 2020,  qun thuc v Bo Bo</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Ti 15-3, chng trnh <i>Ci xuyn Vit 2020</i> chnh thc khp li vi mn tranh ti ca hai th sinh l Ngc Phc v Bo Bo. y c l l vng thi c nhiu khn gi mong i. Ngh s Hoi Linh cng c mt  c v tinh thn cc th sinh.</p><p class=\"\">C tnh, phong cch ca c hai th sinh Ngc Phc v Bo Bo tip tc c chng minh trong vng chung kt <i>Ci xuyn Vit 202</i>0, to nn du n ring chinh phc gim kho Minh Nh v Kiu Oanh. </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/tiet-muc-ngoc-phuoc-4-16158468776621896257104-1615846918052161406809.png\" id=\"img_c66e7880-85dc-11eb-bdd8-b769aacbcc27\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1377\" alt=\"Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i - nh 2.\" title=\"Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"dd3f13d0-85dc-11eb-a726-f5ee3677901b\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/tiet-muc-ngoc-phuoc-4-16158468776621896257104-1615846918052161406809.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Ngc Phc (gia) vo vai tip vin hng khng</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Ngc Phc ng vai mt tip vin hng khng mt hng hng khng gi r trong tc phm <i>H cnh ni u?</i>H tr cho Ngc Phc trong tiu phm ny c din vin Gia Bo, Phng Lan, Duy Khnh Zhou Zhou, Nguyn Tho, Mu t, L L, Phc Lc...</p><p class=\"\">Ni dung tiu phm xoay quanh chuyn bay nh mnh vo vng thi tit xu, phi cng li b \"khng tc\" khng ch, tip vin phi liu mnh iu khin my bay  cu mi ngi.</p><p class=\"\">Vi li din t nhin cng ci duyn sn khu, c tip vin Ngc Phc kho lo x l cc tnh hung rc ri khch hng mang li, to ting ci cho khn gi. Ngc Phc bit tn dng li th hi hnh th v kh nng hot ngn ca mnh khin khn gi thch th.</p><p class=\"\">Gim kho Minh Nh nh gi cao kh nng din xut ca Ngc Phc, cng nh bit cch khai thc cu chuyn, kt hp gia cc thnh vin to nn tit mc nhiu ting ci.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/16/tiet-muc-bao-bao-21-16158471576361077100921.jpg\" id=\"img_6d53fee0-85dd-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1378\" alt=\"Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i - nh 3.\" title=\"Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"6d53fee0-85dd-11eb-b77c-29fc7599307b\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/16/tiet-muc-bao-bao-21-16158471576361077100921.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">on ci lng tung c Hunh Long h tr Bo Bo trong m chung kt</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Cn Bo Bo ng vai mt chng kp i ht chu  l K Yn trong tit mc <i>Bn b hnh phc</i>. H tr Bo Bo c Ngc Hoa, Lc Hong Long, Di Dng, Dim Phng, Lm Thng v on ci lng tung c Hunh Long.</p><p class=\"\">Trn ng i din, Bo Bo gp mt c gi b nhm giang h ui bt. Anh v ngi li  gip c gi chy trn nhng cui cng b nhm giang h bt kp trn sng. Bng mu tr v kh nng x l tnh hung, anh  gii thot c cho c gi.</p><p class=\"\">Trong tit mc d thi ny, Bo Bo   li n tng vi kh nng v o h qung khi ti hin cc nghi thc quan trng trong l K Yn. Ci lng h qung cng chnh l nim am m ca anh.</p><p class=\"\">Gim kho Kiu Oanh ghi nhn ti nng v phong  ca Bo Bo qua cc vng thi, c bit l m chung kt mang n mt tit mc honh trng.</p><p class=\"\">Kt qu chung cuc, vi im tuyt i 20 t ban gim kho, Ngc Phc xut sc tr thnh qun qun <i>Ci xuyn Vit</i> ma th 4. Danh hiu  qun thuc v Bo Bo vi tng im 19,75.</p><div type=\"RelatedOneNews\" class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\">              <img style=\"float: left; width: 150px; height: 120px; margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/150_120/2020/11/24/aea08b561d2dec73b53c-1606178684164600521433-crop-16061786932371705269485.jpg\" alt=\"Ci xuyn Vit tr li sau gn 3 nm vng bng\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/150_120/2020/11/24/aea08b561d2dec73b53c-1606178684164600521433-crop-16061786932371705269485.jpg\"/>     Ci xuyn Vit tr li sau gn 3 nm vng bng     <p class=\"VCObjectBoxRelatedNewsItemSapo\">TTO - Ti 23-11, tp u tin chng trnh Ci xuyn Vit vi ch  Cuc i ti  chnh thc ln sng THVL1 sau gn 3 nm vng bng. Cc th sinh  li n tng khi th hin sc mu ring, to ting ci chinh phc khn gi, ban gim kho.</p> </div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/ngoc-phuoc-dang-quang-cuoi-xuyen-viet-2020-voi-so-diem-tuyet-doi-2021031604292529.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Ngc Phc ng quang Ci xuyn Vit 2020 vi s im tuyt i', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ngoc-phuoc-dang-quang-cuoi-xuyen-viet-2020-voi-so-diem-tuyet-doi', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:23:09', '2021-03-20 12:23:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/ngoc-phuoc-dang-quang-cuoi-xuyen-viet-2020-voi-so-diem-tuyet-doi/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
