(973, 1, '2021-03-20 12:27:58', '2021-03-20 12:27:58', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 ca mac moi (<strong>BN2568-2570</strong>) co 2 trng hp ghi nhan trong nuoc tai Hai Duong va 1 ca uoc cach ly ngay sau nhap canh tai Ninh Thuan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>BN2568</strong> tai phuong Hai Tan, TP. Hai Duong: nam, 8 tuoi, la F1 cua BN2528 va BN2561, uoc cach ly ngay 8/3. Ket qua xet nghiem ngay 17/3 khng nh bnh nhn duong tinh voi SARS-CoV-2. Hien benh nhan ang uoc cach ly ieu tri tai Benh vien a khoa tinh Hai Duong co so 2 - Benh vien ai hoc Sao o co so 2.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>BN2569</strong> tai xa Kim inh, huyen Kim Thanh, tinh Hai Duong: nam, 48 tuoi, la F1 cua BN2484, uoc cach ly ngay 3/2. Ket qua xet nghiem ngay 17/3 xc nh bnh nhn duong tinh voi SARS-CoV-2. Hien benh nhan ang uoc cach ly ieu tri tai Benh vien a khoa tinh Hai Duong co so 2 - Benh vien ai hoc Sao o co so 2.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img alt=\"Thm 3 ca COVID-19 ti Hi Dng v Ninh Thun - 1\" height=\"395\" data-id=\"1548027\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"395\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/18/so-lieu-18042087.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"0\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">S liu thng k ca B Y t.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>BN2570</strong> uoc cach ly ngay sau nhap canh tai Ninh Thuan: nu, 30 tuoi, la cong dan Viet Nam, ia chi tai phuong 4, quan 11, TP. HCM. Benh nhan tren tu Philippines nhap canh san bay Cam Ranh ngay 7/3, uoc cach ly ngay sau khi nhap canh tai tinh Ninh Thuan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ket qua xet nghiem ngay 17/3 khng nh bnh nhn duong tinh voi SARS-CoV-2. Hien benh nhan uoc cach ly, ieu tri tai Benh vien a khoa tinh Ninh Thuan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo bo co ca Tiu ban iu tr, Ban Ch o quc gia phng, chng dch COVID-19, hin Vit Nam cha khi cho 2.198 bnh nhn mc COVID-19.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s nhng trng hp mc bnh ang iu tr ti nc ta, 37 ngi c kt qu m tnh ln 1. Ngoi ra, 18 ngi m tnh ln 2 v 63 bnh nhn m tnh ln 3 vi SARS-CoV-2.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S ca t vong v COVID-19  nc ta n nay l 35, gm 31 ngi ti  Nng, 3 ngi  Qung Nam v 1 ngi  Qung Tr.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phn ln trong s h l ngi cao tui, c bnh l nng nh suy thn mn giai on cui, ung th mu giai on cui khng p ng ho cht, hi chng mch vnh, suy h hp cp, thoi ho a khp, tng huyt p, suy thng thn mn, tiu ng type 2, nhim trng huyt, vim phi, suy kit, suy a tng.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/them-3-ca-covid-19-tai-hai-duong-va-ninh-thuan-ar601745.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'Thm 3 ca COVID-19 ti Hi Dng v Ninh Thun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'them-3-ca-covid-19-tai-hai-duong-va-ninh-thuan', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:27:58', '2021-03-20 12:27:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/them-3-ca-covid-19-tai-hai-duong-va-ninh-thuan/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(974, 1, '2021-03-20 12:31:59', '2021-03-20 12:31:59', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<div>t v ang ngt ngy vi cn st bng  khi CLB Bnh nh qut ng i dn u V-League 2021 l CLB  Nng 1-0  tm thi vn ln xp hng 3 di s chng kin ca HLV Park Hang-seo.</div>\n<p> l trn u HLV Park Hang-seo rt hi lng v mn trnh din ca cc tuyn th. Huy Hng, Thanh Ho tr li sau chn thng v  tt. Nht l H Tn Ti chi n tng v ghi bn thng quyt nh trn u.</p>\n<p>c bit, 1 ngy sau trn u HLV Park Hang-seo bt ng quay tr li sn Quy Nhn. Khng cn khn gi, ln ny ng kim tra rt k mt c mi ti y.</p>\n<div>C th hiu s cn thn ca HLV Park Hang-seo khi cn tm iu kin tt v ph hp nht  tuyn Vit Nam tp hun d kin vo thng 5 ti, chun b cho 3 trn cui cng vng loi th 2 World Cup 2022 gp Indonesia (7.6), Malaysia (11.6) v UAE (15.6).</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"HLV Park Hang-seo 2 ln kim tra sn Quy Nhn, tuyn Vit Nam n Bnh nh? - nh 1\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/quocviet/2021_03_20/park/hotantaiclbbinhdinhdanangngoclinh03_iopm.jpg\" caption=\"HLV Park Hang-seo 2 ln kim tra sn Quy Nhn, tuyn Vit Nam n Bnh nh? - nh 1\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>HLV Park Hang-seo d khn trn CLB Bnh nh gp CLB  Nng ngy 19.3</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>Hng n mc tiu c t nht t 4 - 6 im sau 3 trn, HLV Park Hang-seo   ngh VFF nghin cu a im tp hun c iu kin thi tit ging UAE, ni vo ma h nhit  c th ln n trn 40  C. </div>\n<p>Ni v nng nng,  Vit Nam nu min Trung xp s 2 th khng ai xp s 1. Ci kh l sn bi phi t chun  tng hiu qu bi tp v gim thiu ti a nguy c chn thng cho cc cu th, d kin s lng gi s l 34 ngi.</p>\n<div>Sn Quy Nhn ang c nhng iu kin rt thun li  ng c lm a im tp hun cho tuyn Vit Nam, iu chc chn s l liu kch cu bng  cho ng o ngi hm m ni y ln u tin c n tuyn quc gia v tp hun.</div>\n<p>B ra 15 t ng, sn Quy Nhn  c i tu k lng bao gm lp gh khn i, sa sang phng chc nng v nht l lm li hon ton mt c.</p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"HLV Park Hang-seo 2 ln kim tra sn Quy Nhn, tuyn Vit Nam n Bnh nh? - nh 2\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/quocviet/2021_03_20/park/00hotantaiclbbinhdinhdanangngoclinh06_bcss.jpg\" caption=\"HLV Park Hang-seo 2 ln kim tra sn Quy Nhn, tuyn Vit Nam n Bnh nh? - nh 2\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Hu v H Tn Ti ghi im vi thy Park </p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Nh rt nhiu khn gi  chng kin vo chiu 19.3, mt c Bermuda ca sn Quy Nhn  mt mt mu xanh n tng. Hm , HLV Park Hang-seo  tranh th 15 pht ngh gii lao gia hip  xung sn thm mt c.</p>\n<p> ri nh mun an lng hn vi nhng k vng, n sng nay trc khi ra sn bay HLV Park Hang-seo   ngh tr li sn Quy Nhn  t mnh kim tra tht k khp mt sn trong 15 pht, cng vi phng thay , phng v sinh... mt cch t m.</p>\n<div>Quyt nh trong lng ca HLV Park Hang-seo vn ang c gi kn. Nhng nhn cch ng mc in thoi ra chp lin tc ri vui v ln xe ra sn bay, ngi hm m x Nu c th khp khi mng, ch i ln u tin trong lch s c n tuyn Vit Nam v tp hun di ngy.</div>\n\n<!-- Begin Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n<!-- End Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div><script>\n//window.fbAsyncInit = function() {\n// FB.init({\n// appId : \'288067561729014\',\n// autoLogAppEvents : true,\n// x