(976, 1, '2021-03-20 12:34:03', '2021-03-20 12:34:03', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/logo-nam-tay-nguyen-16161476378171194577481.png\" id=\"img_3a42\" w=\"959\" h=\"551\" alt=\"V m vn phng dy li xe chui: S x l nghim khi tip nhn h s t cng an - nh 1.\" title=\"V m vn phng dy li xe chui: S x l nghim khi tip nhn h s t cng an - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"3a42\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/logo-nam-tay-nguyen-16161476378171194577481.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Trung tm Gio dc ngh nghip Nam Ty Nguyn - nh: TT</p></div></div><p>Lin quan vm vn phng dy li \"chui\", thu hn 8,4 t ng, chiu 19-3, ngun tin ti S Giao thng vn ti (GTVT) k Nng cho bit  nm thng tin sai phm ti Cng ty TNHH Gio dc ngh nghip Nam Ty Nguyn (Trung tm Nam Ty Nguyn, k RLp, k Nng) sau phn nh ca <i>Tui Tr Online.</i></p><p>S GTVT k Nng  chn chnh cc n v phi thc hin ng quy nh v tuyn sinh, dy l thuyt, thc hnh t.</p><p><span style=\"\">\"Do cha nhn c h s t cng an nn cha xc nh c cc sai phm c th ca Trung tm Nam Ty Nguyn. Tuy nhin theo phn nh ca Tui Tr, cc sai phm ca Trung tm Nam Ty Nguyn rt ln, phi x l nghim. Khi c y  h s sai phm, c th cn phi nh ch hot ng ca trung tm ny\", ngun tin khng nh.</span><br/></p><p>V vic quyn li hc vin, ngun tin S GTVT k Nng ni:<span style=\"\">\"Ch c th gii quyt khi c danh sch t cng an\".</span></p><p>Trong khi , ng Tng Nht Trng, gim c Trung tm Nam Ty Nguyn, ph nhn trch nhim v h s, tin u do ch tch HQT L Vit Hu nhn ring, ng khng nm.</p><p>V vy, quyn li ca s hc vin cha c cp giy php li xe nh th no ng cng khng chu trch nhim.   </p><p>Phng vin  nhiu ln lin lc li nhng ng L Vit Hu khng tr li d trc  ng ch ng lin h cung cp thng tin, ri n phng hy cuc hn khng thng bo.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"wrapnote\" data-back=\"#cfe2f3\" style=\"background-color: rgb(207, 226, 243);\"><p><b>S khng cp php nn vic dy li chui s... khng c thm quyn?</b></p><p>Lin quan n vn  ny, chiu 19-3, lnh o S GTVT k Lk c vn bn khng nh khng bit, khng qun l vic nhn h s, dy li \"chui\" ti k Lk ca vn phng i din Cng ty TNHH T vn li xe an ton (s 30 inh Tin Hong, TP Bun Ma Thut).  </p><p>Theo S GTVT k Lk, <span>vic kim tra vi phm ca vn phng ny  c Cng an tnh tin hnh theo thm quyn. Tuy nhin, hin s vn cha nhn c vn bn kt lun t cng an hay bt c n v qun l no.</span></p><p>Cng theo S GTVT k Lk, trong nm 2020 n v  thanh tra v pht hin mt s sai phm ti cc c s dy li xe, trong  c Trng trung cp Bnh Minh  t  nhn 300 h s, hn 1,3 t ng ca hc vin...</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/vu-mo-van-phong-day-lai-xe-chui-se-xu-ly-nghiem-khi-tiep-nhan-ho-so-tu-cong-an-2021031916564941.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'V m vn phng dy li xe chui: S x l nghim khi tip nhn h s t cng an', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vu-mo-van-phong-day-lai-xe-chui-se-xu-ly-nghiem-khi-tiep-nhan-ho-so-tu-cong-an', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:34:03', '2021-03-20 12:34:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/vu-mo-van-phong-day-lai-xe-chui-se-xu-ly-nghiem-khi-tiep-nhan-ho-so-tu-cong-an/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
