(977, 1, '2021-03-20 12:37:08', '2021-03-20 12:37:08', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"content-id\">\n\n                                        \n                                        \n                                        <div class=\"content-news-detail old-news\" data-field=\"body\">\n                                            <p>Cng thng tin <i>Myanmar Now</i> a tin 2 ngi  thit mng khi lc lng an ninh n sng  TP Mogok. Theo thng k ca nhm hot ng Hip hi H tr T nhn Chnh tr (AAPP), s ngi thit mng trong cc cuc biu tnh  ln ti 237 ngi.<br/></p><p>Tnh trng bo lc khng dp tt c s phn n v vic lt  chnh ph c bu c v bt gi b Aung San Suu Kyi. D vy, mt s ngi t chc biu tnh cho bit h  iu chnh chin thut. </p><p>\"Chng ti biu tnh  ni khng c cnh st hay qun i. V khi chng ti nghe tin h ang n, chng ti nhanh chng gii tn. Ti khng mun mt mt ng i no nhng chng ti s phn i bng mi cch c th cho n khi thng li\" - nh vn ng Kyaw Min Htike ni vi hng tin <i>Reuters</i> trc khi ng v nhng ngi khc t chc 1 cuc biu tnh bn ngoi trung tm th trn Dawei. </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img id=\"img_2408b360-8949-11eb-971a-5321a1fdd0a5\" w=\"800\" h=\"533\" alt=\"Cng ng quc t gia tng p lc ln Myanmar - nh 1.\" title=\"Cng ng quc t gia tng p lc ln Myanmar - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"2408b360-8949-11eb-971a-5321a1fdd0a5\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" src=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/2021/3/20/photo-1-16162232693751757017789.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Cnh st chng bo ng bt gi 1 ngi biu tnh. nh: Reuters</p></div></div><p>Theo nhng bc nh do cng thng tin <i>Voice of Myanmar</i> cng b, c hng chc ngi biu tnh tp trung  TP Mandalay v th trn Kyaukme ku gi s can thip t bn ngoi  chm dt bo lc.</p><p>Vo ngy 19-3, Tng th k Lin Hip Quc (LHQ) Antonio Guterres ln n nhng g ng t co l s tn bo ko di ca qun i Myanmar v ku gi \"cng ng quc t cn khn thit phn ng 1 cch thng nht v kin quyt\".</p><p>Trong khi , bo co vin ca LHQ Tom Andrews  ngh s dng cc bin php trng pht  p li nhng g ng gi l cc cuc tn cng tn nhn ca qun i nhm vo ngi dn. Th gii phi p tr bng cch gim kh nng tip cn tin bc v v kh ca h. Ngay by gi\" - ng Andrews vit trn Twitter.</p><p>H vin M  thng qua o lut ln n cuc o chnh. Cc nh lp php M ch trch cc bin php ngy cng khc nghit chng li ngi biu tnh Myanmar. </p><p>Qun i Myanmar  sit cht dch v internet v km hm cc phng tin truyn thng t nhn, khin cho vic xc nhn thng tin cng tr nn kh khn.</p><p>i s cc nc phng Ty  ln n bo lc  khu cng nghip Hlaing Tharyar ca th  thng mi Yangon, ni hng chc ngi thit mng trong vi ngy sau khi cc nh my may mc do Trung Quc lm ch b phng ha cui tun trc. \"Hnh ng ct internet v n p cc phng tin truyn thng s khng che giu c nhng hnh ng ca qun i\" - trch thng bo ngy 19-3 ca cc i s phng Ty.<br/></p><figure class=\"WithCaption-container-Aau3d WithCaption-outside-2Jvzs\"/> \n                                            <!-- B&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u Dable / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                            \n                                            <!-- K&#7871;t th&uacute;c / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                        </div>\n\n                                        <span class=\"author fr\" data-field=\"author\">&#13;\n                                            Bo Hnh</span>\n                                        \n                                        <div class=\"sharemxh bottomshare\">\n                                            \n                                            \n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"print\">\n                                                &#13;\n                                                    <img src=\"https://nld.mediacd