(979, 1, '2021-03-20 12:39:03', '2021-03-20 12:39:03', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><p>HLV Masahiro Shimoda t  king d tin v Vit kiu Lee Nguyn - ngi n ca CLB TP HCM, trc trn u  vng 4 V-League 2021.</p><div id=\"\">\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG9259-8955-1616117661.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=NPvZlM0OSpAc7IV9gf6Q6g\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1591\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"1038\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 65.237651444548%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG9259-8955-1616117661.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=5_i7_dEPru2KwdjQJQHp5Q 1x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG9259-8955-1616117661.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=vrllJPe3Eq0cwwYfwf6h_w 1.5x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG9259-8955-1616117661.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=dFI7cztcUc8c0YURkCG4-Q 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Xc nh Lee Nguyn l ngi n quan trng nht, Si Gn FC cho bit,  c cch ho gii cu th ny. nh: c ng.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG9259-8955-1616117661.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=5_i7_dEPru2KwdjQJQHp5Q\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Lee Nguyn  thi u hai trn cho TP HCM ma ny. nh: <em>c ng.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\"><em>*TP HCM - Si Gn FC: 19h15 th Su 19/3, trn VnExpress.</em></p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Lee Nguyn giu k thut, kho lo v s hu nhn quan chin thut tt. V th, chng ti s c ngi bt cht, khng cho cu y chi t do v tung ra nhng ng chuyn nguy him cho ng i\", HLV Masahiro Shimoda ca Si Gn FC tit l. \"Bn cnh , TP HCM cn c ba tin o Brazil c k thut c nhn v th lc tt na. Ti mun cc cu th Si Gn FC phi chi tp trung,  chia ct h\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">TP HCM l CLB bo chi nht ma ny, khi chiu m tin v Lee Nguyn t M v HLV HLV Mano Polking. </p><p class=\"Normal\">Lee Nguyn, sinh nm 1986, tng khoc o HAGL v Bnh Dng t nm 2009 n 2011. Anh sau  v M thi u, ni bt nht l khi khoc o CLB New England Revolution giai on 2012-2018,  191 trn, ghi 51 bn v tr thnh ngi sao ca CLB. Tin v c b l ngi Vit cn chi cho CLB Los Angeles FC v Inter Miami, CLB thuc quyn s hu ca David Beckham. Cui nm 2020, khi c CLB TP HCM tip xc, anh nhn li.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Vi ng cp  c tha nhn, Lee Nguyn tr thnh mc tiu  cc i th d chng.  trn u vi Qung Ninh tun trc, anh di chuyn rng nhng khng to c t bin v b Phm Nguyn Sa v Nguyn Hi Huy thay nhau theo km. </p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG1561-JPG-6355-1616117661.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=7ol4GN-B1rZvqx8QSAFexg\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1560\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"1012\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 64.814814814815%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG1561-JPG-6355-1616117661.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=NEz2C64nxpXxbkyJGkD7uQ 1x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG1561-JPG-6355-1616117661.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=LSXm4JWarmUdpvc6iTmEVA 1.5x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG1561-JPG-6355-1616117661.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=YWc9epenCTf_KnD0kfMXWQ 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"ng Shimoda s c trn ra mt u tin vi t cch HLV trng Si Gn FC. nh: c ng.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/DONG1561-JPG-6355-1616117661.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=NEz2C64nxpXxbkyJGkD7uQ\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">ng Shimoda s c trn ra mt u tin vi t cch HLV trng Si Gn FC. nh: <em>c ng.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Trn u vi TP HCM hm nay l trn ra mt ca ng Shimoda sau khi tip qun chic gh HLV trng t ng V Tin Thnh. Trc , Si Gn FC  thng hai trn v thua mt. </p><p class=\"Normal\">Si Gn FC di thi HLV Shimoda ang tch cc nng cao th lc. ng thy ngi Nht Bn mong mun cc cu th th hin sc mnh tp th, li  chc chn trc khi tm cch tip cn khung thnh i phng. \"Ti ch mi c ba tun lm vic vi cu th nn cn thm thi gian  truyn t  tng ca mnh cho h hiu. Tuy vy, thi  nghim tc ca h lm ti rt hi lng. Chng ti chin u trn tinh thn tp th v trn derby ny khng ai mun thua cuc. Hy vng cc cu th s th hin ht kh nng  ginh ba im\", ng Shimoda ni.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Trong khi Si Gn FC c nhiu thi gian chun b, TP HCM ch c ba ngy sau khi tr v Qung Ninh. H cn tn tht lc lng khi th mn Bi Tin Dng v trung v Trn nh Khng chn thng, khng th ng k trn ny. Nu nh v tr ca Bi Tin Dng  c Phm Vn Cng thay th  d b cho th mn s mt Thanh Thng, th trung v Nguyn Tng Tin s trm ch ca Trn nh Khng.</p><p class=\"Normal\"><strong>Nhng, vn  quan trng nht ca TP HCM l tm l</strong>. H vn cn m c v trn thua Qung Ninh m ton i cho rng li nhiu thuc v trng ti. Trong khi Lee Nguyn t trng ti bt vit v khng chnh xc khin h mt oan bn thng  u hip hai, th hm qua CLB TP HCM  kin ngh VFF xem li nm tnh hung trng ti sai dn n sai lch kt qu. ng thi ny khng th thay i kt qu nhng c th gp phn gip tinh thn cc cu th thoi mi hn.</p><p class=\"Normal\">HLV Polking nh gi cao Si Gn FC nhng vn tin vo mt chin thng: \"Si Gn FC rt mnh v s hu chn st  Merlo cc k nguy him, nht l khi chi bng bng. Chng ti  tp bi chng bng bng rt nhiu  khc ch cu y. Ngoi ra, chng ti s c mt vi thay i  tip cn trn u tt hn, to nhiu c hi v bn thng hn\".</p><p class=\"Normal\"><strong>i hnh xut pht d kin</strong></p><p class=\"Normal\"><em>TP HCM:</em> Thanh Thng, Tng Tin, Thnh Tn, Tng Quc, Ngc c, Vn Thun, Hong Thnh, Dario, Lee Nguyn, Paulo, Junior.</p><p class=\"Normal\"><em>Si Gn FC:</em> Vn Phong, Cng Thnh, Mnh Cng, Vn Ng, Thiago, Woo Sangho, Minh Trung, Matsui, Vn Trin, Tn Ti,  Merlo.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/162032904-946907762745402-5088-9500-4818-1616117661.png?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=RDPXc24ogKt9e4QXyASEBw\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"849\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"388\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 45.700824499411%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/162032904-946907762745402-5088-9500-4818-1616117661.png?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=q5wVTKVd-DTEDp8xN-aqJw 1x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/162032904-946907762745402-5088-9500-4818-1616117661.png?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=lnStIdpAFM2hhu-sZNkP9w 1.5x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/162032904-946907762745402-5088-9500-4818-1616117661.png?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=V3QSxQhiSvyiNR9rc6ZIIw 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" styl