(982, 1, '2021-03-20 12:42:57', '2021-03-20 12:42:57', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616052123769764754727.jpg\" id=\"img_a71db1a0-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"1429\" h=\"869\" alt=\"Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 - nh 1.\" title=\"Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a71db1a0-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616052123769764754727.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Cc din gi v khch mi ti hi ngh trc tuyn ch  \"Sng kin m hnh thnh ph kiu mu cho mng Lin Hip Quc 100 nm\".</p></div></div><p class=\"\">y l mt trong nhng hot ng ca \"Sng kin 100 nm Lin Hip Quc (UN 2045)\" do Lin Hip Quc v Din n Ton cu Boston t chc.</p><p class=\"\">Hi ngh vi s tham gia ca ng Ramu Damodaran - tng bin tp tp ch <i>Bin Nin S</i> ca Lin Hip Quc, trng Academic Impact ca Lin Hip Quc - iu phi chnh. Cc din gi bao gm ng Kamal Malhotra - iu phi vin thng tr Lin Hip Quc ti Vit Nam; thng c Michael Dukakis - ch tch Din n Ton cu Boston v Vin Michael Dukakis; gio s Thomas Patterson (i hc Harvard); gio s John Quelch (i hc Harvard); gio s Alex Pentland (i hc MIT).</p><p class=\"\">Pha Vit Nam, cc din gi ca hi ngh gm c ng Nguyn Trng Khnh - tng cc trng Tng cc Du lch Vit Nam; ng L Tun Phong - ch tch UBND tnh Bnh Thun; ng Bi Thnh Nhn - ch tch HQT Tp on Novaland</p><p class=\"\"><b>Phan Thit vi c hi tr thnh im n du lch MICE s 1</b></p><p class=\"\">ng Nguyn Trng Khnh - tng cc trng Tng cc Du lch Vit Nam - cho bit chin lc pht trin sn phm du lch n nm 2025, nh hng n nm 2030  xc nh thu ht u t, pht trin du lch MICE l mt trong nhng nh hng quan trng cn c quan tm  Vit Nam.</p><p class=\"\">Trong , Bnh Thun c thin nhin u i vi b bin di (c lt vo top 10 bi bin p nht chu  - Thi Bnh Dng do Skyscanner bnh chn). Nhiu thng cnh v di tch lch s, vn ha bn a c sc, thch hp vi nhu cu gii tr, ngh dng ca khch du lch MICE.</p><p class=\"\">Bn cnh , kh hu n ha v n nh m bo Phan Thit c th n khch quanh nm. Phan Thit cng s hu v tr kinh t - x hi thun li: ca ng khu vc kinh t trng im ng Nam B, l mt nh ca t gic vng du lch \"TP.HCM -  Lt - Phan Thit - Nha Trang\". \"Nh vy, c th ni Phan Thit c y  nhng yu t c bn  pht trin du lch MICE\" - ng Khnh ni.</p><p class=\"\">Tuy nhin, ng Khnh cng cho rng du lch MICE l mt loi hnh du lch cao cp vi nhiu c trng, yu cu cao v mc  chuyn nghip.  tr thnh trung tm du lch MICE ln, Phan Thit cn ch  nhanh chng u t hon thin cc c s, a im c sc cha ln, trang b c s vt cht, k thut cao  p ng yu cu t chc cc s kin, hi ngh chuyn nghip, quy m. Cn nng cao kh nng kt ni giao thng vi cc trung tm, th trng ngun.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616052126856821912027.jpg\" id=\"img_a90424e0-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"960\" h=\"640\" alt=\"Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 - nh 2.\" title=\"Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a90424e0-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/photo-1-1616052126856821912027.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Phan Thit vi nhiu thng cnh v di tch lch s, vn ha bn a c sc, thch hp vi nhu cu gii tr, ngh dng ca khch du lch MICE (nh: khu ngh dng Centara Mirage Resort Mui Ne).</p></div></div><p class=\"\">\"Cn c s ng h, vo cuc ca chnh quyn cc cp t trung ng n a phng; cam kt u t ca cc tp on, nhng sng kin t ph ca cc c nhn, t chc trong v ngoi nc.</p><p class=\"\">V pha Tng cc Du lch, chng ti cam kt s lun ng hnh cng s pht trin ca du lch Bnh Thun trong cng tc nh hng u t pht trin sn phm, xc tin qung b, kt ni doanh nghip v cng nh pht trin ngun nhn lc\", ng Khnh khng nh.</p><p class=\"\">Theo ng L Tun Phong - ch tch UBND Bnh Thun, vi y  tim nng v pht trin du lch, thnh ph Phan Thit c quc t bit n nh mt thin ng ngh dng. Th tng Chnh ph  ph duyt quy hoch tng th pht trin Khu du lch quc gia Mi N n nm 2025, tm nhn n nm 2040.</p><p class=\"\">Theo , Mi N v cc khu vc ln cn  c la chn  tr thnh khu vc u tin pht trin du lch ca Vit Nam, to mt sc bt mnh m v s thu ht u t gip Bnh Thun tr thnh mt im n du lch hp dn, c th cnh tranh vi Pattaya, Phuket ca Thi Lan.</p><p class=\"\">\"Lnh o tnh Bnh Thun c kht vng n nm 2030 Phan Thit l mt vin ngc qu, mt im n du lch v ngh dng ng m c cho cc mc ch du lch bin v gii tr, du lch thm him v th thao, du lch vn ha, tm linh, du lch chm sc sc khe, ngh dng v c bit l du lch hi ngh (MICE)\", ng Phong cho bit.</p><p class=\"\"><b>Tn dng sc mnh ca tr tu th gii</b></p><p class=\"\">Theo ng L Tun Phong, mc tiu a Phan Thit thnh \"Thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 khu vc v th gii\" khng ch   ch ca lnh o a phng m  c nhng chin lc v k hoch trin khai bi bn.</p><p class=\"\">Thi gian qua, tnh Bnh Thun  c nhng bc chuyn mnh ng k v tm nhn, trin khai quy hoch ng b v c s h tng nh ng cao tc mi ang xy dng, sn bay Phan Thit ang hon tt th tc u t, d kin s khi cng trong thng 4-2021. n nm 2025, h tng giao thng kt ni vi thnh ph Phan Thit s c hon thin.</p><p class=\"\">Pht biu ti hi ngh, ng Bi Thnh Nhn - ch tch Tp on Novaland - chia s, trong qu trnh pht trin d n NovaWorld Phan Thiet - mt siu thnh ph bin - du lch - sc khe quy m 1.000ha ti Tin Thnh - Phan Thit, tp on nhn thy ni y hi  cc iu kin, l c hi vng  tr thnh mt im n sng to mi l ton cu.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/18/photo-2-16160521268621306172239.jpg\" id=\"img_a9401c70-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"1430\" h=\"873\" alt=\"Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 - nh 3.\" title=\"Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a9401c70-87ba-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/18/photo-2-16160521268621306172239.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">NovaWorld Phan Thiet v Thnh ph X Hi Tr Tu Nhn To (AIWS City) - s kt hp gia thnh ph o v thnh ph tht to nn mt mu hnh c sc ca th gii nm 2045 (nh phi cnh NovaWorld Phan Thiet).</p></div></div><p class=\"\">Phan Thit l ni ni danh vi \"bin xanh, ct trng, nng vng\" ang c nhiu li th v giao thng kt ni vi cc thnh ph ln trn th gii qua sn bay quc t, cng bin, ng cao tc. Ni y hi  cc iu kin  tr thnh im n ton cu:</p><p class=\"\">C khu du lch quc gia Mi N; c nn vn ha Champa c o, nhiu bi bin sch p t nhin, kh hu quanh nm nng m, qu t di do a dng, chi ph sinh hot thp v ang c quy hoch pht trin. c bit, ch cch TP.HCM khong 150km, Phan Thit khi kt ni vi TP.HCM s tr thnh lin kt vng ni tri.</p><p class=\"\">\"Chng ti mi gi v trn qu ghi nhn mi s ng gp v tr tu, ti lc t cng ng; c bit t Lin Hip Quc v cc thnh vin t chc ca mnh  cng xy dng nn mt thnh ph Phan Thit l vin ngc qu ca nhn loi trong th k 21\", ng Nhn cho hay.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p>Ti hi ngh, cc din gi  xut sng kin m hnh kt ni gia NovaWorld Phan Thiet v Thnh ph X Hi Tr Tu Nhn To (AIWS City) - s kt hp gia thnh ph o v thnh ph tht to nn mt mu hnh c sc ca th gii nm 2045; ng thi tho lun cc hot ng gip a Phan Thit tr thnh \"Thnh ph du lch MICE s 1 khu vc v th gii\".</p><p>ng Michael Dukakis - ch tch Din n Ton cu Boston, ch tch Vin Michael Dukakis - cho bit: \"AIWS City s to ra nhng gi tr mi nh cc Gii thng AIWS  tn vinh nhng  tng, sng kin v gii php t ph ca cc nh t tng v sng to nhm xy dng mt th gii vn minh, thnh vng, ha bnh v hnh phc. </p><p>Chng ti rt vui mng c phi hp vi NovaWorld Phan Thiet, Lin minh Lnh o ton cu Club de Madrid t chc cc s kin quan trng; trc tin s l hi ngh ti Phan Thit vo nm 2022 - nn tng gp phn xy dng Phan Thit tr thnh im n ni bt dnh cho hi hp, khen thng, hi ngh v trin lm (MICE) trn th gii\".</p><p>ng Thomas Patterson - gio s Trng Qun l nh nc Kennedy, thuc i hc Harvard - chia s: \"AIWS City s cng hin nhng  tng  pht trin NovaWorld Phan Thiet, t  gp phn xy dng h sinh thi ti thnh ph Phan Thit da trn cc tiu ch v pht trin bn vng, ci tin cng ngh, sng to trong gio dc v bo tn vn ha\".</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/phan-thiet-chay-dua-tro-thanh-thanh-pho-du-lich-mice-so-1-20210318143225202.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Phan Thit chy ua tr thnh thnh ph du lch MICE s 1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phan-thiet-chay-dua-tro-thanh-thanh-pho-du-lich-mice-so-1', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:42:57', '2021-03-20 12:42:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/phan-thiet-chay-dua-tro-thanh-thanh-pho-du-lich-mice-so-1/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(983, 1, '2021-03-20 12:52:56', '2021-03-20 12:52:56', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S im Vinmec Central Park t c l gn 100% v chun mc y t quc t v 9,96/10 trong tun th 1.271 tiu ch v cht lng iu tr v an ton ngi bnh. y l ln th II, Vinmec Central Park t chng ch JCI danh gi c cng nhn trn ton cu ny.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong t ti thm nh ti Vinmec Central Park qu I/2021, JCI  s dng b tiu chun phin bn 7 mi nht, c hiu lc t 1/1/2021; v l phin bn duy nht tch hp b tiu chun Hip hi nh gi bn ngoi v cht lng trong Chm sc Sc khe Quc t (IEEA) ph duyt thng 12.2020. So vi cc b tiu chun p dng trc , phin bn 7 c nhiu tiu chun kht khe hn, vi cc tiu ch quan trng nh: An ton Laser, thit b cnh bo i vi ngi bnh nguy c cao, nh gi tri nghim ngi bnh v cht lng dch v</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><img alt=\"Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park - TP.HCM nhn chng ch quc t JCJ ln II - 1\" height=\"1019\" data-id=\"1548373\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"1019\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/vinmec-1-10560351.png\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"0\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park c cng nhn t chng ch quc t JCI ln th II v an ton ngi bnh v cht lng iu tr.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D b sung nhiu tiu chun mi nhng kt qu nh gi ca on thm nh cho thy Vinmec Central Park  tim cn im tuyt i  hu ht cc tiu ch. Cc chuyn gia ca JCI nh gi cao bnh vin trong vic m bo ton din cc tiu ch quc t v an ton ngi bnh; ngn nga ti a nguy c nhim khun; tn trng v bo v quyn li  ngi bnh v gia nh an tm chm sc sc khe. c bit, bnh vin hon ton p ng c cc tiu chun mi, tun th chun mc cc tiu ch an ton bc x quang hc, gim thiu nguy c nhim x cho nhn vin v khch hng. Cc khoa phng u s dng thit b y t tn tin, c chc nng cnh bo - bo ng, gip pht hin sm cc nguy c nh hng n qu trnh chm sc v iu tr.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><img alt=\"Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park - TP.HCM nhn chng ch quc t JCJ ln II - 2\" height=\"444\" data-id=\"1548376\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"444\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/vinmec-2-10560463.JPG\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"1\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">Ngi bnh ti Vinmec Central Park c chm sc ton din t cc nhm chuyn mn khc nhau gip nng cao hiu qu iu tr, gim s dng khng sinh, tit kim chi ph...</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V tri nghim dch v, 100% ngi bnh ti Vinmec Central Park c th hng s chm sc ton din t cc nhm chuyn mn khc nhau (bc s, iu dng, nhn vin h tr) thng qua m hnh chm sc i nhm. Khng ch m bo cht lng dch v, m hnh ny cn gip gim s dng khng sinh, tng hiu qu iu tr, tit kim chi ph...cho ngi bnh. Trong cng tc phng chng dch COVID19 cng nh kh nng ng kh bnh dch ton cu, cc chuyn gia JCI cng nh gi cao Vinmec Central Park m bo cht lng v an ton phng chng dch COVID  19 chun quc t.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vinmec Central Park l mt trong nhng bnh vin u tin trn th gii thm nh thnh cng phin bn JCI phin bn 7. Do nh hng ca dch COVID-19, nm 2021, ton b quy trnh thm nh c thc hin trc tuyn. V th, JCI nh gi rt cao vic Vinmec Central Park u t h thng cng ngh thng tin v thit b ghi hnh Full HD ti tt c khu vc trong v ngoi bnh vin, p ng mi yu cu ca cc thm nh vin. TS. L Quc S, G Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park chia s: <em>Vinmec Central Park  a JCI t cc quy trnh vi hn 1.000 tiu chun tr thnh vn ha thm vo tng thnh vin,  mi ngi lun thc s lm vic trong tinh thn Cht lng v an ton ca JCI</em>.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><img alt=\"Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park - TP.HCM nhn chng ch quc t JCJ ln II - 3\" height=\"460\" data-id=\"1548374\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"460\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/vinmec-3-10560382.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"2\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">JCI nh gi cao vic Vinmec Central Park u t h thng cng ngh thng tin v thit b ghi hnh Full HD ti tt c khu vc bnh vin, p ng mi yu cu thm nh.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">nh gi cao nhng thnh cng ca Vinmec Central Park, TS. Robert Christmas, Trng nhm thm nh JCI nhn nh: <em>Khng ch l mt bnh vin p v hin i, Vinmec Central Park c t chc chuyn nghip v phi hp cht ch tuyt vi, lun t s an ton cho ngi bnh v cht lng l u tin hng u. T chc JCI t ho  cng ng hnh vi Vinmec Central Park trong hnh trnh bnh vin khng ngng nng cao cht lng chm sc v iu tr</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park  t chng ch JCI ln I vo thng 6/2017. Vi s kin Vinmec Central Park t JCI ln II ny, Vinmec  tr thnh H thng Y t u tin v duy nht ti Vit Nam c 2 bnh vin  H Ni (Vinmec Times City) v TPHCM (Vinmec Central Park) 2 ln t Du vng JCI.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cng vi b tiu chun JCI, H thng Y t Vinmec lin tc cp nht v thc hin cc tiu chun cht lng quan trng khc nh: Tiu chun cht lng bnh vin theo 83 tiu ch ca B Y t; Cc tiu chun quc t ISO 15189:2012 v Tiu chun cht lng theo 169 tiu ch ca B Y t dnh cho labo y t Mi y nht cc labo chn on khng nh COVID-19 theo tiu chun B Y t ca Vinmec  t chun an ton ca WHO phc v cng ng chng dch kp thi.</p>\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><img alt=\"Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park - TP.HCM nhn chng ch quc t JCJ ln II - 4\" height=\"438\" data-id=\"1548375\" data-detail=\"1\" data-width=\"660\" data-height=\"438\" src=\"https://image.vtc.vn/resize/th/upload/2021/03/19/vinmec-4-10560415.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" data-index=\"3\"/>&#13;\n<figcaption>&#13;\n<p class=\"expEdit\">Cc phng xt nghim ti Vinmec tun th cc tiu chun quc t ISO 15189:2012 v Tiu chun cht lng theo 169 tiu ch ca B Y t dnh cho labo y t.</p>&#13;\n</figcaption>&#13;\n</figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tun th cht ch cc tiu chun cht lng khng ch l iu kin thun li  Vinmec kt ni v chia s cc phng php iu tr mi vi cc t chc uy tn trn th gii m cn khng nh cam kt v n lc ca Vinmec trong hnh trnh thc hin s mnh chm sc sc khe cho ngi dn Vit Nam.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/benh-vien-vinmec-central-park-tp-hcm-nhan-chung-chi-quoc-te-jcj-lan-ii-ar601845.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'Bnh vin Vinmec Central Park', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'benh-vien-vinmec-central-park', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:52:56', '2021-03-20 12:52:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/benh-vien-vinmec-central-park/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(984, 1, '2021-03-20 12:56:58', '2021-03-20 12:56:58', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"abody\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<div>S tr li ca ng Joan Laporta trong cng v ch tch Barcelona ang to nhiu thay i  i bng x Catalan, trong  ha hn mang v mt ngi sao tn cng ng cp  chi cnh siu sao Messi: Haaland t Borussia Dortmund.</div>\n<div>T nht bo th thao <em>Sport </em>va tit l, trong ngy 19.3 ch tch CLB Barcelona Joan Laporta ngay khi va chnh thc nhn vn phng v iu hnh i bng x Catalan th vic u tin l gi cho Mino Raiola bn v vic chuyn nhng Erling Haaland.</div>\n<p>Gia ng Joan Laporta v Mino Raiola rt thn thit, v siu c ny cng l i din ca tin o Zlatan Ibrahimovic v hu v Maxwell - nhng cu th tng c a n Barcelona giai on Joan Laporta lm ch tch t 2003 n 2010.</p>\n<p>Nay vi mi quan h bn cht, mt ln na ng Joan Laporta mun Mino Raiola thit lp phi v a Erling Haaland n sn Nou Camp trong ma h ny. T <em>Sport </em>cho bit, Mino Raiola  tr li ng Joan Laporta rng s rt kh, nhng hon ton c th.</p>\n<p>Erling Haaland c mc ph ph v hp ng 75 triu euro nhng phi vo ma h 2022, cn nu ra i trong ma h ny th mc ph phi t 100 triu euro n 150 triu euro nh i hi ca CLB Borussia Dortmund.</p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"Barcelona  lin h Erling Haaland, Neymar ha ch ti hp Messi ti Nou Camp  - nh 1\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/gianglao/2021_03_20/haaland_scuz.jpeg\" caption=\"Barcelona  lin h Erling Haaland, Neymar ha ch ti hp Messi ti Nou Camp  - nh 1\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Ch tch Barcelona, Joan Laporta  lin h \"siu c\" Mino Raiola bn vic a Erling Haaland n sn Nou Camp </p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Tuy nhin, mi kh nng ra i hay  li ca Erling Haaland, v  thi im no u ty thuc nhiu vo siu c Mino Raiola, ngi nm gi mi chi tit b mt rng buc trong hp ng khi k kt vi Borussia Dortmund hi thng 12.2019.</p>\n<div>Trong khi , ngi i din c ca ngi sao Neymar, ng Andre Cury va h l thng tin khin gii CV Barcelona y phn khi,  l ngi sao ngi Brazil hin c  tr li sn Nou Camp trong tng lai gn  ti hp vi ngi bn Messi thay v  Paris nh tin tc gn y.</div>\n<div>L do theo ng Andre Cury ni vi t El Litoral ca Argentina v Barcelona c ch tch mi Joan Laporta v s gi li c Messi, cn Neymar cng cm thy di triu i ca v ch tch ny i bng x Catalan s hi sinh v sm tr li nh cao. Do ,  nh ny s c hm nng li, nh cch y gn 2 nm chnh ng Andre Cury h l  sp a c Neymar t Paris v li Barcelona th bt thnh pht cht.</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"imagefull\" align=\"center\" style=\"mwidth:600px;\">&#13;\n    <tbody>&#13;\n        <tr>&#13;\n            <td>&#13;\n            <div style=\"text-align:center;color: #595959;\"><img alt=\"Barcelona  lin h Erling Haaland, Neymar ha ch ti hp Messi ti Nou Camp  - nh 2\" src=\"https://image.thanhnien.vn/660/uploaded/gianglao/2021_03_20/messineymar_hjhw.jpeg\" caption=\"Barcelona  lin h Erling Haaland, Neymar ha ch ti hp Messi ti Nou Camp  - nh 2\"/>\n            <div class=\"pswp-content__caption\">\n            <div class=\"imgcaption\">\n            <p>Messi v Neymar s ti hp  Barcelona?</p>\n            \n            </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>&#13;\n            </td>&#13;\n        </tr>&#13;\n    </tbody>&#13;\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>Neymar tng c ng Andre Cury pht hin v lm ngi i din, sau  a n Barcelona nm 2013 chi 4 ma bng trc khi chuyn sang PSG ma h 2017 vi mc gi k lc th gii n nay l 222 triu euro.</div>\n<div>Hin Neymar cha gia hn hp ng mi vi PSG khi thi hn ch cn 1 ma na kt thc (thng 6.2022), cng vic thay i tch cc ca Barcelona hin nay th hon ton c th ngi sao ny quay li sn Nou Camp trong mt din bin gy sc bng  th gii.</div>\n\n<!-- Begin Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n<!-- End Dable In_article Widget / For inquiries, visit http://dable.io -->\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div><script>\n//window.fbAsyncInit = function() {\n// FB.init({\n// appId : \'288067561729014\',\n// autoLogAppEvents : true,\n// xfbml : true,\n// version : \'v2.10\'\n// });\n// FB.AppEvents.logPageView();\n//};\n(function(d, s, id){\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) {return;}\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src = \"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));\n</script><script>\nwindow.fbAsyncInit = function() {\nFB.init({\nappId : \'288067561729014\',\nautoLogAppEvents : true,\nxfbml : true,\nversion : \'v3.1\'\n});\n};\n(function (d, s, id) {\nvar js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\nif (d.getElementById(id)) { return; }\njs = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\njs.src = \"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js\";\nfjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\n}(document, \'script\', \'facebook-jssdk\'));\n</script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/the-thao/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barcelona-da-lien-he-erling-haaland-neymar-hua-chi-tai-hop-messi-tai-nou-camp-131736t.html\">Bo Thanh Nin</a>', 'Barcelona  lin h Erling Haaland, Neymar ha ch ti hp Messi ti Nou Camp | Tin chuyn nhng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'barcelona-da-lien-he-erling-haaland-neymar-hua-chi-tai-hop-messi-tai-nou-camp-tin-chuyen-nhuong', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:56:58', '2021-03-20 12:56:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/barcelona-da-lien-he-erling-haaland-neymar-hua-chi-tai-hop-messi-tai-nou-camp-tin-chuyen-nhuong/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
