(986, 1, '2021-03-20 12:59:03', '2021-03-20 12:59:03', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/logo-khanh-1616149653403897550987.jpg\" id=\"img_62db\" w=\"1723\" h=\"1071\" alt=\"Bt ngi t chc cho 13 ngi Trung Quc vt bin sang Campuchia - nh 1.\" title=\"Bt ngi t chc cho 13 ngi Trung Quc vt bin sang Campuchia - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"62db\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/logo-khanh-1616149653403897550987.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Nguyn Vn Khanh ti c quan iu tra - nh: MINH PHC</p></div></div><p>Theo thng tin t c quan iu tra, Nguyn Vn Khanh quen vi mt ngi tn Bnh  Campuchia.</p><p>T thng 4-2020, Khanh nhiu ln n khch t TP Chu c  a ln x Khnh An, huyn An Ph, tnh An Giang giao cho Bnh t chc cho h xut cnh tri php sang Campuchia vi tin cng 500.000 ng/ngi.  </p><p>Ti 6-3, Khanh thng qua mt ngi bn lin h thu xe16 ch do ti x Nguyn Phng Hng - 35 tui, ng phng Vnh M, TP Chu c - iu khin sang th x Tn Chu, An Giang rc 13 ngi (quc tch Trung Quc) sang TP Chu c.  </p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/19/logo-13-doi-tuong-1616149654234123408743.jpg\" id=\"img_bdaf\" w=\"1199\" h=\"709\" alt=\"Bt ngi t chc cho 13 ngi Trung Quc vt bin sang Campuchia - nh 2.\" title=\"Bt ngi t chc cho 13 ngi Trung Quc vt bin sang Campuchia - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"bdaf\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/19/logo-13-doi-tuong-1616149654234123408743.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">13 ngi quc tch Trung Quc nhp cnh tri php b lc lng Cng an tnh An Giang bt gi ngy 7-3 - nh: MINH PHC</p></div></div><p>n khong 3h15 ngy 7-3, ti x Nguyn Phng Hng rc 13 ngi Trung Quc v n khu vc khm Chu Qui 1, phng Chu Ph B, TP Chu c. Trong lc i mt ngi trn x bin gii Khnh Bnh xung  giao li v nhn tin cng th b lc lng cng an pht hin bt gi.  </p><p>Qua kim tra, lc lng cng an pht hin 13 ngi Trung Quc khng c giy t xut nhp cnh theo quy nh.</p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/bat-nguoi-to-chuc-cho-13-nguoi-trung-quoc-vuot-bien-sang-campuchia-20210319172926522.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Bt ngi t chc cho 13 ngi Trung Quc vt bin sang Campuchia', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bat-nguoi-to-chuc-cho-13-nguoi-trung-quoc-vuot-bien-sang-campuchia', '', '', '2021-03-20 12:59:03', '2021-03-20 12:59:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/bat-nguoi-to-chuc-cho-13-nguoi-trung-quoc-vuot-bien-sang-campuchia/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
