(988, 1, '2021-03-20 13:01:00', '2021-03-20 13:01:00', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div data-field=\"body\">\n                                            <p>\"H chiu vc-xin\" ha hn tr thnh mt trong nhng cng c hu ch lm nn tng cho qu trnh khi phc kinh t hu i dch Covid-19.<br/></p><p><b>T chu  n chu u</b></p><p>y ban chu u (EC) hm 17-3  xut k hoch cp \"Chng ch Xanh k thut s\" (DGC) - mt loi \"h chiu vc-xin\" - nhm to iu kin thun li cho vic i li t do v an ton gia cc nc thnh vin Lin minh chu u (EU) trong bi cnh i dch Covid-19. DGC c gi tr chung trong cc nc thnh vin EU, c cp cho nhng i tng  chng nga hoc  hi phc sau khi mc Covid-19. DGC s c cp min ph, hin th bng hai ngn ng gm ngn ng chnh thc ca quc gia thnh vin pht hnh v ting Anh, c tnh tng tc, an ton, khng mang tnh phn bit i x. N c sn  nh dng k thut s hoc vn bn giy v c tch hp m QR.</p><p>DGC do y ban chu u  xut s ch lu gi nhng thng tin c nhn ti thiu, phn thng tin y t s bao gm ngy tim chng vc-xin, loi vc-xin, kt qu xt nghim hoc xc nhn  hi phc sau khi mc Covid-19. EC nhn mnh h thng \"Chng ch Xanh k thut s\" l mt bin php tm thi v cng c s ht hiu lc ch sau khi T chc Y t th gii (WHO) tuyn b chm dt tnh trng khn cp v y t quc t.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/684/2021/3/19/14-chan-16161631661551065952947.jpg\" id=\"img_319bc260-88bd-11eb-a74a-1f5c37e957ea\" w=\"500\" h=\"333\" alt=\"H chiu vc-xin: Cha kha m ca bin gii - nh 1.\" title=\"H chiu vc-xin: Cha kha m ca bin gii - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"319bc260-88bd-11eb-a74a-1f5c37e957ea\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://nld.mediacdn.vn/2021/3/19/14-chan-16161631661551065952947.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Th tng Israel Benjamin Netanyahu cm th xanh chng nhn  tim vc-xin hm 4-3 nh: REUTERS</p></div></div><p> xut s cn phi c tt c quc gia ni khi EU chp thun. y ban chu u k vng DGC s khi phc quyn t do i li, l mt trong nhng quyn c bn tr ct ca EU, nhm gip cng dn trong khi di chuyn t do mt cch an ton, c trch nhim v ng tin cy. Theo i Euronews,  xut DGC cn phi c thng qua nhanh chng  c Ngh vin v Hi ng chu u  c th trin khai ngay trong ma h nm nay.</p><p>Trc EU, Trung Quc  khi ng chng trnh cp chng nhn y t in t cho ngi dn mun ra nc ngoi, dn u th gii v k hoch cp \"h chiu vc-xin\". Ngi dn Trung Quc  c th s hu chng nhn y t in t hin th tnh trng tim chng vc-xin ca ngi dng v kt qu xt nghim thng qua mt chng trnh trn nn tng mng x hi WeChat k t ngy 8-3. Theo hng tin Tn Hoa X, chng nhn y t in t bao gm m QR cho php cc quc gia khc c c thng tin sc khe ca cng dn Trung Quc nhp cnh.</p><p>Trung Quc d kin m phn cng nhn \"h chiu vc-xin\" vi tng quc gia trong s 40 nc  tha thun mua vc-xin ca h. T trc khi trin khai \"h chiu vc-xin\", chnh quyn Trung Quc  yu cu ngi dn cung cp m QR y t trong WeChat v cc ng dng in thoi khc  c php s dng cc phng tin giao thng ni a cng nh khng gian cng cng. M v Anh cng mt s quc gia khc trn th gii cng ang xem xt vic cp chng nhn y t tng t.</p><p><b>Phao cu sinh ca ngnh du lch</b></p><p> xut \"Chng ch Xanh k thut s\" ca EC ni trn ngay lp tc  nhn c s hoan nghnh v ng h ca Hi ng Du lch v L hnh Th gii (WTTC). iu ny s to ra mt s thc y ng k v rt cn thit cho cc nn kinh t, gip bo v hng triu vic lm. Iceland t ngy 18-3 s m ca bin gii cho ton b du khch  c tim vc-xin m khng cn phi tri qua xt nghim hoc cch ly bt buc.</p><p>Trong khi dch Covid-19 ang c du hiu bng pht tr li, mt s nc EU ph thuc vo du lch nh Ty Ban Nha, Hy Lp v Croatia ang k vng vic p dng h thng \"h chiu vc-xin\" c th m ng cho ma du lch vo ma h nm nay nhm gip vc dy ngnh du lch vn b nh hng nng n. Theo t Telegraph (Anh), ring Hy Lp  c tha thun \"bong bng vc-xin\" vi Israel v Cyprus, cho php ngi  tim chng c th i li gia 3 nc m khng cn cch ly.</p><p>Trong n lc khi phc hot ng bay trn ton cu, Hip hi Vn ti Hng khng quc t (IATA) ang pht trin chng trnh \"h chiu vc-xin\" ca ring mnh thng qua ng dng m h hy vng c th c cng nhn ti cc sn bay trn ton th gii. T gia thng 3, Singapore Airlines  yu cu hnh khch trn chuyn Singapore n London - Anh s dng ng dng di ng Travel Pass (th thng hnh s) do IATA pht trin. ng dng lu tr thng tin sc khe ca hnh khch, gm kt qu xt nghim Covid-19 v tnh trng tim chng. Hng Malaysia Airlines cng d tnh tch hp ng dng Travel Pass vo ng dng in thoi ca h di dng mt th s ha v sc khe.</p><p>Khng ng ngoi cuc, mt s cng ty du lch  Thi Lan ang pht ng chin dch \"M ca Thi Lan an ton\", ku gi chnh ph cho php n du khch quc t tr li t ngy 1-7 ti. Chnh quyn Thi Lan cho hay nc ny ang nghin cu v  tng \"h chiu vc-xin\". T thng 4, hng Air New Zealand cng s yu cu hnh khch i t TP Auckland ti Sydney - c dng th Travel Pass nh \"h chiu vc-xin\" nhm gip xc minh tnh trng tim phng v kt qu xt nghim Covid-19 ca hnh khch. Cc hng British Airways (Anh), Qatar Airways (Qatar), Emirates, Etihad Airways (Cc Tiu Vng quc  Rp Thng nht) cng ng k th im ng dng Travel Pass trn mt s chuyn bay ca h.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode alignCenter active\" data-back=\"#FFFEC7\" data-border=\"#999\" style=\"background-color:#E6E6FA;\" id=\"ObjectBoxContent_1616163331340\" type=\"content\"><div placeholder=\"[nhp ni dung]\"><p><b>WHO khng ng h</b></p><p>WHO hi thng 2 cng b mt bo co tm thi phn i vic tim vc-xin c xem l iu kin i li t do gia cc nc. WHO a nhiu lo ngi v mt khoa hc, o c, lut php v cng ngh nhm khuyn co chnh ph cc nc khng theo ui  tng \"h chiu vc-xin\". Theo mng tin tc Euronews (Php), WHO cho rng vn cn nhng n s quan trng lin quan n hiu qu ca vic tim chng vc-xin chng hn nh mc  hn ch s ly nhim, mc  bo v ca vc-xin trc cc ca nhim khng c triu chng v kh nng min dch ko di bao lu.</p></div></div><p><i>(Cn tip)</i></p>\n                                            <!-- B&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u Dable / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                            \n                                            <!-- K&#7871;t th&uacute;c / &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i &#273;&aacute;p, h&atilde;y truy c&#7853;p http://dable.io -->\n                                        </div><script async defer crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v5.0&appId=889975511027097\"></script>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://nld.com.vn/thoi-su-quoc-te/ho-chieu-vac-xin-chia-khoa-mo-cua-bien-gioi-20210319211611411.htm\">Bo Ngi Lao ng</a>', '\"H chiu vc-xin\": Cha kha m ca bin gii', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ho-chieu-vac-xin-chia-khoa-mo-cua-bien-gioi', '', '', '2021-03-20 13:01:00', '2021-03-20 13:01:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/ho-chieu-vac-xin-chia-khoa-mo-cua-bien-gioi/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
