(990, 1, '2021-03-20 13:03:02', '2021-03-20 13:03:02', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><p><span class=\"location-stamp\">H Ni</span>Ngh s L Hng - bng hng trong tnh khc on Chun - qua i ti 18/3 sau thi gian mc ung th i trng, th 86 tui.</p><div id=\"\">\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ch Thy - con gi ngh s - cho bit b ra i trong vng tay ca con chu ti Bnh vin 108. Nhng ngy cui i, b iu tr ti nh ring theo  nguyn. Tuy nhin, hm 16/3, b yu hn, kh th, cc con li a vo bnh vin cp cu.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Ngh s pht hin bnh t u nm 2020 khi  giai on cui. Thng 9 cng nm, bnh tr nng, ung th di cn n nhiu b phn trong c th. Trong sut qu trnh cha tr, b th hin tinh thn lc quan. Nhng lc tnh to, ngh s thch nghe nhc, lm nhm theo giai iu quen thuc hoc tr chuyn cng con chu. Ch Thy cho bit cch y hn 10 nm, b b t qu, mt ging nn khng ht c na. Trc , b vn i ht cng cc on cu chin binh cho  nh ngh.</p><div style=\"text-align:center\">\n<figure class=\"item_slide_show clearfix\">\n<!--start video embed-->\n<div onclick=\"Video.playVideo(320139)\" id=\"video_parent_320139\" class=\"box_embed_video_parent embed_video_new\" data-vcate=\"1003834\" data-vscate=\"1003007\" data-vscaten=\"Gii tr\" data-vid=\"320139\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-articleoriginal=\"4250823\" data-ads=\"1\" data-license=\"0\" data-duration=\"236\" data-brandsafe=\"0\" data-type=\"0\" data-play=\"0\" data-frame=\"\" data-aot=\"\">\n<div data-vid=\"320139\" class=\"box_img_video embed-container\">\n<img src=\"https://iv1.vnecdn.net/giaitri/images/web/2021/03/19/nghe-si-le-hang-hat-truoc-ngay-hoi-ban-1616122420.jpg?w=750&amp;h=450&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=v-qpAjlMkfMXpibW9CQiLQ\" alt=\"Ngh s L Hng ht &quot;Trc ngy hi bn&quot;\"/>\n</div>\n<div id=\"embed_video_320139\" class=\"box_embed_video\" style=\"display:none;\">\n\n\n<div class=\"embed-container\">\n\n<p>Ngh s L Hng ht \"Trc ngy hi bn\"</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--end video embed-->\n<figcaption class=\"desc_cation\"><div class=\"inner_caption\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Ngh s L Hng th hin ca khc \"Trc ngy hi bn\" (Trnh Qu). Video:<em> Youtube Yyvktt.</em></p>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"Normal\">Nh vn Nguyn Trng Qu au bun khi nghe tin. Anh tng c thi gian gp g, tr chuyn vi ngh s khi thc hin cun sch <em>Mt thi H Ni</em> <em>ht</em> nm 2018. Ln u gp, Trng Qu n tng vi v p du dng, thi  nim n, thn thin ca b. B k v m nhc, nhng k nim trong sut thi gian lm ngh  anh c t liu vit sch. \"C khng c s xa cch ca mt ngh s go ci. Trong sut qu trnh vit sch, c h tr ti rt nhit tnh\", anh ni. Trc Tt, Trng Qu gh thm ngh s, khi  ang cha tr ti bnh vin. C hai tr chuyn v sch, m nhc. B h hi, mt nh ln nim vui khi nhc v ch  mnh yu thch.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Thp nin 1950, b l ngh s ca rp i ng (H Ni) m nhc s on Chun lm gim c. B l nng th trong nhiu tc phm ca ng nh <em>L  mun chiu, T o xanh, Chic l cui cng, Bi ca b x, Tm s, Mu nng c bao gi phai u... </em>Nhng cu ht<em> </em>\"Nhng mi ma thu khi l vng bay v di i/ ng v xa lm  ngi i/ Nh em t ln mi i mt/ i vng em ri vui vi ai\" (L  mun chiu) ly cm hng t b. Tuy nhin, b khng th hin ca khc no ca on Chun.</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/le-hang-8380-1616124240.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=VdlEwLUBOI9SZHYE4AZQMw\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"766\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 63.810391978122%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/le-hang-8380-1616124240.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=_jLBYAIAyYJiybf-x9AlEQ 1x, https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/le-hang-8380-1616124240.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=ijTxWqrXlwVDmcce3wt-Sg 1.5x, https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/le-hang-8380-1616124240.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=zHfdFFfzSjrAR8GweAS1mw 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Ngh s L Hng theo thi gian. nh: Nh vn Trng Qu.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/le-hang-8380-1616124240.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=_jLBYAIAyYJiybf-x9AlEQ\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Ngh s L Hng theo thi gian. nh: <em>Nh vn Trng Qu.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Ngh s L Hng tn tht l L L Ho, sinh nm 1935 ti lng Gip Nh, Thanh Tr, H Ni. B tng ot gii nht k thi ht ti i pht thanh H Ni 1953 nh ca khc <em>m xun d khc</em> ca nhc s Phm Duy. B ghi du n vi cht ging soprano, cao, trong tro qua lot ca khc <em>Trc ngy hi bn</em> (Trnh Qu), <em>Hng v H Ni</em> (Hong Dng), <em>Cu h bn b Hin Lng</em> (Hong Hip),<em> m xun</em> (Phm Duy)... Nm 1984, b c Nh nc phong danh hiu Ngh s u t t u.</p><p class=\"Normal\">L ving ngh s L Hng din ra vo 9h30 ngy 22/3 ti Nh tang l Quc gia, s 5 Trn Thnh Tng, linh cu sau  c ha tng ti i ha thn Hon v, H Ni.</p><p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong>Hiu Nhn</strong></p>\n</div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/nghe-si-le-hang-qua-doi-4250823.html\">VNEXPRESS.NET</a>', 'Ngh s L Hng qua i', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nghe-si-le-hang-qua-doi', '', '', '2021-03-20 13:03:02', '2021-03-20 13:03:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/nghe-si-le-hang-qua-doi/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(991, 1, '2021-03-20 13:05:11', '2021-03-20 13:05:11', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"VideoStream\" data-advmode=\"5\" data-src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=tuoitre&amp;new_info_domain=true&amp;stgdmn=hls.tuoitre.vn&amp;vid=tuoitre/2021/2/19/ket-x-ecau-phu-my-16137256231731197121083-10006.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;poster=https://video-thumbs.tuoitre.vn/tuoitre/2021/2/19/ket-x-ecau-phu-my-16137256231731197121083-10006.jpg&amp;_info=33337700729011eb814f0d69fbb15544\" data-width=\"600px\" data-height=\"400px\" id=\"videoid_103956\" videoid=\"103956\" videoexternalid=\"0\"><div class=\"VideoCMS_Caption\"><p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\">Giao thng trn cu Ph M hng qun 7 i TP Th c b n tc ko di - Video: CHU TUN</p></div></div><p>Theo ong oan Van Tan - giam oc Trung tam Quan ly ieu hanh giao thong o thi TP.HCM, tnh trng un tac tai khu vuc cau Phu My din ra t<span style=\"\">u 12h trua 19-2.</span></p><p><span style=\"\">Nguyn nhn do xe tai bin s 51C-79XXX va 51D-70XXX chy tu huong quan 7 qua TP Thu uc bi hong, phai dung tren cau khien dong xe un u ko di en 14h cung ngay.</span></p><p>Nhn tin bo, luc luong canh sat giao thong lap tuc co mat xu ly, ieu tiet giao thong tu xa e giam luong xe i len cau Phu My.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/2/19/mg0215-1613725754274596089514.jpg\" id=\"img_785f2310-7290-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1414\" alt=\"Cu Ph M kt nhiu gi do xe ti hng v xe container va qut taxi - nh 2.\" title=\"Cu Ph M kt nhiu gi do xe ti hng v xe container va qut taxi - nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"785f2310-7290-11eb-b84e-fd61cdec49f3\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/2/19/mg0215-1613725754274596089514.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Hng di t, xe ti ni ui nhch tng cht mt qua cu Ph M - nh: CHU TUN</p></div></div><p>Theo ghi nhn ca <i>Tui Tr Online</i>, hng ngn xe  phi nhch tng cht mt khi chy qua on cu Ph M hng t qun 7 i TP Th c.</p><p>Trong lc dng xe ni ui nhau vt qua on n  th ti u dc cu Ph M hng t qun 7 i TP Th c li xy ra mt v va chm giao thng gia xe container v taxi, cng khin tnh trng n tc trm trng hn v ko di n<span style=\"\">khong 15h30.</span></p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/2/19/img1600-16137258418141414089234.jpg\" id=\"img_5bc1eec0-7292-11eb-bdd8-b769aacbcc27\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1452\" alt=\"Cu Ph M kt nhiu gi do xe ti hng v xe container va qut taxi - nh 3.\" title=\"Cu Ph M kt nhiu gi do xe ti hng v xe container va qut taxi - nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"5bc1eec0-7292-11eb-bdd8-b769aacbcc27\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/2/19/img1600-16137258418141414089234.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Mt v va chm giao thng xy ra ti u dc cu Ph M - nh: CHU TUN</p></div></div><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/2/19/mg0168-16137258795832023859979.jpg\" id=\"img_74b62d60-7292-11eb-81f1-91864e4a64d8\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1333\" alt=\"Cu Ph M kt nhiu gi do xe ti hng v xe container va qut taxi - nh 4.\" title=\"Cu Ph M kt nhiu gi do xe ti hng v xe container va qut taxi - nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"74b62d60-7292-11eb-81f1-91864e4a64d8\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/2/19/mg0168-16137258795832023859979.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Lc lng cnh st giao thng c mt iu tit v phn lung ng - nh: CHU TUN</p></div></div><div class=\