(mch:  100 ln/pht, huyt p:huyt p ti thiu  90 mmHg, huyt p ti a  140 mmHg, th &gt; 25 ln/pht v/hoc SpO2 &#13;\n</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B Y t cng nu i tng chng ch nh khi tim vaccine COVID-19 l ngi c tin s phn v t  2 tr ln ti ln tim trc hoc vi bt c thnh phn no ca vaccine .</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo , nhn vin y t khm sng lc phi c tp hun chuyn mn v khm sng lc trc tim chng vaccine phng COVID-19.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cc phng tin khm sng lc gm: Nhit k, ng nghe, my o huyt p, my o SpO2 (nu c), bng kim khm sng lc trc tim chng vaccine phng COVID-19.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">i tng tim chng c thm khm nu  iu kin tim chng s c t vn v k giy cam kt ng  tim chng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thc hin vic ghi chp, lu gi c s d liu tim chng ca cc i tng vo phn mm qun l h s sc khe ton dn trn trang in t http//hssk.kcb.vn theo quy nh hin hnh.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phiu khm sng lc trc tim chng v Phiu cam kt ng  tim chng c lu ti im tim chng. Thi gian lu l 15 ngy. Cc ni dung khc cn tun th theo hng dn tim chng ca B Y t.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo B Y t, qu trnh trin khai tim vaccine COVID-19 cn ch nh tim chng ngay cho nhng trng hp  iu kin tim chng. Ngc li, c th tr hon tim chng cho nhng trng hp c cc yu t phi tr hon tim chng.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngoi ra, cn chuyn tim v theo di ti bnh vin cho nhng trng hp c cc yu t thn trng v khng ch nh tim cho nhng ngi c chng ch nh tim chng.</p>\n                            \n                    </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vtc.vn/bo-y-te-khuyen-cao-9-doi-tuong-can-hoan-tiem-vaccine-covid-19-ar601742.html\">VTC NEWs</a>', 'B Y t khuyn co 9 i tng cn hon tim vaccine COVID-19', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bo-y-te-khuyen-cao-9-doi-tuong-can-hoan-tiem-vaccine-covid-19', '', '', '2021-03-20 13:31:11', '2021-03-20 13:31:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/bo-y-te-khuyen-cao-9-doi-tuong-can-hoan-tiem-vaccine-covid-19/', 0