(999, 1, '2021-03-20 13:38:13', '2021-03-20 13:38:13', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><p>Putin thch thc Biden tranh lun trc tip  ngi dn hai nc cng xem, sau khi Tng thng M gi ng l \"k st nhn\".</p><div id=\"\">\n<p class=\"Normal\">\"Ti va mi ngh ti chuyn ny\", Tng thng Vladimir Putin ni trong cuc phng vn trn truyn hnh nh nc Nga hm 18/3. \"Ti mun  ngh vi Tng thng Biden tip tc tranh lun, nhng vi iu kin phi pht trc tip. Khng tr hon, trc tip, ci m, thng thn. Ti cho rng ngi dn Nga v ngi dn M s rt hng th n xem\".</p>\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\" class=\"tplCaption\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/2-1616119525-3965-1616120014.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=TFsZLB0oKRDeIRhGmkL4bA\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"1200\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"834\"/>\n<meta itemprop=\"href\" content=\"\"/>\n<div class=\"fig-picture\" style=\"padding-bottom: 69.444444444444%;position: relative;\"><picture>\n<!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n<source data-srcset=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/2-1616119525-3965-1616120014.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=oF8q7tjdHLXw3bKR6jJhAA 1x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/2-1616119525-3965-1616120014.jpg?w=1020&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=5KQ58_CYUJ0HimD9HZOchg 1.5x, https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/2-1616119525-3965-1616120014.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=Km9jn9ysm5UcT20LTxOxVg 2x\">\n<!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n<img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"position: absolute;width:100%;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Tng thng Putin d mt s kin  Moskva, Nga, hm 18/3. nh: Reuters.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/03/19/2-1616119525-3965-1616120014.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=oF8q7tjdHLXw3bKR6jJhAA\"/>\n</source></picture></div>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\n<p class=\"Image\">Tng thng Putin d l k nim 7 nm ngy sp nhp Crimea  Moskva, Nga, hm 18/3. nh: <em>Reuters.</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure><p class=\"Normal\">Tuyn b ny ca Putin c coi nh mt li \"thch thc\" Tng thng M Joe Biden tham gia tranh lun trc tip, mt ngy sau khi Moskva v Washington n ra tranh ci ngoi giao v bnh lun ca Biden cho rng Putin l \"k st nhn\" khi tr li phng vn knh truyn hnh ABC ca M. Nga lp tc triu hi i s ti M  tham vn v tng lai quan h song phng.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Putin  xut t chc tranh lun vi Tng thng M vo ngy 19/3. \"Ti khng mun ko di. Ti mun ti rng taiga vo cui tun ny  th gin mt cht\", Putin ni. \"V th chng ta c th t chc vo ngy mai hoc th hai. Chng ti sn sng tin hnh bt k lc no thun tin cho pha M\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">Khi c hi v  xut ny ca Putin, th k bo ch Nh Trng Jen Psaki ni rng cuc tranh lun nhiu kh nng khng th din ra, bi Biden s ti Georgia theo lch trnh vo 19/3.</p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Ti mun ni rng Tng thng  i thoi vi Tng thng Putin\", Psaki ni, lu  Biden cn m thoi vi nhiu lnh o th gii khc. \"Tng thng, tt nhin, s ti Georgia ngy mai v kh bn rn\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">Trc , trong s kin trc tuyn k nim 7 nm sp nhp bn o Crimea, Putin cng a ra phn ng v bnh lun ca Biden. \"Ti nh hi cn nh, khi tranh ci trong vn nh, chng ti thng ni \'ng suy bng ta ra bng ngi\'\", Putin ni. \" khng ch l cu ni ca tr con hay tr a. Cu ny cn cha ng n  su sc\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">\"Chng ta lun nhn thy  ngi khc nhng nt tnh cch ca chnh mnh v ngh rng h cng nh mnh\", ng ni thm.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Cc quan chc Nga  phn ng quyt lit trc tuyn b ca Biden trong cuc phng vn vi ABC News pht sng hm 17/3, khi Tng thng M ni rng Putin \"s phi tr gi\" v can thip bu c M. Mt bo co tnh bo M c gii mt ni rng Nga  tm cch gy tn hi cho chin dch tranh c ca Biden ti cuc ua vo Nh Trng nm ngoi, trong khi ng h cho Donald Trump.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Khi c hi liu ng c ngh Putin, ngi b co buc u c i th chnh tr, l \"k git ngi\" hay khng, Biden p: \"Ti c\". Bnh lun c a ra khi B Thng mi M thng bo h s sit hn ch xut khu  trng pht Nga v co buc \"u c\" th lnh i lp Alexei Navalny.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Navalny hi thng 8/2020 bt tnh khi ang trn chuyn bay t Siberia n Moskva, sau  c a ti Berlin, c,  iu tr. Cc nc phng Ty co buc Nga \"u c\" Navalny bng cht c Novichok thi Lin X, nhng Moskva nhiu ln bc b.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Ch tch H vin Nga Vyacheslav Volodin cho rng \"Biden xc phm ngi dn t nc chng ti\", nhn mnh rng \"Putin l Tng thng ca chng ti, cng kch ng y l cng kch t nc chng ti\".</p><p class=\"Normal\">in Kremlin cng bc b co buc can thip bu c M nm 2020. \" l iu hon ton v cn c v khng c c s\", pht ngn vin in Kremlin Dmitry Peskov ni.</p><p class=\"Normal\">Nga cng tng b M co buc can thip bu c nm 2016. Tnh bo M cho rng Nga pht ng chin dch mng x hi c li cho Trump, trong khi lm mt uy tn i th Hilary Clinton. Moskva  bc b co buc ny.</p><p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong>Hng Hnh</strong> (Theo <em>ABC News</em>)</p>\n</div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/putin-thach-biden-tranh-luan-truc-tiep-4250707.html\">VNEXPRESS.NET</a>', 'Putin thch Biden tranh lun trc tip', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'putin-thach-biden-tranh-luan-truc-tiep', '', '', '2021-03-20 13:38:13', '2021-03-20 13:38:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/putin-thach-biden-tranh-luan-truc-tiep/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1000, 1, '2021-03-20 13:40:00', '2021-03-20 13:40:00', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/2/18/quoc-lo-5-16136433214736685253.jpg\" id=\"img_3814cc10-71d2-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" w=\"2000\" h=\"1125\" alt=\"Ch cho xe phc v chng dch COVID-19 i trn quc l 5 qua Hi Dng - nh 1.\" title=\"Ch cho xe phc v chng dch COVID-19 i trn quc l 5 qua Hi Dng - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"3814cc10-71d2-11eb-b051-a11b7a9e5065\" type=\"photo\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/2/18/quoc-lo-5-16136433214736685253.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\">Quc l 5 trn a bn Hi Dng vng v khi hn ch xe qua li - nh: NINH HI</p></div></div><p>y l ni dung c th hin trong cng vn ca Tng cc ng b gi cc s giao thng vn ti, hip hi vn ti ngy 18-2.  </p><p>Theo , trc tnh hnh din bin ht sc phc tp ca dch COVID-19 trn a bn tnh Hi Dng, S Giao thng vn ti Hi Dng   ngh trit  phn lung trn cc quc l 5, 17B, 38, 38B qua a bn tnh Hi Dng phc v phng, chng dch COVID-19.  </p><p>Do vy, Tng cc ng b  ngh cc s giao thng vn ti, cc hip hi vn ti thng tin, qun trit n cc doanh nghip vn ti v t chc, c nhn c phng tin lu thng trn a bn tnh Hi Dng thc hin nghim tc vic phn lung, hn ch lu thng trn cc quc l qua a bn tnh Hi Dng theo phng n ca S Giao thng vn ti Hi Dng.  </p><p>c bit, quc l 5 ch cho php xe  phc v phng chng dch COVID-19, cc xe u tin theo quy nh Lut giao thng ng b; cc phng tin khc di chuyn theo phng n phn lung v cc trng hp c bit khc theo Ch th 16/CT-TTg ngay 31-3-2020 cua Thu tng v theo s ch o ca Ban ch o phng chng dch a phng.  </p><p>Tng cc ng b  ngh cc n v qun l quc l qua a bn tnh Hi Dng phi hp vi cc lc lng chc nng ca tnh phn lung t chc giao thng; Tng cng ty Pht trin h tng v u t ti chnh Vit Nam - VIDIFI (n v qun l quc l 5), phi hp t chc lp cht trm khi cn thit theo  ngh ca S Giao thng vn ti Hi Dng.  </p>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/chi-cho-xe-phuc-vu-chong-dich-covid-19-di-tren-quoc-lo-5-qua-hai-duong-20210218171646363.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Ch cho xe phc v chng dch COVID-19 i trn quc l 5 qua Hi Dng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chi-cho-xe-phuc-vu-chong-dich-covid-19-di-tren-quoc-lo-5-qua-hai-duong', '', '', '2021-03-20 13:40:00', '2021-03-20 13:40:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/chi-cho-xe-phuc-vu-chong-dich-covid-19-di-tren-quoc-lo-5-qua-hai-duong/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
