(1002, 1, '2021-03-20 13:41:09', '2021-03-20 13:41:09', ' [ad_1]\r\n<br><div id=\"main-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"\"><div><img src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/586/2021/3/17/kiem-tra-dien-1-3read-only-16159982886631317880864.jpg\" id=\"img_782023f0-8739-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" w=\"1024\" h=\"576\" alt=\"Cnh bo tin in sinh hot ti TP.HCM s tng mnh do nng nng - nh 1.\" title=\"Cnh bo tin in sinh hot ti TP.HCM s tng mnh do nng nng - nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"782023f0-8739-11eb-8f56-37d0a63ac5c7\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2021/3/17/kiem-tra-dien-1-3read-only-16159982886631317880864.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\"><p data-placeholder=\"[nhp ch thch]\" class=\"\"> trnh nng ha n tin in, nm nay EVNHCM cng b trc thng tin. Trong nh: on kim tra ca B Cng thng kim tra vic ghi ch s in ti TP.HCM nm 2020 - nh: NGC HIN</p></div></div><p class=\"\"><span style=\"\">Trao i vi bo ch, Tng cng ty in lc TP.HCM (EVNHCMC) cnh bo tin in ca cc h gia nh ti TP c th tng cao trong cc thng nng nng v cho hay cc sai st ca nhn vin ghi ch s in s c khc phc, khng  khch hng bc xc trong thi gian ti.</span><br/></p><p class=\"\"><b>Coi chng tin in<span style=\"\">tng mnh</span></b></p><p class=\"\">Theo ng Nguyn Ph Vnh - trng ban kinh doanh EVNHCMC, tiu th bnh qun ngy ca 15 ngy u thng 3 l 76,5 triu kWh/ngy, cao hn sn lng bnh qun ngy ca 15 ngy thng 3 nm ngoi l 76,2 triu kWh/ngy.</p><p class=\"\">Theo ng Vnh, c c thng 3, sn lng in bnh qun ngy ca TP.HCM t 77,3 triu kWh/ngy, tng 1,97% so vi sn lng in bnh qun ngy ca thng 3-2020 l 75,8 triu kWh/ngy v cao hn ngy bnh qun tiu th ca thng 2-2021 l 56,8 triu kWh/ngy.</p><p class=\"\">Vi tnh hnh tiu th in c xu ng tng cao trong ma nng nng, ng Vnh d bo sn lng in nhn bnh qun ngy ca thng 4, 5, 6 tip tc tng cao so vi cng k nm ngoi v t t 79,7 n 81,5 triu kWh/ngy.</p><p class=\"\">Theo ng Vnh, nm 2018 tiu th in h gia nh tng 23%, nm 2019 tng 30,69% v nm 2020 tng 13,52%. Do , ng Vnh cnh bo tin in cc h gia nh s theo xu hng tng cao trong cc thng ma kh sp n.</p><p class=\"\"><b>Khng ct in,<span style=\"\">khng  xy ra sai st</span></b></p><p class=\"\">ng Lun Quc Hng - ph tng gim c EVNHCMC - cho bit trong cao im nng nng, in lc TP.HCM tuyt i khng ct in khch hng, khng ct in bo dng hoc sa cha. ng Hng cam kt \"khch hng tuyt i khng mt in\" trong cao im nng nng sp ti.</p><p class=\"\">ng Vnh cho bit ti TP.HCM  thay hn 83% cngt c chc nng o m t xa. Trc nhiu thc mc v cngt cc nm trc, ng Vnh n u: \"Cngt trc khi lp cho khch hng  c kim tra, kim nh theo quy nh ca php lut. Nu khch hng c khiu ni, cng ty s x l ngay, khng  thc mc ko di\".</p><p class=\"\">c bit, ng Vnh cng cam kt nm nay khng  xy ra cc sai st ch quan ca nhng nhn vin ghi ch s lm nh hng, bc xc n khch hng.</p><p class=\"\">Chiu theo c cu biu gi bn in sinh hot 6 bc thang, EVNHCMC tnh ton ngi tiu dng c tiu th in di 500 kWh/thng c mc tng tin in so vi mc tng in nng tiu th tng i cao khi s dng in nhiu hn t 7-18%. Ngc li, nhm khch hng tiu th trn 500 kWh/thng c mc tng tin in so vi mc tng in nng tiu th thp khi s dng in nhiu hn ch t 1-4%.</p><p class=\"\">ng Nguyn Tn Hng - gim c trung tm chm sc khch hng ca EVNHCM - cho bit hin nay  c hn 867.000 khch hng ci t v s dng ng dng CSKH EVNHCM trn thit b di ng. ng Hng khuyn co khch hng c th ci ng dng ny  theo di ch s, mc tiu th in mi ngy ca gia nh  iu tit mc  s dng in.</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\" type=\"wrapnote\"><p><b>Phc tra 100% khch c sn lng in tng t bin</b></p><p>Trc kh nng ngi dn s phn nh, khiu ni v tin in tng cao trong ma nng nng, EVNHCMC cho bit s trin khai thc hin nhiu gii php  tng cng cng tc cng khai minh bch trong hot ng ghi ch s v pht hnh ha n tin in... Tt c cc kin ngh ca khch hng lin quan n tin in s c thc hin trong vng 24 gi.</p><p>Bn cnh , ngnh in s thng bo v phc tra 100% cho khch hng c sn lng tng t bin t 1,3 ln so vi thng trc lin k. Tt c cc sai st (nu c) lin quan n cngt v ghi ch s cngt u c tip nhn, gii quyt v tin hnh cc th tc truy thu hoc thoi hon tin in cho khch hng theo ng quy nh.</p></div>\n        </div>\r\n<br>[ad_2]\r\n<br><a href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/canh-bao-tien-dien-sinh-hoat-tai-tp-hcm-se-tang-manh-do-nang-nong-20210317232910026.htm\">Bo Tui Tr</a>', 'Cnh bo tin in sinh hot ti TP.HCM s tng mnh do nng nng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'canh-bao-tien-dien-sinh-hoat-tai-tp-hcm-se-tang-manh-do-nang-nong', '', '', '2021-03-20 13:41:09', '2021-03-20 13:41:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/baonhanh/canh-bao-tien-dien-sinh-hoat-tai-tp-hcm-se-tang-manh-do-nang-nong/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
